NK038(nyi)005:1: // dpal mgon po legs ldan ljang sngon drag po'i dbang
NK038(nyi)005:2: chog drag po'i rjes gnang dang bcas pa bzhugs so
NK038(nyi)005:3: // dkon mchog gsum gyi ngo bo chos kyi rje //
NK038(nyi)005:4: sku lnga rab rdzogs drug pa rdo rje 'chang //
NK038(nyi)005:5: gnyis su med pa'i zhabs la gus btud nas //
NK038(nyi)005:6: bka' sdod legs ldan nag po'i dbang chog bri //
NK038(nyi)005:7: gzhung dang mthun pa'i gnas nyid du //
NK038(nyi)005:8: tshad dang ldan pa'i bla ma dang //
NK038(nyi)005:9: snod dang ldan pa'i slob ma yis //
NK038(nyi)005:10: dgos pa'i yo byad tshogs pa dang //
NK038(nyi)005:13: las kyi lha bskyed mchod bstod brlab //
NK038(nyi)005:14: big nan+ta krid a mri ta ku n+da li ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)005:16: sh+au nya ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra s+w+aa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK038(nyi)005:17: suray+aa tsan+da pad+ma d+hu d+hu t+wa a ga na sha /
NK038(nyi)005:27: sarba pany+tsa amri ta h'u h+r+ai th+aa /
NK038(nyi)005:30: at+ya nud pan tod ta h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)005:31: man+dala bsangs sbyangs lha mo gser mdog rgyan ldan bum 'dzin phag la bzhugs /
NK038(nyi)005:34: spro bsdu lam pra tri b+h+ye s+w+aa h+aah dbang bskur byin rlabs spyan drangs bstim /
NK038(nyi)005:35: na mo sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya w+aak+ka tsit+ta badz+ra s+w+aa b+ha wa ad+ma ko & ham /
NK038(nyi)005:36: ma h+aa a dar+sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+ha wa +aad+ma ko nya ham /
NK038(nyi)005:37: badz+ra sa ma ya dza dad pa dad ni dam tshig gi //
NK038(nyi)005:38: tshur gshegs sa yi lha mo che //
NK038(nyi)005:39: mchod yon bzhes nas 'di nyid du //
NK038(nyi)005:40: mchod pas sa bdag dgyes par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:41: e h+ya hi b+ha ga w+aan //
NK038(nyi)005:42: ma h+aa ka ru ni ka tri sha h+aoh sa ma ya stam /
NK038(nyi)005:44: k+aa ya w+aa k+ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra //
NK038(nyi)005:45: kun bzang phyi mchod phud gtor ni //
NK038(nyi)005:46: rtsa sngags mchod sngags btags pas dbul //
NK038(nyi)005:47: bde bar gshegs pa lha mo che //
NK038(nyi)005:48: de sogs tshig dang mdzod kyi sngags //
NK038(nyi)005:49: rtsa sngags mchod sngags btags pas dbul //
NK038(nyi)005:50: de nas bzlas dang bstod pa bya //
NK038(nyi)005:51: lam pra ti b+h+ye ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK038(nyi)005:52: sa'i lha mo bstan ma gzi 'bar ma //
NK038(nyi)005:53: sku gser phyag na gser gyi bum pa bsnams //
NK038(nyi)005:54: 'ja' tshon mdog ldan phag gi khri la bzhugs //
NK038(nyi)005:55: de la phyag 'tshal bsnyen bskur mchod cing bstod //
NK038(nyi)005:56: skyob pa sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK038(nyi)005:57: spyod pa'i tshul dang mchod par gyi //
NK038(nyi)005:58: sa dang pha rol phyin pa la //
NK038(nyi)005:59: lha mo khyod ni dpang du gyur //
NK038(nyi)005:61: rig pa 'dzin pas de lta mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:62: gtor ma'i pha 'bang phyogs gnyis la //
NK038(nyi)005:63: byin la grogs bcol bskrad par bya //
NK038(nyi)005:64: lha mo dgyes nas sa la thim //
NK038(nyi)005:65: lag pa rdo rje dang bcas pas //
NK038(nyi)005:66: sa la gtug cing sngags 'di brjod //
NK038(nyi)005:67: badz+ra kro ta ha na ha na h'u phata //
NK038(nyi)005:68: de nas lha yi sta gon ni //
NK038(nyi)005:69: man+dala bdud rtsi byugs pa bya //
NK038(nyi)005:71: ma h+aa man+dala sid+d+hi gu ru h'u //
NK038(nyi)005:72: dur khrod skra yi cha dbye zhing //
NK038(nyi)005:73: slob dpon bdag bskyed gsal btab la //
NK038(nyi)005:74: man+dala b+h+rum las dur khrod gzhal yas khang //
NK038(nyi)005:75: bskyed cing khrag gi thig le las //
NK038(nyi)005:76: so so'i gnas su rtsa sngags ni //
NK038(nyi)005:77: gdan la lha rnams bskyed par bya //
NK038(nyi)005:78: b+h+rum bi shwa bi shud+he badz+ra dz+ny+aa na tsakra b+h+rum /
NK038(nyi)005:79: sarba dush+ta ni tri ri ra bam ti ra bam /
NK038(nyi)005:80: ko ka thang dmar rgya mtsho'i dbus //
NK038(nyi)005:81: ma la ya yi ri rtse ru //
NK038(nyi)005:82: pho brang lte ba gru gsum lnga //
NK038(nyi)005:83: mu khyud khrag khyams sgo bzhir ldan //
NK038(nyi)005:84: phyi rol 'bes mkhar brgya dang bcas //
NK038(nyi)005:85: rab tu 'jigs pa skyed dbu ru //
NK038(nyi)005:86: dgra bgegs ro yi gdan steng du //
NK038(nyi)005:87: ma h+aa k+aa la kro ta h'u rak+sha kro ti shwa ri rak+mo he /
NK038(nyi)005:88: shar la sogs pa'i khang bzhi ru //
NK038(nyi)005:92: tsit+ta dz+wa la sa ma ya //
NK038(nyi)005:93: khro bo gnod sbyin srin po dang //
NK038(nyi)005:94: ma mor bcas pa 'khor bcas bskyed //
NK038(nyi)005:95: btsan khang rnams la ma mo dang //
NK038(nyi)005:96: bar khyams dbang mo sgo bzhir te //
NK038(nyi)005:97: gru bzhir gru 'degs bzhi dag rnams //
NK038(nyi)005:99: mthar bya gcan zan la sogs pa /
NK038(nyi)005:100: cho ga bzhin du bskyed byas la //
NK038(nyi)005:101: bslab skur drangs thim stim pa la //
NK038(nyi)005:102: phyi nang mchod bzlas bstod pa ni /
NK038(nyi)005:103: h'u lha yi ded dpon tshogs kyi bdag /
NK038(nyi)005:104: legs ldan nag po mthu bo che //
NK038(nyi)005:105: dur khrod bdag po sgrol ba'i ging //
NK038(nyi)005:106: khro bo'i rgyal po khyod la bstod //
NK038(nyi)005:108: drag po'i sku la rgyal ba'i bka' sdod mchog /
NK038(nyi)005:109: de nas ye shes lnga ldan rgyal ba rigs lnga'i 'khor //
NK038(nyi)005:110: phrin las bdud 'dul dgra bgegs kun gyi gshed //
NK038(nyi)005:111: legs ldan 'khor dang bcas la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK038(nyi)005:112: de nas 'dod don la gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK038(nyi)005:113: legs ldan 'khor bcas dgos su gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:114: khyod la bstod pa bya ba dang //
NK038(nyi)005:115: slob ma rjes su bzung bya'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)005:121: de nas bum bteg bum pa gnyis rgyan ldan bsangs sbyangs gong dang mtshungs /
NK038(nyi)005:124: rnam rgyal mgon po'i gzhal yas su //
NK038(nyi)005:125: 'khor bcas bskyed pa'i sgrub thabs bzhin //
NK038(nyi)005:126: las bum gdan gsum mchog gsum gyi //
NK038(nyi)005:127: bdud rtsi 'khyil par bskyed pa ni //
NK038(nyi)005:128: ljags gu rgya gram dril bu can //
NK038(nyi)005:129: brlab cing dbang bskur mchod pa'i bar //
NK038(nyi)005:130: gong bzhin byas la bzlas pa ni //
NK038(nyi)005:131: mgon po'i bsnyen bsgrub bzhi sngags la //
NK038(nyi)005:132: dbang sngags btags la bzla bya zhing //
NK038(nyi)005:133: las bum gong la khrus sngags sbrel //
NK038(nyi)005:134: mgon po'i gong bzhin bstod byas la //
NK038(nyi)005:135: sems dpa' ljang gu sna tshogs phrin las bdag /
NK038(nyi)005:136: sku gsung thugs kyi byin rlabs khyam //
NK038(nyi)005:137: ye shes bdud rtsi srid gsum 'od spung 'khyil //
NK038(nyi)005:138: khro rgyal bdud rtsi 'khyil la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK038(nyi)005:139: snyan gzhu byin ldan chu ru bsam //
NK038(nyi)005:140: de nas slob ma'i sta gon ni //
NK038(nyi)005:141: slob ma khrus byas man+dala dbul //
NK038(nyi)005:142: gral la rim par bgod pa yis //
NK038(nyi)005:143: gsol ba 'di skad gdab par bya /
NK038(nyi)005:146: phyag rgya tshogs mchod dkyil 'khor du //
NK038(nyi)005:147: bdag kyang mnyam par sbyar ba'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)005:148: byin brlabs rab tu bzhugs su gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:149: de 'dod slob bu'i sems gnyis bskyed //
NK038(nyi)005:150: sems nyid ldan pa gsang don sbyin //
NK038(nyi)005:151: e ma bde gshegs snying po las //
NK038(nyi)005:153: khyod la rab tu bstan par bya //
NK038(nyi)005:154: ces pas bar gyi don bshad do //
NK038(nyi)005:155: de nas slob mas gsol ba btab pa //
NK038(nyi)005:156: he ru ka sogs khyed la 'dus //
NK038(nyi)005:157: mthar lam chen por bdag 'dod de //
NK038(nyi)005:159: mkhyen rab ye shes bdag la stsol //
NK038(nyi)005:161: de nas rdo rje slob ma yis //
NK038(nyi)005:162: tshe sba bgegs bskrad sgrib pa bral //
NK038(nyi)005:163: lhar bskyed go bgo lus bsrung bya //
NK038(nyi)005:164: +aa yu dz+ny+aa na b+hin du sha badz+ra sngags kyis bskrad /
NK038(nyi)005:165: lag sor bslab bral bde stobs sbyangs //
NK038(nyi)005:166: rtsa ba'i sngags kyi mgon por bskyed //
NK038(nyi)005:167: go bgo lus bsrungs bka' nan cing //
NK038(nyi)005:168: de nas srung skud gsum sgril la //
NK038(nyi)005:169: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa'i sngags kyis btab //
NK038(nyi)005:170: dpung par bcings pas lus bdag bya //
NK038(nyi)005:171: man+dala rigs lnga'i rab gnas ldan //
NK038(nyi)005:172: so shing dor ste ltas rtog go //
NK038(nyi)005:173: tsan dan 'am ni dri chu la //
NK038(nyi)005:174: sngags btab khrus bshal khongs su btung //
NK038(nyi)005:175: badz+ra dzi ha sam b+har d+ha ni h'u /
NK038(nyi)005:176: hri bi shud+d+ha sarba d+harma sarba sa pa nish+tsa pa
NK038(nyi)005:177: sha d+ha ya sarba bi skalpa sa na ye s+w+aa
NK038(nyi)005:178: h+aa / de nas bgegs bskrad bshad kyang rung //
NK038(nyi)005:179: d+hi dang ha yi sngags pa yis //
NK038(nyi)005:180: ku sha chun po gnyis byin la //
NK038(nyi)005:181: sngags dang bstan bya rmi lam rtag /
NK038(nyi)005:182: dri zhing ngan na bzlog pa bya //
NK038(nyi)005:183: de nas thig tshon byin rlabs te //
NK038(nyi)005:184: legs ldan dkyil 'khor gzhung bzhin bri //
NK038(nyi)005:185: las gzhung bsrang la gzhung bzhin mchod //
NK038(nyi)005:187: slob ma khrus bya man+dala dbul /
NK038(nyi)005:188: dpal mgon legs ldan nag po yis //
NK038(nyi)005:189: lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK038(nyi)005:191: dpa' bos thugs rjes gzung du gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:192: legs ldan nag po'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK038(nyi)005:194: las dang bsam pa thams cad 'grub //
NK038(nyi)005:195: bla med theg chen 'bras bu thob //
NK038(nyi)005:196: gnas skabs bstan pa bsrung ba'i phyir /
NK038(nyi)005:198: slob mas nus zhes khas blangs pa'i //
NK038(nyi)005:199: bu khyod su yin ci la dga' //
NK038(nyi)005:200: bdag ni las mchog skal bar ldan //
NK038(nyi)005:202: sangs rgyas mdzad dka' spyad nas ni //
NK038(nyi)005:203: 'gro ba thams cad bsgral bar mos //
NK038(nyi)005:206: ha la ha la ram kro ta kro ta yam /
NK038(nyi)005:210: sdom pa rim par blang ba ni //
NK038(nyi)005:211: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK038(nyi)005:212: ces nas byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK038(nyi)005:213: ces sogs dang e ma ngo mtshar lnga brjod /
NK038(nyi)005:214: dam tshig khas blangs ba ni /
NK038(nyi)005:216: rdo rje chos dbyings kun gyi gtso //
NK038(nyi)005:217: sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig ni //
NK038(nyi)005:218: bde ba mchog gi dam pa de //
NK038(nyi)005:219: sems can don dang 'phrin las grub //
NK038(nyi)005:220: sangs rgyas yon tan 'byung ba'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)005:221: dam tshig dam pa bsrung bar bgyi //
NK038(nyi)005:222: dam tshig thob par gsol gdab pa //
NK038(nyi)005:223: chos sku rang bzhin dag pas na //
NK038(nyi)005:224: bdag kyang rang bzhin rnam par dag /
NK038(nyi)005:225: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK038(nyi)005:227: sems can 'byams klas ma lus kun //
NK038(nyi)005:228: mchog nyid 'grub par bgyis pas na /
NK038(nyi)005:229: sku'i dbyig tu bdag bskyed cig /
NK038(nyi)005:230: slar yang bzlog par mi bgyid do //
NK038(nyi)005:231: bcom ldan mchog gis bzung lags te //
NK038(nyi)005:232: mchog nyid bsgrub phyir rdo rje blang bar bgyi //
NK038(nyi)005:233: rdo rje rgyal po khyed bzhugs pas //
NK038(nyi)005:234: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje ste //
NK038(nyi)005:235: rdo rje bdag nyid mchog nyid ste //
NK038(nyi)005:236: phun sum tshogs pa bsgrub lags pas //
NK038(nyi)005:237: bdag la dus 'dir stsal du gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:238: 'di ni rgyal ba kun gyi thugs //
NK038(nyi)005:239: sangs rgyas kun gyi dam tshig yin //
NK038(nyi)005:240: lus ngag yid gsum sku gsung thugs //
NK038(nyi)005:241: rtag tu 'bral bar ma byed cig /
NK038(nyi)005:242: de ltar khyod kyi rtag tu spyod //
NK038(nyi)005:243: tsan dan chu dang bdud rtsi sbyin //
NK038(nyi)005:244: 'di ni khyod kyi dmyal ba'i chu //
NK038(nyi)005:245: dam tshig 'das na bsreg par byed //
NK038(nyi)005:246: sangs rgyas kun gyi khrag chen po //
NK038(nyi)005:247: snying nas drangs te thung bar byed //
NK038(nyi)005:248: yak+sha kro ta sa ma ya h'u /
NK038(nyi)005:249: de ltar bas na bu khyod kyi //
NK038(nyi)005:250: dam tshig 'di ni bsrung bar gyis //
NK038(nyi)005:251: dam tshig bsrung na dngos grub ni //
NK038(nyi)005:253: pany+tsa a mri ta tha tha tha h'u //
NK038(nyi)005:254: de ring phan chad bu khyod kyi //
NK038(nyi)005:255: phyag na rdo rje nga yin gyis //
NK038(nyi)005:256: nga yi ji ltar bgo ba bzhin //
NK038(nyi)005:257: khyod kyi de lta bya dgos so //
NK038(nyi)005:260: ye shes phan pa'i rjes su sbyar na spyi dang mthun zhing thamsacada zer /
NK038(nyi)005:261: sngon tshe gong nas bsnyen pa'i lha //
NK038(nyi)005:262: bdag gi nye gnas gang lag pa //
NK038(nyi)005:263: las 'phro thugs rje ldan pa'i lha //
NK038(nyi)005:264: gang yin de la 'bab gyur cig /
NK038(nyi)005:266: pra ti gri h+na swa mi lam //
NK038(nyi)005:267: sa t+wa ma h+aa b+ha la /
NK038(nyi)005:268: rdo rje che ge mo zhes bya'o //
NK038(nyi)005:269: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dang //
NK038(nyi)005:270: dpa' bo rnal 'byor ma thams cad kyis byin gyis rlobs cig /
NK038(nyi)005:271: dpal he ru ka bdag la dbab tu gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:272: badz+ra sa ma ya dzah ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK038(nyi)005:273: e d+h+ye b+h+aa ka w+aan ma h+aa ka ru ni ka tri sh+ya ho /
NK038(nyi)005:276: a we sha ya k+aa ya wak+ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra /
NK038(nyi)005:277: sngon gyi mig mkhan rgyal po yis //
NK038(nyi)005:278: thur mas ling tog bsal ba ltar //
NK038(nyi)005:279: bu khyod kyi ni mi shes pa'i //
NK038(nyi)005:280: rab rib rgyal ba rnams kyis bsal //
NK038(nyi)005:281: badz+ra dz+ny+aa na tsak+shu pra be sha ya phata /
NK038(nyi)005:283: ni ye shes lhun gyis grub //
NK038(nyi)005:284: mum ni ye nas rang sangs rgyas //
NK038(nyi)005:285: h'u ni rtsa brgyad byang chub sems //
NK038(nyi)005:286: dkyil 'khor rnam gsum dbyer med pas //
NK038(nyi)005:287: na zhes mthong ba yongs su dag /
NK038(nyi)005:288: ma 'dres yongs su mthong bar shog /
NK038(nyi)005:289: pho brang dbus na thod mkhar lnga //
NK038(nyi)005:290: dkyil na gyi ling yab yum te //
NK038(nyi)005:291: khro bo gnod sbyin srin po dang //
NK038(nyi)005:292: ma mo rim pas phyogs bzhir gnas //
NK038(nyi)005:293: btsan mo srin mo bcu drug dang //
NK038(nyi)005:294: gru chad bzhi la gru 'debs bzhi //
NK038(nyi)005:295: bar 'khyams khrag mtsho dbang mo dang //
NK038(nyi)005:296: sgo bzhir sgo ma chen mo bzhi //
NK038(nyi)005:297: de dag mtha' na 'bebs mkhar brgyad //
NK038(nyi)005:298: kun gyi phyi na sha za dang //
NK038(nyi)005:299: gnod sbyin 'dre srin ro langs dang //
NK038(nyi)005:300: bya gcan lce spyang mang pos bskor //
NK038(nyi)005:301: sha khrag rus pa ri dang mtsho //
NK038(nyi)005:302: dur khrod gnas chen 'jigs pa ltos //
NK038(nyi)005:303: man+dala phul la dbang nyid zhu //
NK038(nyi)005:304: dbyig gi ye shes gtso mchog nyid //
NK038(nyi)005:305: rdo rje sems dpa' mchog 'dzin pa //
NK038(nyi)005:306: khyod ni dam tshig mchog lags kyis //
NK038(nyi)005:307: dbang phyug rgyal por dbang bskur cig /
NK038(nyi)005:308: rin po che yi dbang mchog 'di //
NK038(nyi)005:309: sangs rgyas kun gyi phyag byas pa //
NK038(nyi)005:310: gsang gsum gnas las byung ba yis //
NK038(nyi)005:311: rdo rje'i dbang bskur chen po sbyin //
NK038(nyi)005:312: dbang rdzas rnam lnga'i slob ma la //
NK038(nyi)005:313: rigs lnga'i rab gnas tshul bzhin bya //
NK038(nyi)005:314: don lnga'i rtog pa so sor bskyed //
NK038(nyi)005:315: mkha' dbyings rnam dag bum pa'i nang //
NK038(nyi)005:316: dpal ldan mgon po'i dkyil 'khor bzhugs //
NK038(nyi)005:317: gnyis med byang chub sems rtogs chus //
NK038(nyi)005:318: byin rlabs chu yis dbang thob shog /
NK038(nyi)005:319: bur kur ma h+aa ka la kro ta h'u //
NK038(nyi)005:320: rak+sha kro ti shwa ri drag mo he kro ta
NK038(nyi)005:321: yak+sha rak+sha tsit+ta dz+wa la sa ma y+aa ha he
NK038(nyi)005:322: phata b+h+yo / ru lu ru lu a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK038(nyi)005:328: a b+hi shika ta ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin dbu rgyan mchog /
NK038(nyi)005:329: gzi brjid phung po bla na med //
NK038(nyi)005:330: sangs rgyas rin chen las byung ba'i //
NK038(nyi)005:331: dbu rgyan mchog gi dbang bskur ro //
NK038(nyi)005:332: rat+na mu ku tra a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK038(nyi)005:333: chos sku rdo rje mtshan nyid de //
NK038(nyi)005:334: rdo rje la yang mtshan nyid med //
NK038(nyi)005:335: rdo rje lta bu'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK038(nyi)005:336: chos sku rdo rje lta bur ltos /
NK038(nyi)005:338: 'di ni sang rgyas gsungs dbyangs nyid //
NK038(nyi)005:339: ye shes sems dpa'i dam tshig rnams //
NK038(nyi)005:340: rdo rje sems dpa'i dka' thub dam //
NK038(nyi)005:341: rtag tu khyod kyi bcang bar gyis //
NK038(nyi)005:343: yang dag bla med dkyil 'khor du //
NK038(nyi)005:344: mtshan drangs rdo rje'i ming rtags pa //
NK038(nyi)005:345: sngags 'chang ming gi dbang bskur bas //
NK038(nyi)005:346: rig 'dzin zhing du grags gyur cig /
NK038(nyi)005:349: slob dpon khyod ni dgongs su gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:350: legs ldan nag po'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK038(nyi)005:351: gsang ba mchog gi dbang bskur bas //
NK038(nyi)005:352: de ring bdag la stsal du gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:353: dkyil 'khor rnams gsum dbyer med pa'i //
NK038(nyi)005:354: yab yum gnyis med bde ba'i don //
NK038(nyi)005:355: byang chub sems kyi thig le 'dis //
NK038(nyi)005:356: bde chen rgyal por dbang bskur ro //
NK038(nyi)005:357: a ho ma h+aa su kha bo d+hi tsit+ta +aahman+dala phul la 'di skad zhu //
NK038(nyi)005:358: khyod ni dam tshig kun gyi gtsang //
NK038(nyi)005:359: rdo rje sems dpa'i bskyed mdzad ma //
NK038(nyi)005:360: sems can don sgrubs phrin las kyi //
NK038(nyi)005:361: thugs rje mnyam sbyor grub par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:362: nye gnas kro ti shwa ri ma //
NK038(nyi)005:363: mtshan ma sgeg cing mdzes pa mo //
NK038(nyi)005:364: lhan cig skyes dga' skyed pa'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)005:365: lha mo 'di dang rol bar gyis //
NK038(nyi)005:367: de bzhin gshegs pa dgyes pa gyi //
NK038(nyi)005:368: rdo rje chos dbyings kun gyi gtso //
NK038(nyi)005:369: mi gnas chags pa chen po las //
NK038(nyi)005:370: ma lus 'byung gnas bdag la stsol //
NK038(nyi)005:371: gsang ba'i gsang chen rab gsang ba //
NK038(nyi)005:372: rang gi sems kyi me long ltos //
NK038(nyi)005:373: mthong bas de bzhin nyid du 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)005:374: gzhan min rang byung de kho na'o //
NK038(nyi)005:375: de nas drag po'i rjes gnang ni //
NK038(nyi)005:376: lcags khang dmigs rten byas pa'i mthar //
NK038(nyi)005:377: drag po'i rdzas rnams bgram par bya //
NK038(nyi)005:378: mgon po 'khor bcas bskyed bstim bskul //
NK038(nyi)005:379: yon tan brjod la sbyin par bya //
NK038(nyi)005:380: bsnyen bsgrub rim pa'i sngags brjod cing //
NK038(nyi)005:381: man ngag thams cad rdzogs par sbyin //
NK038(nyi)005:382: sangs rgyas kun gyi ral gri che //
NK038(nyi)005:384: dgra bgegs gdug pa bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)005:385: de ring bu yis blang bar bya //
NK038(nyi)005:387: ti ra bde chen gsal shing 'di /
NK038(nyi)005:388: srid gsum dbang du bsdu ba dang //
NK038(nyi)005:389: gdug pa brdul du rlag bya'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)005:390: de ring ti ra rat+na d+ha ka dz+wa la a b+h+yi /
NK038(nyi)005:392: dug lnga dbyings su bsgral ba dang //
NK038(nyi)005:393: sdig can lnga phung bshig pa'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)005:394: de ring badz+ra a ba d+ha //
NK038(nyi)005:395: drag po'i gnam lcags phur bu 'di //
NK038(nyi)005:396: dbyings nas ye shes shar ba dang //
NK038(nyi)005:397: zhig bcu gnas su bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)005:398: de ring badz+ra k+ai la ya a b+hi /
NK038(nyi)005:399: thod rlon gdug pa'i khrag gis bskong //
NK038(nyi)005:400: 'khor ba dong nas sprug pa dang //
NK038(nyi)005:401: dam nyams snying khrag 'thung ba'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)005:402: de ring ka pa ma rak+ta a b+hi //
NK038(nyi)005:403: mdung rnon g.yang gzhi ru mtshon 'di //
NK038(nyi)005:404: bdud kyi g.yul las rgyal ba dang //
NK038(nyi)005:405: ban dgra'i snying gzer gdab pa'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)005:406: de ring badz+ra shu la a b+hi //
NK038(nyi)005:408: 'khor bcas gnas nas drangs pa dang //
NK038(nyi)005:409: dgra srog yan lag sdam pa'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)005:410: de ring n+aa ga pa sha a b+hi /
NK038(nyi)005:411: chos sku yon tan mchog mnga' ba'i //
NK038(nyi)005:412: phyag mtshan drag po tsa ma ra //
NK038(nyi)005:413: dam can gnas mchog mgo ba'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)005:414: de ring badz+ra tsa ma ra a b+hi /
NK038(nyi)005:415: legs ldan khro rgyal thugs ka nas //
NK038(nyi)005:416: tsar sha pa ni mtshon cha mchog /
NK038(nyi)005:417: yungs dkar rgyal po sha ri ram //
NK038(nyi)005:418: de ring badz+ra si ta li rak+sha yak+sha a b+hi /
NK038(nyi)005:419: gu gul sbyar ba'i rdzas mchog 'di //
NK038(nyi)005:420: dgra bo lha dang dbye ba dang //
NK038(nyi)005:421: bgegs rnams nyes nas bskrad pa'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)005:422: de ring ma ku ta la a pra ti la ab+hi //
NK038(nyi)005:423: ri rab gling bzhi rgya gram 'di //
NK038(nyi)005:424: rtog pa'i zug rngu gzhil ba dang //
NK038(nyi)005:425: gdug pa can rnams mnan pa'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)005:426: de ring b+hi sha badz+ra sum e bam ma ya a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK038(nyi)005:428: nyon mongs 'khor ba bag chag dang //
NK038(nyi)005:429: dgra bgegs thams cad bsreg bya'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)005:430: de ring badz+ra dz+wa la ram kha a b+hi /
NK038(nyi)005:431: thabs shes chags sdang mda' gzhu dang //
NK038(nyi)005:432: drag po'i thun zor dam rdzas 'di //
NK038(nyi)005:433: dgra bgegs rdul du brlag bya'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)005:434: de ring badz+ra tik+sh+na khad kha a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK038(nyi)005:435: de nas zhabs la spyi bos gtug /
NK038(nyi)005:436: yon mchog dbul zhing gtang rag gtang //
NK038(nyi)005:437: tshogs kyi mchod pas mnyes par byas //
NK038(nyi)005:438: lhag brten gshegs bsdu lus srung bsngo //
NK038(nyi)005:439: dza gad rdzas kyi bkra shis gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:440: dpal ldan mgon po legs ldan nag po'i dbang dang
NK038(nyi)005:441: drag po'i sngags kyi rjes gnang bla ma gong ma'i
NK038(nyi)005:442: yi ge btsun myong se bar mngon nas /
NK038(nyi)005:443: dur khrod mngon par rol pa'i mtshon cha 'khor lo dang /
NK038(nyi)005:444: dug gi spu gri'i rgyud dang /
NK038(nyi)005:445: rgya gzhung mthun phyir gsal bar /
NK038(nyi)005:446: gtsang shod sa ma ti d+h+wa dzas sdebs pa /
NK038(nyi)005:447: bde gsal don dang ldan pa zhes bya ba 'dis /
NK038(nyi)005:448: 'gro ba mang po'i don byed par gyur cig /
NK038(nyi)005:452: gsang bdag phyag na rdo rje /
NK038(nyi)005:464: zur chung shes rab grags pa /
NK038(nyi)005:466: 'dar nag pa bsod nams grags pa /
NK038(nyi)005:473: bar ston blo gros rgyal mtshan /
NK038(nyi)005:476: sh+aa kya'i ras pa rdo rje chos rgyal bzang po /
NK038(nyi)005:477: spang ston chos kyi rgyal mtshan /
NK038(nyi)005:479: de gnyis ka la slob dpon chen po bde legs rgyal mtshan /
NK038(nyi)005:480: des bar rin chen rgyal mtshan //
NK038(nyi)005:481: des gnubs ston rat+na sh+ri b+ha dra /
NK038(nyi)005:482: des dpal he ru ka'i ngo bo zur dbang rgyal hor rdo rje /
NK038(nyi)005:483: des gtsang bsang ston gyi sa'i thig le gsal ba gong gi 'du khang gi steng du /
NK038(nyi)005:484: theg pa mchog gi rnal 'byor pa /
NK038(nyi)005:486: rdo rje grags pa rgyal mtshan /
NK038(nyi)005:487: mkhyen rab dbang phyug dbon po rnams la sgru 'phrul
NK038(nyi)005:488: zhi khro dong sprugs legs ldan dang bcas pa'i dbang
NK038(nyi)005:489: rdzogs par dge zhing bka' stsal pa /
NK038(nyi)005:490: bstan pa dar rgyas 'gro ba smin grol shog /
NK038(nyi)005:491: lha btsun gtor bton gyi dapa'o //
NK038(nyi)005:492: dpal ye shes kyi mgon po legs ldan nag po'i mchod phreng bzhugs so //
NK038(nyi)005:493: bcom ldan 'das he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)005:494: 'di gar dpal ye shes kyi mgon po legs ldan gyi mchod phreng gtong bar 'dod pas /
NK038(nyi)005:495: yi dam gang byed kyi dkyil 'khor bcas kyi rim pa rnams gzhung dang mthun zhing /
NK038(nyi)005:496: ye shes kyi mgon po'i bris sku dang //
NK038(nyi)005:498: spyan gzigs la sogs pa rnams mdzes shing bag dro bar bshams /
NK038(nyi)005:499: de nas rang nyid bde ba'i gdan la 'dug ste /
NK038(nyi)005:500: gu gul dang sha chen la sogs bsreg /
NK038(nyi)005:501: rkang gling dang rol mo sna tshogs spir zhing //
NK038(nyi)005:502: rang nyid yi dam gsal ba'i nga rgyal dang ldan pas 'di skad do //
NK038(nyi)005:503: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u /
NK038(nyi)005:505: bdag nyid dpal du gsal ba'i thugs ka nas /
NK038(nyi)005:508: rak+ta'i rgya mtsho chen por gyur /
NK038(nyi)005:509: de'i dbus su ram 'phros 'dus 'od du zhu ba las //
NK038(nyi)005:510: ri bo ma la chos 'dzin rigs kyi sgrub gnas //
NK038(nyi)005:511: dug shing nags tshal gtum pa'i dur khrod //
NK038(nyi)005:512: gnam lcags ur mo char ltar 'bab pa //
NK038(nyi)005:513: gsur chen dud pa sprin ltar 'thibs pa //
NK038(nyi)005:514: bya gcan sna tshogs 'phur zhing lding ba //
NK038(nyi)005:515: sha za lce spyang rgyug cing 'gral ba //
NK038(nyi)005:516: dur khrod ma mo mkha' 'gro 'du ba'i gnas //
NK038(nyi)005:517: rab tu 'jigs shing bskrag pa'i bsgrub gnas su //
NK038(nyi)005:518: bdag nyid dpal du gsal ba'i thugs ka nas bam 'phros 'dus 'od du zhu ba las /
NK038(nyi)005:519: bam ro'i thod mkhar du gyur te //
NK038(nyi)005:520: shar phyogs stag gi thod pa /
NK038(nyi)005:522: nub phyogs rta yi thod pa /
NK038(nyi)005:523: byang phyogs bya'i thod pa las grub pa de yang /
NK038(nyi)005:524: stag thod thams cad 'dzum mu lu lu /
NK038(nyi)005:525: mi thod thams cad bshugs pa tse re re /
NK038(nyi)005:526: rta thod thams cad 'tsher lha nga nga ra ra /
NK038(nyi)005:527: bya thod thams cad tshig sgra di ri ri yod pa /
NK038(nyi)005:528: de la srin po'i thod pas kha bad byas pa /
NK038(nyi)005:529: ngos la rgyal po glog ltar 'khyugs pa /
NK038(nyi)005:530: las kyi 'od zer thog mda' 'phro ba /
NK038(nyi)005:531: rtse nas bdud bya nag po lding ba /
NK038(nyi)005:532: ru mtshon sna tshogs pu ru ru 'phyar ba /
NK038(nyi)005:533: gnam lcags 'bar ba'i sgo mo bcug pa /
NK038(nyi)005:534: de'i nang du lcags mkhar nag po /
NK038(nyi)005:535: gru gsum 'bar ba re re nang gi lcags mkhar
NK038(nyi)005:536: gyi dbus su rdo rje brag dang rin po che'i
NK038(nyi)005:537: khri / pad+ma nyi zla brtsegs pa'i steng /
NK038(nyi)005:538: bam chen gsar rnying bsnol ba'i gdan stengs su /
NK038(nyi)005:539: bdag nyid dpal du gsal ba'i thugs ka nas /
NK038(nyi)005:541: rdo rje dang gri gug lte ba rus mtshan par gyur /
NK038(nyi)005:542: sbur kur ma h+aa ka la ya h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)005:543: zhes sngags ci mang bzlas la /
NK038(nyi)005:544: ma h+aa ka la nyid kyi skur gyur te /
NK038(nyi)005:545: mgon po legs ldan sku mdog mthing nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK038(nyi)005:546: dbu skra thor gtsug gyen du bardzesa pa /
NK038(nyi)005:547: shangs kyi dbyibs mtho zhing khro gnyer smin phrag tu brjid pa /
NK038(nyi)005:548: stag dang pa ta'i gong lag byas pa /
NK038(nyi)005:549: dbu dang phyag zhabs la rin po che'i sbrul gyis brgyan pa /
NK038(nyi)005:550: de ltar gsal ba'i zhabs kyi glang mo gnyis gnyis /
NK038(nyi)005:551: rtsib log g.yas g.yon gnyis na phar ba rkang rdabs dang /
NK038(nyi)005:553: dpung pa g.yon gnyis na seng ge ral pa can gnyis /
NK038(nyi)005:554: spyi bor bya khyung nag po klu mtha' yas mgo bo gsum pa /
NK038(nyi)005:555: lus po sbrul du 'dug pa'i mjug ma zhal du gsol ba /
NK038(nyi)005:556: klu'i lag pa gnyis thal mo sbyar ba //
NK038(nyi)005:557: srin po lag pa g.yon khar bcug pa //
NK038(nyi)005:559: de'i g.yas su las kyi bdud po khros pa gcer bu nag po /
NK038(nyi)005:560: bya rog gi gdong pa can //
NK038(nyi)005:562: g.yon thod khrag sbrul gyis brgyan pa 'dzin pa //
NK038(nyi)005:563: g.yon du las kyi srin mo smug nag gcer sha za zhing //
NK038(nyi)005:564: ral gri dang snying thogs pa mche ba gtsigs pa //
NK038(nyi)005:566: kha phyir ltas pa rgyab tu las kyi bdud po nag po //
NK038(nyi)005:567: g.yas lcags kyu dang g.yon thod khrag 'dzin pa //
NK038(nyi)005:568: mdun du nye gnas kro ti shwa ri ma g.yas ral gri dang g.yon b+han+d+ha 'dzin pa //
NK038(nyi)005:569: bzhi ka'ang bam gyi gdan la bzhugs par gyur //
NK038(nyi)005:570: shar du gying gi rgyal po lag pa gnyis gsal shing mi ro la btsugs nas //
NK038(nyi)005:571: mkhar ba'i tshul du brten pa /
NK038(nyi)005:572: 'khor du gying gi tshogs kyis bskor ba /
NK038(nyi)005:573: lhor za byed dkar mo shel phreng ma /
NK038(nyi)005:574: gser gyi rdo spyi bo nas brgyan pa /
NK038(nyi)005:575: phrag pa gnyis na nyi zla 'char ba /
NK038(nyi)005:576: phyag na gser gyi gri dang zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK038(nyi)005:577: seng ge dkar mo la zhon pa /
NK038(nyi)005:578: 'khor du ma mo'i tshogs kyis bskor ba /
NK038(nyi)005:579: nub tu gza' bdud nag po ra hu la /
NK038(nyi)005:580: dbu dgu bya rog gi dbu dang bcu /
NK038(nyi)005:582: g.yon chu srin zhags pa bsnams pa dud ka smad sbrul mjug tu 'khyil ba /
NK038(nyi)005:583: lus po thams cad mig gis gang ba /
NK038(nyi)005:585: dregs pa sde brgyad kyis bskor ba /
NK038(nyi)005:586: byang du gnod sbyin zangs mdog rgyal mo smug nag /
NK038(nyi)005:587: g.yas gri gug dang g.yon b+han+d+ha 'dzin pa /
NK038(nyi)005:588: yum bse gdongs zangs kyi rdzu 'phrul can gyi tshogs dpag tu med pas bskor ba /
NK038(nyi)005:589: lha tshogs de rnams kyi dpral bar /
NK038(nyi)005:590: mgrin par +aah thugs kar h'u las 'od 'phros pas //
NK038(nyi)005:591: gnas ri bo ma la ya'i rtse mo nas dpal
NK038(nyi)005:592: ye shes kyi mgon po legs ldan nag po la
NK038(nyi)005:593: / gshog pa can gyis nam mkha' gang kheng ba /
NK038(nyi)005:594: ldeer mo can gyi sa gzhi gang ba /
NK038(nyi)005:597: bsgrub pa po bdag gi stong grogs la gnas 'dir spyan drangs /
NK038(nyi)005:598: badz+ra sa ma dzah zhes rol mo sbir /
NK038(nyi)005:599: de nas spyan drangs pa ni /
NK038(nyi)005:601: lang ka yul gyi grol brdal gyi //
NK038(nyi)005:602: dbus kyi ri bo ma la ya //
NK038(nyi)005:603: ko ka thang dmar rgya mtsho'i do //
NK038(nyi)005:604: drag shul yod pa'i rtse mo na //
NK038(nyi)005:605: bcom ldan rdo rje srin po yis //
NK038(nyi)005:606: bdud kyi sde rnams btul nas kyang //
NK038(nyi)005:607: gsang ba sngags kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i tshe //
NK038(nyi)005:608: ming gi dbang bskur bran du khas blangs nas //
NK038(nyi)005:609: rdo rje ro langs tshogs kyi bdag /
NK038(nyi)005:610: mgon po nag po chen po la //
NK038(nyi)005:611: nye gnas kro ti shwa ri ma //
NK038(nyi)005:612: yab yum gnyis su med pa'i sku //
NK038(nyi)005:613: lang ka'i mnga' bdag la sogs pa //
NK038(nyi)005:614: slas dang byed po bran mo'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:615: 'dus pa chen mo rnal 'byor tshogs bcas rnams //
NK038(nyi)005:616: gnas 'dir brtse phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:619: rdo rje brag chen gtam pa dang //
NK038(nyi)005:620: nyi zla pad+ma rin chen khri //
NK038(nyi)005:621: bam chen bsnol ba'i gdan stengs su //
NK038(nyi)005:622: rab 'jigs dpa' bo 'khor bcas bzhugs su gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:624: lha min dmag tshogs g.yul bzlog cing //
NK038(nyi)005:625: lha dmag dkar pos dbugs 'byin pa //
NK038(nyi)005:626: legs ldan nag po 'khor bcas la //
NK038(nyi)005:627: mchod cing bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK038(nyi)005:629: bsod nas gzi brjid pa la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK038(nyi)005:630: ye shes tshogs chen rdzogs la phyag spyod pa rlabs
NK038(nyi)005:631: chen pa la drag shul mthu chen pa la pha
NK038(nyi)005:632: rol phyin bcu pa la sgrib pa rnams gnyis dag
NK038(nyi)005:633: la bdag med gnyis med rtogs la ston pas lung
NK038(nyi)005:634: bstan thob la sngon gyi rgyal ba rnams dang dgongs
NK038(nyi)005:635: pa gcig / rig 'dzin bsgrub thabs rnams dang byin rlabs gcig /
NK038(nyi)005:636: ma mo mkha' 'gro rnams dang dam tshig gcig /
NK038(nyi)005:637: lha srin sde brgyad rnams dang mthu rtsal gcig /
NK038(nyi)005:638: sngon gyi drang srong rnams dang smon lam gcig /
NK038(nyi)005:639: tshogs bdag khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK038(nyi)005:640: mgon po khyed la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK038(nyi)005:643: stong gsum 'adi'am stong gsum gzhan dag na //
NK038(nyi)005:644: la du la phug la sogs yid bzhin zas //
NK038(nyi)005:645: thang skyes chu skyes la sogs longs spyod rkyen //
NK038(nyi)005:646: 'chi med bdud rtsi la sogs dam tshig chu //
NK038(nyi)005:647: rim gsum mchod pa tshogs bdag mnyes gyur cig /
NK038(nyi)005:648: rdo rje can gyi rnal 'byor khyod //
NK038(nyi)005:649: rdo rje can du ci nges pa //
NK038(nyi)005:650: gsang ba gsum dang mnyam pa'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)005:651: mi phyed rdo rje'i dam tshig sbyin //
NK038(nyi)005:652: mi phyed rdo rje'i dam tshig 'di //
NK038(nyi)005:653: gsang ba gsum gyi dbyings nas byung //
NK038(nyi)005:654: dkyil 'khor gsum gyi dam tshig nyams //
NK038(nyi)005:655: sgrubs gnas 'jigs pa'i dus med do //
NK038(nyi)005:656: gsang ba gsum gyi gdams pa nyams //
NK038(nyi)005:657: khyod kyis rab tu bslus gyur na //
NK038(nyi)005:658: de nas khros pas sha chen po //
NK038(nyi)005:659: nyams pa'i snying nas drangs te 'thung //
NK038(nyi)005:662: yak+sha a mri ta stod na ra kan /
NK038(nyi)005:664: rdo rje dri yi bdud rtsi mchog /
NK038(nyi)005:665: pany+tsa a mri ta dang sbyar //
NK038(nyi)005:666: gso ba'i mchog gi srog gi snying //
NK038(nyi)005:667: snying dang snying gi spun du bya'o //
NK038(nyi)005:668: ma h+aa pany+tsa sa ma ya +aah bdag gi lan gsum blangs /
NK038(nyi)005:669: tshogs bdag la lan gsum phul bas 'bral ba med pa'i grogs zhu'o //
NK038(nyi)005:670: zhes bdud rtsi rang gi gsum blangs /
NK038(nyi)005:672: ma h+aa mtsho gling sgrub gnas su //
NK038(nyi)005:673: rdo rje srin po'i spyan snga ru //
NK038(nyi)005:674: ji ltar khas blangs dam bcas pa'i //
NK038(nyi)005:675: dam tshig gnyen la ma 'da' cig /
NK038(nyi)005:677: de nas rak+ta las phud skyogs kyi logs su spyad la /
NK038(nyi)005:680: rje btsun rtsa ba dang brgyud par bcas pa'i dpal
NK038(nyi)005:681: ldan bla ma dam pa rnams kyi bka' bden pa
NK038(nyi)005:682: dang / bden pa chen pos byin gyis rlab ces
NK038(nyi)005:683: pa nas gnod byed dgra bgegs gang yin pa de
NK038(nyi)005:684: dag thams cad skyob byed kyi lha dang phrol la
NK038(nyi)005:685: dang / / mgon po'i sman raka 'di nyid kyi steng du mchis par gyur cig /
NK038(nyi)005:686: zhes rnga drag tu brdung zhing rak+ta gtor mar bran //
NK038(nyi)005:688: tshogs kyi bdag po mthu bo che //
NK038(nyi)005:689: bar snang khams su rgyu ba la //
NK038(nyi)005:690: bcom ldan rdo rje sems dpa' yis //
NK038(nyi)005:691: lag tu rdo rje sbyin pa ni //
NK038(nyi)005:692: rdo rje ming gi dbang bskur tshe //
NK038(nyi)005:693: sngar bcas gces kyang btag pa ste //
NK038(nyi)005:694: tshogs kyi bdag po chen por btags //
NK038(nyi)005:695: ma h+aa ka la mthu bo che //
NK038(nyi)005:697: bdag gi rten cing mchod pa la //
NK038(nyi)005:698: gzhung ba dang 'gal bzod par gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:699: phrin las nyams myong gsol ba ni //
NK038(nyi)005:700: lha'i dgra lha chen por gsol ba btab nas //
NK038(nyi)005:701: rnal 'byor yongs kyi pho nya zhal bzhes pa /
NK038(nyi)005:702: lha min dmag tshogs 'dul ba'i mthu rtsal can //
NK038(nyi)005:703: bdag gi bcol pa'i phrin las bsgrub par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:704: dam nyams dgra bgegs myur du bsgral du gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:705: rdo rje brag chen grag thang na //
NK038(nyi)005:706: gnyen pa'i tshul gyi bka' bsdod pa //
NK038(nyi)005:707: tsan dan dbyug pa sngon po yis //
NK038(nyi)005:708: khams gsum rdul du brlag mdzad pa'i //
NK038(nyi)005:709: khyed kyi thugs dam dus la babs //
NK038(nyi)005:710: bdag gi dgra bgegs tshogs la g.yul 'gyed na //
NK038(nyi)005:711: g.yul gyi mgon dang dpal du khyed gsol gyis //
NK038(nyi)005:712: log 'dren dgra bgegs myur du bsgral du gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:713: dam nyams dgra bgegs myur du bsgral du gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:714: bdag gi rgyal ba phyi rab mdzad du gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:715: dam tshig dbang gi lus dang grib ma bzhin //
NK038(nyi)005:716: 'grogs te bdag dang 'khor tshogs bsrung du gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:717: tshogs bdag khyed kyi 'khor tshogs kyis //
NK038(nyi)005:718: bka' nyan rnams kyi bdag la khram btab nas //
NK038(nyi)005:719: khram kha phyi zhing bar chad bzlog tu gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:720: tshe dang rdzu 'phrul mthu dang mngon shes dang //
NK038(nyi)005:721: rigs rgyud longs spyod chos kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK038(nyi)005:722: snying nas bstan pa bshig pa dang //
NK038(nyi)005:723: rdo rje slob dpon smad pa dang //
NK038(nyi)005:724: dam tshig gnyen po bral byed pa //
NK038(nyi)005:725: gsod cig choms shig bsgral du gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:728: rus pa klad pa nang rol zo //
NK038(nyi)005:729: bdun rgyud rtsad nas gcod par bgyi //
NK038(nyi)005:730: de nas lag tu thogs la /
NK038(nyi)005:731: ho dpal ma h+aa ka la tshogs kyi bdag po
NK038(nyi)005:732: 'dus pa chen po rnal 'byor pho mo'i tshogs dang
NK038(nyi)005:733: bcas pa thams cad la dgongs su gsol /
NK038(nyi)005:734: sngon bcom ldan 'das kyi 'khor nyams bsrungs ba zhal gyis bzhes pa de bzhin du /
NK038(nyi)005:735: lha'i mi mang po lha'i dgra lha chen por mnga' gsol te /
NK038(nyi)005:736: lha ma yin gyi g.yul bzlog /
NK038(nyi)005:737: glang po che sna smyon btul ba dang /
NK038(nyi)005:738: lha ma yin gyi bu mo nam mkha'i glog ma sprin gyi bzlar gyur pa rdul du brlag ste /
NK038(nyi)005:739: bgegs kyi rgyal po bi na ya ji ltar btul ba dang /
NK038(nyi)005:740: seng ge gza' chen gyi bu mo lta ba log ste dge slong ma'i bdud du gyur zhing /
NK038(nyi)005:741: nya sha mig go can gyi mgon po rtse gcig tu rten /
NK038(nyi)005:742: mchod cing sgrub nas thugs dam kyi rgyud bskul nas /
NK038(nyi)005:743: bstan pa bshig pa'i dam nyams che ge mo 'di nyid /
NK038(nyi)005:744: lo grangs dang zla grangs zhag du ma bzhag par /
NK038(nyi)005:745: rtags dang mtshan ma nyid du bsgral du gsol /
NK038(nyi)005:746: phan zhing gsol ba'i cho ga mdzod la bsngo ba
NK038(nyi)005:747: dang smon lam btab pa yid bzhin du 'grub ste
NK038(nyi)005:748: / bsam pa thams cad yid bzhin du 'grub par smon to ho /
NK038(nyi)005:750: 'di nas mnga' gsol bya ba ni //
NK038(nyi)005:752: bzhengs shig chos kyi dbyings nas bzhengs //
NK038(nyi)005:753: bskyod cig yum chen mkha' la bskyod //
NK038(nyi)005:754: gshegs shig sems can don la gshegs //
NK038(nyi)005:755: lha chen dpal 'bar gshegs su gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:756: chos skyong mgon po nag po la //
NK038(nyi)005:757: dkon mchog gsum gyis mnga' gsol ba'i //
NK038(nyi)005:758: sku yi cha lugs gsum dang ldan //
NK038(nyi)005:759: chos skyong dus gsum sangs rgyas khrims kyi cha lugs gsum dang ldan //
NK038(nyi)005:760: chos skyong rig gsum mgon pos //
NK038(nyi)005:761: brjid pa'i gzi mdangs gsum dang ldan //
NK038(nyi)005:762: chos skyongs khro bo rnams kyi zhal gyi khro gnyer gsum dang ldan //
NK038(nyi)005:764: lha chen brgyad kyi dbu skra kham nag thor tshugs can //
NK038(nyi)005:765: chos skyong klu chen brgyad kyi yan lag sbrul gyi tshom bus brgyan //
NK038(nyi)005:766: chos skyong sa bdag rnams kyi na bza' mthing ber nag po gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:768: zhing skyongs phyag na tsan dan beng chen bsnams //
NK038(nyi)005:770: gza' chen brgyad kyi brjid pa'i smin ma glog ltar 'khyug /
NK038(nyi)005:771: chos skyong rgyu skar rnams kyi sku smad rme ba'i dub bus brgyan //
NK038(nyi)005:772: chos skyong gshin rje rnams kyi spyan nas bskal pa'i me chen 'bar /
NK038(nyi)005:773: shangs nas bskal pa'i rlung chen tshub //
NK038(nyi)005:774: zhal nas bskal pa'i chu chen 'bab //
NK038(nyi)005:776: ma mo rnams kyi chags chen rak+ta'i thig les brgyan //
NK038(nyi)005:777: chos skyong byin chen rnams kyis zhag gi zor ris gsum dang ldan //
NK038(nyi)005:778: chos skyongs yi dwags rnams kyi rin chen 'bar ba'i thod khyer can //
NK038(nyi)005:779: chos skyong pho nya lhag pa'i thal chen tshom bus brgyan //
NK038(nyi)005:780: chos skyong srin po rnams kyi thod rlon phreng ba'i do shal can //
NK038(nyi)005:781: lha chen mgon po mnga' gsol lo //
NK038(nyi)005:782: mgon po'i thugs dam chos la mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:783: mgon po'i yid chags bskor la mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:784: mgon po'i phrin las dgra bgegs sgrol //
NK038(nyi)005:785: mgon po'i thugs dam brgyud bskul lo //
NK038(nyi)005:787: de nas bar gdangs bar gdangs dang ldan pas tshig gis /
NK038(nyi)005:789: ma srin gnyen gyi thugs dam bskul //
NK038(nyi)005:790: gtsug tor dkar mo sku yi yum //
NK038(nyi)005:791: a t+ya lam so gsung gi yum //
NK038(nyi)005:792: rdo rje rgyal mo thugs kyi yum //
NK038(nyi)005:793: lam b+ham d+ha ra yon tan yum //
NK038(nyi)005:794: byi d+ha ra ni las kyi yum //
NK038(nyi)005:795: u gtsug ma ni 'od kyi yum //
NK038(nyi)005:796: dkar sha pa ni phrin las yum //
NK038(nyi)005:797: kang ka pa ni pho nya'i yum //
NK038(nyi)005:798: lha chen mgon po thugs dam can //
NK038(nyi)005:799: dmar gyi mchod gtor 'di bzhes la //
NK038(nyi)005:800: sangs rgyas bstan pa'i bka' bsrung mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:801: gtsug lag khang gi bdag po mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:802: bdud 'dul yongs kyi dmag dpon mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:803: gza' chen dgra yi gshed ma mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:804: gzugs med bgegs kyi cha shan mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:805: bdag cag 'khor rig 'dzin srog shing mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:806: dug gsum nad gyi sman pa mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:807: rnal 'byor yongs kyi dgra lha mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:808: bdag gis bsam pa 'grub par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:809: bsam pa'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:810: zhes rol mo chem brdung bya //
NK038(nyi)005:811: de nas bskang gso 'bring po ni //
NK038(nyi)005:813: yon tan lhun rdzogs dngos grub mnga' ba'i lha //
NK038(nyi)005:814: ma lus rmad byung phan bde'i dgongs pa can //
NK038(nyi)005:815: phrin las rnam bzhis gdug pa tshar gcod pa'i //
NK038(nyi)005:816: legs ldan nag po 'khor bcas dgongs su gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:817: rol tshig sku gsung thugs dang yon tan phrin las kyis //
NK038(nyi)005:818: spyi dang khyad par lhag pa'i dam tshig can //
NK038(nyi)005:819: dam rdzas bzhin du tshul bzhin ma 'tshal ste //
NK038(nyi)005:820: khams gsum khyab pa'i sku la bzod par gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:822: thugs rje tshad med rin po che //
NK038(nyi)005:823: bla ma thams cad dgongs su gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:824: byin rlabs yi dam lha tshogs dngos grub dpa' bo
NK038(nyi)005:825: mkha' 'gro mthu stobs chos skyongs bsrung ma dgongs su
NK038(nyi)005:826: gsol // bdag cag dpon slob 'khor bcas kyi //
NK038(nyi)005:827: 'khor ba thog mtha' med pa nas //
NK038(nyi)005:828: bzung ste da lta'i bar du ni //
NK038(nyi)005:829: las dang nyon mongs dbang gyur te //
NK038(nyi)005:830: mtshams med lnga dang nye ba lnga //
NK038(nyi)005:831: mi dge bcu yi las bgyis dang //
NK038(nyi)005:832: bgyid du stsal dang yi rang ba //
NK038(nyi)005:833: nongs zhing 'gyod de mthol lo bshags //
NK038(nyi)005:834: dag cing gtsang bar mdzad du gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:835: so sor mthar pa'i sdom pa la //
NK038(nyi)005:836: 'gal zhing nyams pa ci mchis pa //
NK038(nyi)005:837: gnongs zhing 'gyod pas mthol lo bshags //
NK038(nyi)005:838: dag cing gtsang bar mdzad du gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:839: byang chub sems dpa'i bslab bya la //
NK038(nyi)005:840: 'gal zhing zhes sogs tshig rkang gsum 'dre //
NK038(nyi)005:841: gsang sngags dam tshig gnyen po la //
NK038(nyi)005:842: gzhan yang chos skyongs srung ma ni //
NK038(nyi)005:843: ma h+aa ka la 'khor dang bcas //
NK038(nyi)005:844: dpal ldan lha mo 'khor bcas kyi //
NK038(nyi)005:845: brten pa'i dam tshig bral ba'am //
NK038(nyi)005:846: bsrung ba'i dam tshig nyams pa'am //
NK038(nyi)005:847: za ba'i dam tshig chag pa'am //
NK038(nyi)005:849: mdor na yid la ci 'dod pa //
NK038(nyi)005:850: de kun de bzhin 'grub par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:851: dngos grub char rgyun dbab du gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:852: phrin las rnam bzhi bsgrub tu gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:853: mdor na yid la ci 'dod pa //
NK038(nyi)005:854: he ru ka dpal dpa' bo che //
NK038(nyi)005:855: rnam 'phrul bye ba mtha' yas pa //
NK038(nyi)005:856: dgra bgegs rdul du brlag mdzad pa'i //
NK038(nyi)005:857: mthu chen dpa' bo thugs dam bskang //
NK038(nyi)005:858: gzhan yang thugs dam bskang ba ni //
NK038(nyi)005:859: mtshan nyid ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK038(nyi)005:860: dam tshig ldan pa'i rnal 'byor du //
NK038(nyi)005:861: phyi nang mchod pa tshul bzhin bshams //
NK038(nyi)005:862: sha lnga dang ni bdud rtsi lnga //
NK038(nyi)005:863: 'bru bcud chang gi rgya mtsho dang //
NK038(nyi)005:864: 'dod yon rnam pa sna tshogs kyi //
NK038(nyi)005:865: bla ma dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams //
NK038(nyi)005:866: thugs dam gnyen po rtag tu bskangs //
NK038(nyi)005:867: dam tshig gnyen po bsre ba'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)005:868: bdud rtsi sman gyis thugs dam bskang //
NK038(nyi)005:869: shangs kyi dbang po tshim byed pa //
NK038(nyi)005:870: gsur chen dud pas thugs dam bskangs //
NK038(nyi)005:871: ljags kyi dbang po tshim byed pa'i //
NK038(nyi)005:872: mam sa rtsi bcud thugs dam bskang //
NK038(nyi)005:875: khrag gi ar+g+ham rtag tu mi 'bral 'grogs pa'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)005:876: rtags gtor gnyen po'i 'phral du phrin las grub pa'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)005:877: rgyun gyi gtor ma'i dgra bgegs chom la 'bebs pa'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)005:878: tsit+ta snying gi bya khyi lug nag rgyal mtshan dang //
NK038(nyi)005:879: lcam dral rnams kyi rtag par rten phyir nyams chag bskang phyir rnal 'byor rgyas phyir thugs dam bskang //
NK038(nyi)005:880: thugs dam bskang ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK038(nyi)005:881: phyi nang bar chad zhi ba dang //
NK038(nyi)005:882: bsam pa'i don kun 'grub par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:884: de nas bde chen 'du 'bral med pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK038(nyi)005:885: yang dag gsang ba'i sku gcig 'byung ba ni //
NK038(nyi)005:886: mthing nag mi bsrun 'jigs byed 'bar ba'i sku //
NK038(nyi)005:887: nyid kyi sku mdog mthing nag chen po la //
NK038(nyi)005:888: dbu skra kham nag ral pa gyen du 'khyil //
NK038(nyi)005:889: thabs dang shes rab nyi zla dbu la brgyan //
NK038(nyi)005:890: smin ma nag po khro gnyer brjid pa'i zhal //
NK038(nyi)005:891: spyan zlog zhal bsgrad mche ba rno tshig 'bar //
NK038(nyi)005:892: dam nyams log lta dgra bo'i srog rtsa gcod //
NK038(nyi)005:893: spyan nas me 'bar shangs nas lungs tshub ldang //
NK038(nyi)005:894: phyag gnyis thabs dang shes rab zung du 'brel //
NK038(nyi)005:895: g.yas pa'i phyag na tsan dan beng chen 'bar //
NK038(nyi)005:896: rab tu gsor zhing legs rten gdug pa 'dul //
NK038(nyi)005:897: g.yon pa'i phyag na par bu sku la brten //
NK038(nyi)005:898: dar ber sngo khra brjid pa sku la gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:899: gser ka rin chen 'bar ba sked la bcings //
NK038(nyi)005:900: zhabs gnyis brkyang bskum bsgrad pa'i tshul du bzhugs //
NK038(nyi)005:901: ma h+aa ka la'i tshogs ni sprin ltar thibs //
NK038(nyi)005:902: pho nya sprul pa'i tshogs ni skar ltar 'khrugs //
NK038(nyi)005:903: bstan pa bshig pa'i dam nyams rdul du rlog /
NK038(nyi)005:904: sdig chen dam nyams 'khor ba'i sems can gyi //
NK038(nyi)005:905: bstan pa bshig cing dkon mchog dbu 'phang smod //
NK038(nyi)005:906: dben gnas chom zhing gtsug lag bskor khang bshig /
NK038(nyi)005:907: rdo rje slob dpon sku la bsdo byed pa //
NK038(nyi)005:908: bsgral ba'i zhing du dam nyams 'di 'gyur ro //
NK038(nyi)005:909: pha rol phyin pa'i stobs kyi myur du sgrol //
NK038(nyi)005:910: rgyal ba'i spyan sngar ji ltar khas blangs pa'i //
NK038(nyi)005:911: bdag gi bcol pa'i phrin las 'grub par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:914: mgon po khyed mchod byin rlabs kyi //
NK038(nyi)005:915: phyogs bsam dus kun thams cad du //
NK038(nyi)005:916: sems can legs ston 'byor pa rnams //
NK038(nyi)005:917: bgegs kyi gnod pa kun med shog /
NK038(nyi)005:919: rta dang ba glang nor dang 'bru //
NK038(nyi)005:920: bu tsha pha ma gnyen shes rnams //
NK038(nyi)005:921: dge zhing tshe ring nad med par //
NK038(nyi)005:922: thams cad 'byor dang ldan par shog /
NK038(nyi)005:924: dgra bo nyes byas med 'gyur zhing //
NK038(nyi)005:925: nad dang mu ge kun bral shog /
NK038(nyi)005:926: rgyal po chos bzhin spyod pa yis //
NK038(nyi)005:927: chos kyi yul 'khor skyong bar shog /
NK038(nyi)005:928: bde bar gshegs pa'i bstan pa 'di //
NK038(nyi)005:929: phyogs dus kun tu dar ba dang //
NK038(nyi)005:930: myur du sems can thams cad kyis //
NK038(nyi)005:931: chos kyi snod du rung bar shog /
NK038(nyi)005:932: dge ba 'di yi thams cad rab bsngo zhing //
NK038(nyi)005:933: mgon po khyed mchod byin rlabs kyis //
NK038(nyi)005:934: bdag cag 'khor dang bcas pa rnams //
NK038(nyi)005:935: longs spyod rnam gnyis tshogs rdzogs nas //
NK038(nyi)005:936: bdag cag byang chub mchog thob nas //
NK038(nyi)005:938: zhes 'dod don gyi phrin las bcol //
NK038(nyi)005:939: dpal ye shes mgon po legs ldan nag po'i mchod phreng legs par bkod pa rdzogs so //////
NK038(nyi)005:940: dpal mgon legs ldan 'khor bcas kyi mchod phrin bstod bskul dang bcas pa bzhugs //
NK038(nyi)005:941: gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo rje la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)005:942: dpal mgon po'i bsnyen bsgrub kyi 'phrin las kyi rim pa la /
NK038(nyi)005:944: khro bo'i rgyal po gdong drug h'u sgra can //
NK038(nyi)005:945: yan lag drug ldan khro rgyal gshin rje'i gshed //
NK038(nyi)005:946: ye shes spyan gyis ma rig mun sel ba //
NK038(nyi)005:947: gtum chen gshin rje 'jom la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)005:948: yun gyi lhar yang khyod la gsol 'debs na //
NK038(nyi)005:949: dregs ldan stobs gzhom zil gyis mnan pa dang //
NK038(nyi)005:950: ma mo mkha' 'gro rnams la dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK038(nyi)005:951: nad gtong srin mo'i tshogs rnams las la bskul //
NK038(nyi)005:952: bstan pa bshig pa'i dgra bshegs thal bar rlogs //
NK038(nyi)005:953: khyed kyi thugs rjes bdag la byin gyis brlabs //
NK038(nyi)005:954: h+r+aih rgyal ba kun gyi chos sku pad+ma'i gdung //
NK038(nyi)005:955: chos rje 'od dpag med pa rdo rje'i chos //
NK038(nyi)005:956: spyan ras gzigs dbang h+r+ai las rngam chen sku //
NK038(nyi)005:957: rta mgrin rta skad bzhad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)005:958: ngag gi dbang phyug rta gdong zhal gyis gnon //
NK038(nyi)005:959: rdo rje rta yi stabs bdun gyis //
NK038(nyi)005:961: 'jig rten dregs pa gtum pa'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:962: rdo rje rtog pa'i bya sgron gyis //
NK038(nyi)005:963: snang mdzad ngag gi dbang phyug sku //
NK038(nyi)005:964: byang chub chen po cang shes gtso //
NK038(nyi)005:965: stobs chen dgu yi rdzu 'phrul gyis //
NK038(nyi)005:966: rdo rje rta gdong sprul pa'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:967: nam mkha'i khams kun gang bar mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:968: 'khor ba ma grol bar du ni /
NK038(nyi)005:969: snying rje'i go cha ma brjed par //
NK038(nyi)005:970: 'khor ba'i so mtha' mchod bar bzhes //
NK038(nyi)005:972: rgyal ba kun gyi gsang 'dzin pa //
NK038(nyi)005:973: thugs mchog bdag po'i rdo rje 'dzin //
NK038(nyi)005:974: drag po rtul shugs chen po yis //
NK038(nyi)005:975: dpa' bo 'jig rten gsum las rgyal //
NK038(nyi)005:976: sngon gyi go cha chen po yis //
NK038(nyi)005:977: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK038(nyi)005:979: bdud kyi bdud sde bdud rnams 'joms /
NK038(nyi)005:980: sems dpa' chen po 'bar ba'i sku //
NK038(nyi)005:981: 'jigs su rung dang dpa' byad can //
NK038(nyi)005:982: gtum rngams 'khrugs pa'i ngo bo yis //
NK038(nyi)005:983: dur khrod bdag po rab tu choms //
NK038(nyi)005:984: bdag nyid lhar gsal ba'i thugs ka nas /
NK038(nyi)005:985: b+h+rum gyi gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa bskyed /
NK038(nyi)005:986: der mgon po yab yum 'khor dang bcas pa rgyud
NK038(nyi)005:987: kyi le'u dgu pa'am bco lnga pa nas byung ba
NK038(nyi)005:988: bzhin bskyed do // de nas gsang ba'i rnga brdungs la spyan drangs te /
NK038(nyi)005:989: b+h+rum bi shwa bishud+d+he ban+d+ha ka p+aa la man+da la b+h+rum /
NK038(nyi)005:990: na ra bam byi tri ta ya bam dun b+h+yoh h'u /
NK038(nyi)005:991: lang ka yul gyi grong rdal gyi //
NK038(nyi)005:992: dbus kyi ri bo ma la ya //
NK038(nyi)005:993: ko ka thang dmar rgya mtsho'i do //
NK038(nyi)005:995: drag shul yod pa'i rtse mo na //
NK038(nyi)005:996: rdo rje thabs kyi blta ba'i yum //
NK038(nyi)005:997: chos 'dzin rigs kyi bsgrub gnas su //
NK038(nyi)005:998: dpal chen rdo rje srin po yis //
NK038(nyi)005:999: bdud kyi rigs rnams btul nas ni //
NK038(nyi)005:1000: gsang sngags 'khor lo bskor ba'i tshe //
NK038(nyi)005:1001: ming gi dbang bskur bran tu khas blangs pa'i //
NK038(nyi)005:1002: rdo rje ro langs dur khrod tshogs kyi bdag /
NK038(nyi)005:1003: dpal mgon nag po chen po dang //
NK038(nyi)005:1004: nye gnas kro ti shwa ri ma //
NK038(nyi)005:1005: yab yum gnyis su med pa'i 'khor //
NK038(nyi)005:1006: lang ka'i bdag po la sogs pa'i //
NK038(nyi)005:1008: pho mo 'khor dang bcas pa rnams //
NK038(nyi)005:1009: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung ba'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)005:1011: bur kur ma h+aa ka la rak+mo kro ti shwa
NK038(nyi)005:1012: ri nag mo ting lam ma e a re li
NK038(nyi)005:1013: hrim hrim dza dzah rak+sha sh+ri he ru ka bi
NK038(nyi)005:1014: shwa kro ta dz+wa la man+dala phata phatah ha la
NK038(nyi)005:1015: ha la h'u phatah ta kem ta kem phata ha
NK038(nyi)005:1019: badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha ha ha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi h'u h'u h'u /
NK038(nyi)005:1020: sa ma ya man+dala ma su kha h'u /
NK038(nyi)005:1021: pra be sha pha tah ma h+aa ka ma b+h+rum /
NK038(nyi)005:1022: badz+ra a mri ta ma h+aa kro d+ha am am am /
NK038(nyi)005:1023: e a ra li dza dza /
NK038(nyi)005:1024: e ma dpa' bo thugs rje chung //
NK038(nyi)005:1025: shin tu sde ba'i lto khyim nas //
NK038(nyi)005:1026: snam du bton pas bdag khang gi //
NK038(nyi)005:1027: da yang ci mdzad myur du mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:1028: myur du bsgral na yun du bde //
NK038(nyi)005:1030: 'bangs la nan tan ma chung cig /
NK038(nyi)005:1031: slan cad bka' bzhin rjes su bgyid //
NK038(nyi)005:1032: gal te bka' bzhin ma bgyis shing //
NK038(nyi)005:1033: dam pa'i lung las 'gal gyur na //
NK038(nyi)005:1034: bdag cag rnams kyi mgo lus snying //
NK038(nyi)005:1035: rul myags tshig nas skam gyur cig /
NK038(nyi)005:1036: i dan te na ra kan //
NK038(nyi)005:1039: sa ma ya rak+sha si d+hi bin badz+ra //
NK038(nyi)005:1040: a mri ba kro ta na ra kan //
NK038(nyi)005:1041: ma sring bu mo chung ma'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1043: e pad+ma pra be sha phatah badz+ra kha tham kha tham //
NK038(nyi)005:1044: pra be sha phata phatah dbus su mchis skal mi ldan gyi //
NK038(nyi)005:1046: phud la 'chis skal mi ldan gyis /
NK038(nyi)005:1047: lhag ma zhal chab bran la gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:1049: nye gnas gdung ba'i ma sring rnams //
NK038(nyi)005:1050: ding nas rgyal ba'i bka' yin gyis //
NK038(nyi)005:1051: khyod kyi bka' yi las mkhan te //
NK038(nyi)005:1052: bka'i las rnams myur du sgrubs //
NK038(nyi)005:1053: bdag dang de sngon las log spyad pa'i mthus //
NK038(nyi)005:1054: dpag tu med par 'khor ba'i sdug sngal rgyud //
NK038(nyi)005:1055: da yang thugs rje las 'phro gnyis 'phrad pas //
NK038(nyi)005:1056: bde ba can gyi zhing du myur 'gro yis //
NK038(nyi)005:1057: sring la sogs te dregs pa pho mo'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1058: rjes su bstan pa'i bka' las nyams pa re //
NK038(nyi)005:1059: ji ltar ma byams bu la gdung ba bzhin //
NK038(nyi)005:1060: dam tshig can la dung dung gdung ba bzhin //
NK038(nyi)005:1061: gang zhig sring byams ming la brtse ba bzhin //
NK038(nyi)005:1062: yal gam can la lhang lhang brtse bar gyis //
NK038(nyi)005:1063: mdza' bo grogs la ji ltar gdung tshul bzhin //
NK038(nyi)005:1064: rnal 'byor can la skrig krig gdung bar mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:1065: ji ltar g.yog byams dpon la khur ba bzhin //
NK038(nyi)005:1066: dam pa rnams la yid bzhin nor bur khur //
NK038(nyi)005:1067: khyed brtse bar byed na mar bya'o //
NK038(nyi)005:1068: gdung bar byed na sring mor byed do //
NK038(nyi)005:1069: 'du bral med na sring mor bya'o //
NK038(nyi)005:1070: dam la gnas na slob mar bya'o //
NK038(nyi)005:1071: bskul bar mgyogs na pho nyar bya'o //
NK038(nyi)005:1072: bka' bzhin byed na bka' las brtags //
NK038(nyi)005:1073: ru lu ru lu b+h+yo sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK038(nyi)005:1074: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK038(nyi)005:1076: sngon tshe dpal chen khro bo'i rgyal //
NK038(nyi)005:1077: bdud 'dul rdo rje srin po yis //
NK038(nyi)005:1078: dregs pa bcom nas sgrib pa sbyangs //
NK038(nyi)005:1079: dbang bskur ming btags srog yig phul //
NK038(nyi)005:1080: pho brang kun la dam tshig sbyin //
NK038(nyi)005:1081: bstan pa yongs su bsrung bar byas //
NK038(nyi)005:1082: phyi yi mtshan nas bos pa'i tshe //
NK038(nyi)005:1083: dpal mgon legs ldan nag po bya //
NK038(nyi)005:1084: nang gi mtshan nas bos pa'i tshe //
NK038(nyi)005:1085: bdud 'dul dur khrod sgrol ba'i gying //
NK038(nyi)005:1086: gsang ba'i mtshan nas bos pa'i tshe //
NK038(nyi)005:1087: sgrol byed rdo rje drag po rtsal //
NK038(nyi)005:1088: mna' bor khas blangs ma bsnyel bar //
NK038(nyi)005:1089: rnal 'byor bcol pa'i phrin las mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:1090: sku gsung thugs su bdag sbyor ba'i //
NK038(nyi)005:1091: pho brang da la nga bdag 'dir //
NK038(nyi)005:1092: dpal mgon dregs pa'i tshogs rnams kun //
NK038(nyi)005:1093: rtag tu dam tshig tshul bzhin gyis //
NK038(nyi)005:1094: +aah h'u badz+ra a mri ta ya hi hi sarba man h'u h+r+ai tha /
NK038(nyi)005:1095: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wamh h'u /
NK038(nyi)005:1096: bka' dang bstan pa bsrung bar zhal bzhes pa'i //
NK038(nyi)005:1097: bdud 'dul dbang phyug ma h+aa ka la'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1098: sring yul nag po lang+ka pu ru yis //
NK038(nyi)005:1099: grong khyer bstan nas rlag mdzad cing //
NK038(nyi)005:1100: lha ma yin gyi bu mo ni //
NK038(nyi)005:1101: glog sprin 'dul bar dam bcas pa'i //
NK038(nyi)005:1102: lha chen mgon po nag po khyod //
NK038(nyi)005:1104: rdo rje srin po'i spyan snga ru //
NK038(nyi)005:1105: khas blangs dam bca' ma snyel bar //
NK038(nyi)005:1106: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK038(nyi)005:1107: rnal 'byor bcol pa'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:1109: b+hur kur ma h+aa ka la //
NK038(nyi)005:1110: rak+moo kro ti shwa ri nag mo ting lam sa ma ya stam /
NK038(nyi)005:1111: tish+tha badz+ra rnal 'byor bstan pa bsrung bar zhal bzhes pa'i /
NK038(nyi)005:1112: dpal ldan mgon po 'khor dang bcas pa la //
NK038(nyi)005:1113: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK038(nyi)005:1114: mthu dang rtsal gyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:1115: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)005:1116: rak+mo kro d+hi shwa ri ting lam ma ma h+aa pany+tsa mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)005:1117: kro ta kro bo ging gi tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1118: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri yak+sha gnod sbyin dregs pa'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1119: ma h+aa pany+tsa rak+sha srin po rngam pa'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1120: ma h+aa tsit+ta za byed ma mo'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1121: ma h+aa nye gnas gdung ba'i ma sring brgyad //
NK038(nyi)005:1122: ma h+aa gus pa'i bu mo chen mo brgyad //
NK038(nyi)005:1123: ma h+aa dur khrod gnas pa'i sgo bsrungs bzhi //
NK038(nyi)005:1124: ma h+aa dur khrod bdag po gru 'debs bzhi //
NK038(nyi)005:1125: ma h+aa srin mo chen mo nyi shu brgyad //
NK038(nyi)005:1127: lcang lor bcas pa'i ma h+aa b+han+d+ha ru //
NK038(nyi)005:1128: byang chub sems dang ma h+aa rat+na dang //
NK038(nyi)005:1129: dri chen ku ku chu de rnam pa lnga //
NK038(nyi)005:1130: gnyis med sbyar ba'i pany+tsa a mri ta //
NK038(nyi)005:1131: nag po chen po 'khor dang bcas la 'bul //
NK038(nyi)005:1133: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)005:1143: tshogs kyi bdag po mthu bo che //
NK038(nyi)005:1144: bar snang khams na bzhugs pa'i tshe //
NK038(nyi)005:1145: bcom ldan rdo rje sems dpa' yis //
NK038(nyi)005:1146: lag tu rdo rje byin nas ni //
NK038(nyi)005:1147: dbang bskur ming btags mtshan gsol ba //
NK038(nyi)005:1148: ma h+aa k+aa la ma rung pa //
NK038(nyi)005:1149: tshogs bdag rdo rje phreng ba can //
NK038(nyi)005:1150: bdag gi bsnyen cing bos pa'i tshe //
NK038(nyi)005:1151: dam rdzas mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK038(nyi)005:1152: phrin las snyan snyung gsol ba 'di //
NK038(nyi)005:1153: lha yi dgra lha chen por mtshan gsol nas //
NK038(nyi)005:1154: lha min dmag tshogs 'dul ba'i mthu bo che //
NK038(nyi)005:1155: gnod cing gdug pa'i dgra bgegs rdul du rlogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1156: sku la tshem khrab nag po gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:1157: g.yas pas gsal shing dgra la phyar //
NK038(nyi)005:1158: g.yon pa gshan rti mdung ring bsnams //
NK038(nyi)005:1159: rtse mo mi rkang gzhog pa rtsal //
NK038(nyi)005:1160: zhal gdangs mche gtsig thog ser 'bebs //
NK038(nyi)005:1162: khyod kyi dge mtshan ci yang ma nges te //
NK038(nyi)005:1163: kun bzang lha yi spyan snga ru //
NK038(nyi)005:1164: nyid kyi thugs dam zhal bzhes pa'i //
NK038(nyi)005:1165: khas blangs dam pa snyel lam ci //
NK038(nyi)005:1166: dam bca' bzhin tu 'phrin las mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:1167: nye gnas kro ti shwa ri ma //
NK038(nyi)005:1168: dam rdzas mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK038(nyi)005:1169: da yang bcol pa'i phrin las mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:1170: srin mo nye gnas brgyad rnams kyang //
NK038(nyi)005:1171: dam rdzas mchod pa da yang bcol pa'i gus pa'i bu mo chen mo brgyad /
NK038(nyi)005:1172: dam rdzas da yang dur khrod gru 'debs bzhi rnams kyang //
NK038(nyi)005:1173: dam rdzas da yang ma h+aa k+aa la drag rtsal can //
NK038(nyi)005:1174: tshogs bdag mgon po 'khor dang bcas //
NK038(nyi)005:1175: yang dag don gyi srung ma thugs dam can //
NK038(nyi)005:1176: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung bar zhal bzhes pa'i //
NK038(nyi)005:1177: dpal mgon legs ldan nag po bdud kyi rje //
NK038(nyi)005:1178: gsang mtshan rdo rje ro langs te //
NK038(nyi)005:1179: nye gnas kro ti shwa ri ma //
NK038(nyi)005:1180: dam rdzas mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK038(nyi)005:1181: bcol pa'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:1182: 'khor gyi gnod sbyin sde bzhi thugs dam can //
NK038(nyi)005:1183: kro ti shwa ri khro bo ging gi tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1184: yak+sha gnod sbyin dregs pa'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1185: rak+sha srin po rngam pa'i tshogs /
NK038(nyi)005:1186: tsit+ta za byed ma mo'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1187: dam rdzas sangs rgyas bstan pa gnyen po bsrungs //
NK038(nyi)005:1188: bka' bsdod las kyi bshan pa gying //
NK038(nyi)005:1189: nag po gri gug thod pa 'dzin //
NK038(nyi)005:1190: khyod ni bka' yi las mkhan te //
NK038(nyi)005:1191: dam nyams dgra bgeg sgrol ba'i gying //
NK038(nyi)005:1192: dam rdzas bstan pa'i dgra bgegs myur du sgrol //
NK038(nyi)005:1193: dpal mgon legs ldan nag po 'khor dang bcas pa la //
NK038(nyi)005:1194: dam rdzas bdud rtsi'i rdzas mchod 'bul //
NK038(nyi)005:1195: bla med mchod pa dam pa 'di bzhes la //
NK038(nyi)005:1196: bskang ngo dgra srog chod la shog /
NK038(nyi)005:1197: dam nyams las mkhan dgra bo 'di //
NK038(nyi)005:1198: ma thogs myur du khug la shog /
NK038(nyi)005:1199: mgo dang yan lag breg la shog /
NK038(nyi)005:1200: snying dang dbang po phyung la shog /
NK038(nyi)005:1201: lnga phung yan lag rdul du rlog /
NK038(nyi)005:1202: 'di la byang chub sems med kyis //
NK038(nyi)005:1203: ma thogs myur du sgrol la shog /
NK038(nyi)005:1204: sngon tshe khas blangs dam las khyed ma 'da' //
NK038(nyi)005:1205: rnal 'byor bcol pa'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:1206: bur kur ma h+aa ka la rak+mo krod+hi shwa ri
NK038(nyi)005:1207: nag mo ting lam ma ma h+aa mam sa kh+aa
NK038(nyi)005:1210: go ro tsa na kem ni ri ti /
NK038(nyi)005:1213: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha kha /
NK038(nyi)005:1215: kro ta dz+wa la sa ma ya /
NK038(nyi)005:1218: ma h+aa mam sa tsit+ta dz+wa la /
NK038(nyi)005:1219: ma h+aa mam sa de wa a ra dz+wa la sa ma ya /
NK038(nyi)005:1221: rnal 'byor yongs kyi dpal mgon mchog /
NK038(nyi)005:1222: ma h+aa ka la mthu rtsal can //
NK038(nyi)005:1223: rig 'dzin yongs kyi srog shing yin //
NK038(nyi)005:1225: dregs can yongs kyi dbang phyug yin //
NK038(nyi)005:1226: sngags 'chang yongs kyi dgra bla yin //
NK038(nyi)005:1227: chos skyong yongs kyi rje bo yin //
NK038(nyi)005:1228: dgra bgegs yongs kyi gshed ma yin //
NK038(nyi)005:1229: bdag gis bsrung mar mnga' gsol gyi //
NK038(nyi)005:1230: dam rdzas mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK038(nyi)005:1231: bdag cag 'khor dang bcas rnams la //
NK038(nyi)005:1232: gnod cing sdang sems ldan pa 'di //
NK038(nyi)005:1233: nad dang mtshon gyi char phob sod //
NK038(nyi)005:1234: bdud dang srin po'i dmag drangs la //
NK038(nyi)005:1235: rtsa rgyud rtsad nas rlag par gyis //
NK038(nyi)005:1236: bdag gi 'khor dang chos la sogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1237: longs spyod zas nor khyod kyi srungs //
NK038(nyi)005:1238: ho dpal mgon po nag po /
NK038(nyi)005:1245: srin po nag po bya'i gshog pa can mthing nag
NK038(nyi)005:1246: chen po phyag na tsan dan gyi beng chen thogs
NK038(nyi)005:1247: pa / byang phyogs gnod sbyin chen po brgyad phyi nas 'brang zhing /
NK038(nyi)005:1248: lho phyogs gshin rje brgyad sngon rol zhing sna 'dren pa /
NK038(nyi)005:1249: tshogs chen po bzhi'i mnga' bdag /
NK038(nyi)005:1250: mon pa chen po dang mon mo'i tshogs la dbang bsgyur ba /
NK038(nyi)005:1251: khyod kyi bka' dang bstan pa bsrung bar gyis shig /
NK038(nyi)005:1254: thugs rje'i mthu stobs dgra 'joms sku lnga po //
NK038(nyi)005:1255: sangs rgyas kun gyi bka' yi las mkhan te //
NK038(nyi)005:1256: dpal mgon ljang sngon drag po gsal shing can //
NK038(nyi)005:1257: khyod kyi bstan pa bshig pa bsgral slad du //
NK038(nyi)005:1258: gnas 'dir 'dug la bka' yi dam tshig srungs //
NK038(nyi)005:1259: bsgrub pa'i grogs kyi dgra la rtags chen phyung //
NK038(nyi)005:1260: bur kur ma h+aa pad+ma kro ti shwa ri rnge
NK038(nyi)005:1261: bur phyi ge bi ma na se e o shwa
NK038(nyi)005:1262: mo kro d+ha h'u h'u h'u phata phata phata s+w+aa
NK038(nyi)005:1263: h+aa / bur kur ma a pra na bur tsi
NK038(nyi)005:1264: ki tsi ma na s+ya kha shwa mo krod+ha h'u
NK038(nyi)005:1265: h'u phata phatah bur kur i tsi ki tsi u
NK038(nyi)005:1266: tsut+ma kro d+ha h'u phatah bur kur ti phata sarba
NK038(nyi)005:1267: sid+hi phatah drag po sku lnga rgyal ba'i bka' sdod
NK038(nyi)005:1268: h+aa / mchog / ye shes lnga ldan rgyal ba rigs lnga'i 'khor //
NK038(nyi)005:1269: 'phrin las bdud 'dul dgra bgegs kun gyi gshed //
NK038(nyi)005:1270: gnas 'di tshur spyon gnas 'dir phrin las mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:1271: sa ma ya dzah dzah k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta sid+d+hi h'u /
NK038(nyi)005:1272: dpal mgon yab yum 'khor dang bcas pa la //
NK038(nyi)005:1273: bsnyen bsgrub tshul bzhin du phul bas //
NK038(nyi)005:1274: bdag cag rdo rje slob dpon mched dang lcam dral rnams la /
NK038(nyi)005:1280: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub thams cad /
NK038(nyi)005:1281: dus dang las la ma stos par dus da lta nyid du thob par stsal du gsol /
NK038(nyi)005:1283: nyi ma lho nub ya gi na //
NK038(nyi)005:1284: srin yul pu ra nag po'i dkyil //
NK038(nyi)005:1285: lang ka yul gyi grong brdal na //
NK038(nyi)005:1286: ko ka thang dmar rgya mtsho'i do //
NK038(nyi)005:1287: drag shul byan slag chongs kyi ri //
NK038(nyi)005:1288: gnam lcags yod pa'i rtse mo nas //
NK038(nyi)005:1289: chos 'dzin rigs kyi bsgrub gnas te //
NK038(nyi)005:1290: rdo rje thabs kyi lta ba'i yum //
NK038(nyi)005:1291: dug shing nags tshal gtams pa'i tshal //
NK038(nyi)005:1292: gnam lcags ur mo char bzhin 'bab //
NK038(nyi)005:1293: gsur chen dud pa sprin ltar thibs /
NK038(nyi)005:1294: rnag khrag chu ser mtsho ltar skyil //
NK038(nyi)005:1295: sha rus phung po ri ltar spungs //
NK038(nyi)005:1297: bya gcan mang po lding bzhin 'dzum //
NK038(nyi)005:1298: mon pa sha za gri thogs 'bum //
NK038(nyi)005:1299: mon mo khrag 'thung bsam mi khyab //
NK038(nyi)005:1300: lha srin sde brgyad srog la rngams //
NK038(nyi)005:1302: rab tu 'jigs pa'i yul khams na //
NK038(nyi)005:1303: 'jigs pa'i thod mkhar ldems se ldem //
NK038(nyi)005:1304: shar phyogs bam chen stag thod mkhar //
NK038(nyi)005:1305: stag gi brang yang nye re re //
NK038(nyi)005:1306: lho phyogs bam rim mi thod mkhar //
NK038(nyi)005:1307: mi thod spyi glu rtse re re //
NK038(nyi)005:1308: nub phyogs bam chen rta thod mkhar //
NK038(nyi)005:1309: rta thod mtsher gdangs lhangs se lhang /
NK038(nyi)005:1310: byang phyogs bam ril bya thod mkhar //
NK038(nyi)005:1311: bya thod tsher sgra di ri ri //
NK038(nyi)005:1312: srin po'i thod pas kha bad can //
NK038(nyi)005:1314: ngos la nga rgyal glog dmar 'khyug /
NK038(nyi)005:1315: rtse la bdud bya nag po lding //
NK038(nyi)005:1316: ru mtshon nag po pu ru ru //
NK038(nyi)005:1317: gnam lcags 'bar ba'i sgo mo gsal //
NK038(nyi)005:1318: 'jigs pa'i sku mkhar nang shed na //
NK038(nyi)005:1319: rta ro mang po gcal du bkram //
NK038(nyi)005:1320: mi ro mang po grums su brtsigs //
NK038(nyi)005:1321: mi ro rta ro'i gdan stengs na //
NK038(nyi)005:1322: mnga' bdag bdud kyi rgyal po che //
NK038(nyi)005:1323: gsang bdag phyag na rdo rje yis //
NK038(nyi)005:1324: 'phrin las drag por dbang bskur ba //
NK038(nyi)005:1325: zhal gsum 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK038(nyi)005:1326: sku mdog dbus zhal ljang nag brjid //
NK038(nyi)005:1327: g.yas ser thugs rjes 'gro ba skyob //
NK038(nyi)005:1328: g.yon dmar dbang sdud chags pas 'gugs //
NK038(nyi)005:1329: dmar nag ral pa srid rtser 'bar //
NK038(nyi)005:1330: ral pa sprugs pa'i skra gseb nas //
NK038(nyi)005:1331: gnam lcags thog ser skar ltar 'khrug /
NK038(nyi)005:1332: shangs rlung nad kyi bskal pa 'tshub mar ston //
NK038(nyi)005:1333: zhal gdangs dbang gi mche ba gtsigs //
NK038(nyi)005:1334: rngam pa'i nga ro 'brug ltar sgrog /
NK038(nyi)005:1335: drag po'i rkan sgra bdud la 'debs //
NK038(nyi)005:1337: gdug pa'i mtshon cha ma lus 'phro //
NK038(nyi)005:1338: drag po'i phyag drug gdengs pa las //
NK038(nyi)005:1339: g.yas kyi dang po gsal shing gis //
NK038(nyi)005:1340: srid pa gsum char thal bar rlog /
NK038(nyi)005:1341: bar pa rdo rje gsor zhing 'phyar //
NK038(nyi)005:1342: dgra bgegs mgo lus tshar par gshog /
NK038(nyi)005:1343: tha ma gnam lcags phur pa 'debs //
NK038(nyi)005:1344: dmigs pa'i snying la gzer chen thob //
NK038(nyi)005:1345: g.yon pa'i dang po dung chen du //
NK038(nyi)005:1346: srid gsum snying khrag byung zhing 'thung //
NK038(nyi)005:1347: bar pa rno dbal shan gyi mdung //
NK038(nyi)005:1348: zhing bcu'i snying la gzer chen 'debs //
NK038(nyi)005:1349: tha ma sbrul zhags nag po yis //
NK038(nyi)005:1352: 'dod chags zhing lpags stod g.yogs shing //
NK038(nyi)005:1353: gti mug glang chen lpags pa gyon //
NK038(nyi)005:1354: zhe sdang stag gi sham thabs la //
NK038(nyi)005:1355: gdug pa sbrul gyi ska rags bcings //
NK038(nyi)005:1356: thod sbrul thal zhag rak+tasa brgyan //
NK038(nyi)005:1357: gdug rtsub me yi nang na bzhugs //
NK038(nyi)005:1359: sngoon gyi dam bca' ma snyel bar //
NK038(nyi)005:1360: bcol pa'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:1361: b+h+yo g.yon gyi phyogs na sku sprul pa //
NK038(nyi)005:1362: nye gnas kro ti shwa ri ma /
NK038(nyi)005:1363: gtum mo chen mo 'jigs gzugs can //
NK038(nyi)005:1364: zhal gcig phyag gnyis 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NK038(nyi)005:1365: khrag ral nag mo mun ltar 'thibs //
NK038(nyi)005:1366: sku stod zhing gi g.yang gzhi la //
NK038(nyi)005:1368: sku smad stag lpags re lde la //
NK038(nyi)005:1369: sbrul nag chu srin thod pas brgyan //
NK038(nyi)005:1370: g.yas pa sbrul zhags yab la 'khyud //
NK038(nyi)005:1371: g.yon pa thod skyogs khrag gi bkang //
NK038(nyi)005:1372: rus bcud rkang mar klad khrag rnams //
NK038(nyi)005:1373: 'bru mar chang gi sbyar ba dag /
NK038(nyi)005:1374: rtag par rang gi longs spyod byed //
NK038(nyi)005:1375: yab la bstab cing dgra la 'phen //
NK038(nyi)005:1376: sngon gyi dam bca' ma snyel bar //
NK038(nyi)005:1377: bcol pa'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:1378: b+h+yo che mchog thugs kyi sprul pa ni //
NK038(nyi)005:1379: las kyi mgon po nag po bzhengs //
NK038(nyi)005:1380: zhal gcig phyag gnyis gcer bu'i sku //
NK038(nyi)005:1381: g.yas pa gri gug sngon po 'dar //
NK038(nyi)005:1383: zhabs gnyis dam nyams steng na bgrad //
NK038(nyi)005:1385: lha srin sde brgyad bran du khol //
NK038(nyi)005:1386: dam nyams dgra bo las ngan 'di //
NK038(nyi)005:1387: sho ra re'o ma btang cig /
NK038(nyi)005:1388: ched 'ga' drag tu bskul ba'i tshe //
NK038(nyi)005:1389: rab tu byung ba'i cha byad can //
NK038(nyi)005:1390: g.yas pas sreg shing g.yon pa na //
NK038(nyi)005:1391: bdud kyi spar bu nag po thogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1392: chos gos nag po phyir log gon //
NK038(nyi)005:1393: chos kyi glegs bam khur du khur //
NK038(nyi)005:1394: drag po'i sngags bzlos di ri ri //
NK038(nyi)005:1395: longs spyod mi snying dmar la byed //
NK038(nyi)005:1396: dam nyams sho ra re'o mched 'ga' de yi thugs kyi dges sde mo //
NK038(nyi)005:1397: byang shar mtshams na gnas bcas pa'i //
NK038(nyi)005:1398: snang mdzad mi g.yo gtsug tor can //
NK038(nyi)005:1399: skam ma chu 'jig khros pa'i tshe //
NK038(nyi)005:1400: phyag na rdo rje'i bka' sdod pho nya mo //
NK038(nyi)005:1401: 'khor gyi ma mo 'bum phrag las la bskul //
NK038(nyi)005:1402: dam nyams shwo ra re'o ched 'ga' mthing nag dar gyi 'jol ber can //
NK038(nyi)005:1403: chu dar ljang khu thod du bcings //
NK038(nyi)005:1404: tsan dan smug po'i gying beng can //
NK038(nyi)005:1405: khros pa'i cha byad chen po yis //
NK038(nyi)005:1406: dam nyams sho ra re'o ched 'ga' gcer bu kham nag ral pa can //
NK038(nyi)005:1407: kha nas khrag 'dzag thod phreng can //
NK038(nyi)005:1408: mig nas me yi phung po 'bar //
NK038(nyi)005:1409: g.yas pa me dpung 'bar bas bsreg /
NK038(nyi)005:1410: g.yon pa lcags kyu'i don snying 'byin //
NK038(nyi)005:1411: mi ro rlon pa'i gdan la bzhugs //
NK038(nyi)005:1412: dam nyams sho ra re'o ched 'ga' gdong bzhi gdong nag thod phreng can //
NK038(nyi)005:1413: nag po ral can tshig cing 'phro //
NK038(nyi)005:1414: phyag bzhi gdengs pa'i cho 'phrul lag /
NK038(nyi)005:1415: zhabs bzhi zhabs gnyis rdzu 'phrul rkang //
NK038(nyi)005:1416: g.yas kyi dang po gri gug 'debs //
NK038(nyi)005:1417: 'og ma bse mdung dgra la phyar //
NK038(nyi)005:1418: g.yon gyi dang po rgyu zhags thogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1419: 'og ma zangs gri rno dbal phyar //
NK038(nyi)005:1420: mi ro za zhing thog ser 'bebs //
NK038(nyi)005:1421: khyod kyi zhabs kyi long bu la /
NK038(nyi)005:1424: khyod kyi sta zur g.yas g.yon la //
NK038(nyi)005:1425: pho seng g.yas la mo seng g.yon //
NK038(nyi)005:1426: ral pa sngon po snyigs se snyig /
NK038(nyi)005:1427: khro bo'i tshogs kyi sprul pa 'gyed //
NK038(nyi)005:1428: khyod kyi rtsibs logs g.yas g.yon na //
NK038(nyi)005:1429: 'phar ba rkang sdebs khyugs se khyug /
NK038(nyi)005:1430: dred mo lag sder chems se chem //
NK038(nyi)005:1431: za byed tshogs kyi sprul pa 'gyed //
NK038(nyi)005:1432: khyod kyi smin khyug g.yas g.yon na //
NK038(nyi)005:1433: bya khyung rgyal po ga ru na //
NK038(nyi)005:1434: khyung gi rngam sgras gdug pa 'dul //
NK038(nyi)005:1435: srin po'i tshogs kyi sprul pa 'gyed //
NK038(nyi)005:1436: phyag na rdo rje'i bka' sdod cing //
NK038(nyi)005:1437: bstan pa gshigs pa myur du sgrol //
NK038(nyi)005:1438: b+h+yo khyod kyi bka' nyan las byed pa //
NK038(nyi)005:1439: nye gnas dung ba'i ma sring brgyad //
NK038(nyi)005:1440: goo ri tsoo ri spra mo ha //
NK038(nyi)005:1442: tsan+da li ste srin mo kun //
NK038(nyi)005:1443: rngams shing gtum pa'i ma tshogs rnams //
NK038(nyi)005:1444: 'jigs pa'i gzugs can mtshon cha thogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1445: sdang ba'i dgra bo nyams pa 'di //
NK038(nyi)005:1446: srog la hur thum dus la babs //
NK038(nyi)005:1447: srid pa'i bu mo dri za brgyad //
NK038(nyi)005:1448: seng stag wa sbyang bzhad kyi gdong //
NK038(nyi)005:1449: kang ka bya rog 'ug gdong tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1450: srog la rngam zhing bstod pa'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1451: nyams pa sod la glo snying zo //
NK038(nyi)005:1452: cho 'phrul sna tshogs dgra la thong //
NK038(nyi)005:1453: dur khrod gnas pa'i sgo bsrung bzhi //
NK038(nyi)005:1454: rtson mo gdong mo 'gar log mo //
NK038(nyi)005:1455: 'jug srog mo ste ma mo bzhi //
NK038(nyi)005:1457: dam nyams dgra bo'i yan lag chings //
NK038(nyi)005:1458: dur khrod bdag mo gru 'debs bzhi //
NK038(nyi)005:1459: skam pa shin du skam ma dang //
NK038(nyi)005:1460: ra ro ma dang khrag 'thung ma //
NK038(nyi)005:1461: chags pa'i tshul gyi srog dbugs len //
NK038(nyi)005:1462: dam nyam dgra bo'i dbugs long zhig /
NK038(nyi)005:1463: smyo 'bog btang ba'i dus la babs //
NK038(nyi)005:1464: lha yi ded dpon ka ru na'i //
NK038(nyi)005:1465: chung ma bu mo srin mo'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1466: 'phrogs nas dbang du byas pa yis //
NK038(nyi)005:1467: srin mo mi bsrun drag shul can //
NK038(nyi)005:1468: bcu gnyis dang ni bco brgyad sogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1469: gtso bo phra men gnod sbyin ma //
NK038(nyi)005:1470: srin mo sha za khrag 'thung ma'i //
NK038(nyi)005:1471: dam nyams dgra bo'i bkrag mdangs phrogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1472: tshe dang srog dbugs bla la dbyangs //
NK038(nyi)005:1473: slob dpon dmag dpon sde dpon mo //
NK038(nyi)005:1474: ru dpon pho nya mngag par bya //
NK038(nyi)005:1475: ci bgyid bka' nyan pho nya'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1476: srin mo'i dmag dpung dgra la drongs //
NK038(nyi)005:1477: srin mo'i gza' tshol dgra la ya //
NK038(nyi)005:1478: rbod gtong rngam pa'i dgra snying khos //
NK038(nyi)005:1479: bam ri thod pa'i phyi rol na //
NK038(nyi)005:1480: rnag dang chu ser 'obs nang na //
NK038(nyi)005:1481: khrag dang sha chen bshang gci dang //
NK038(nyi)005:1482: rkang dang klad pa klad rgyas dang /
NK038(nyi)005:1484: sbrang ma sbrang rgod bung ba dang //
NK038(nyi)005:1485: dug sbrul sdig pa'i dom la sogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1486: dgra bo'i bla khyim rmang nas gshig /
NK038(nyi)005:1487: dgra bo'i nang khrol bal ltar g.yengs //
NK038(nyi)005:1488: kang ka ru rtse rkang ldag dang //
NK038(nyi)005:1489: khrag thung mchu dmar khwa skyes dang //
NK038(nyi)005:1490: bya rog 'ug pa khra rgod dang //
NK038(nyi)005:1491: bya gcan mang po ldings zhing lding //
NK038(nyi)005:1492: dgra bo'i bla srog stengs na 'jum /
NK038(nyi)005:1493: sha la za zhing rgyu ma drongs //
NK038(nyi)005:1494: dbang po'i dwangs ma mig 'bras phyungs //
NK038(nyi)005:1495: snying dang glo mcher mkhal ma sogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1496: don snying rmad lnga rtsad nas phyungs //
NK038(nyi)005:1497: lce spyang stag seng dom dang dred //
NK038(nyi)005:1498: 'phar ba rkang bsdebs la sogs pa'i //
NK038(nyi)005:1499: gcan gzan gdug pa'i tshogs rnams kun //
NK038(nyi)005:1500: dam nyams sha rus bcud la rol //
NK038(nyi)005:1501: myur du sod la khrag la thung //
NK038(nyi)005:1502: dur khrod mkha' 'gro ma mo kun //
NK038(nyi)005:1503: bshugs glu len cing dmag tshogs khyod //
NK038(nyi)005:1504: dam nyams srog dbugs dang la ya //
NK038(nyi)005:1505: dgra bo'i sha rus khrag la rol //
NK038(nyi)005:1506: ma h+aa ka la drag po'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1507: sprul pa yang sprul 'khor dang bcas //
NK038(nyi)005:1508: dam rdzas mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK038(nyi)005:1509: bcol pa'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:1510: ces pa dbus kyi gtso bo bskul ba'i le'u ste brgyad pa'o //
NK038(nyi)005:1512: shar phyogs thod mkhar 'jigs pa nas //
NK038(nyi)005:1513: khro bo'i tshogs dang sprul pa'i 'khor //
NK038(nyi)005:1514: khro bo badz+ra king ka ra //
NK038(nyi)005:1515: sku mdog mthing nag 'jigs tshul brjid //
NK038(nyi)005:1516: phyag g.yas mtshon cha'i 'khor lo bskor //
NK038(nyi)005:1517: dmigs bya'i mgo lus dum bur gtubs //
NK038(nyi)005:1518: g.yon pa thod pa rlon pa ru //
NK038(nyi)005:1519: snying khrag 'thung zhing dmigs pa sgrol //
NK038(nyi)005:1520: khyod kyi thugs dam dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)005:1521: khyod kyi bka' 'khor las byed ni //
NK038(nyi)005:1522: gri thogs gying chen sum cu 'gyed //
NK038(nyi)005:1523: gsang ba'i bdag pos dbang bskur nas //
NK038(nyi)005:1524: rdo rje chos kyi ming btags nas //
NK038(nyi)005:1525: zhe sdang 'bar ba'i klong dkyil nas //
NK038(nyi)005:1526: mthing nag 'bar ba'i cha byad can //
NK038(nyi)005:1527: ltas ngan sna tshogs sprul pa 'gyed //
NK038(nyi)005:1528: rdo rje lu gu zhes bya ba'i //
NK038(nyi)005:1529: gri thogs chen po'i dus la babs //
NK038(nyi)005:1530: rgyal ba'i dgong pa kun 'dus pa'i //
NK038(nyi)005:1532: mi zad lag ring khros pa'i lus //
NK038(nyi)005:1533: rdo rje drag po khro bo rtsal //
NK038(nyi)005:1534: gri thogs ser nag 'jigs pa sbrul gyi brgyan //
NK038(nyi)005:1535: kha nas me 'bar stong gsum bsreg /
NK038(nyi)005:1536: rig 'dzin bdun dang dpung tshogs bdag /
NK038(nyi)005:1537: rin chen myur gu zhes bya bas //
NK038(nyi)005:1538: gri thogs dmar nag khrag gi ral pa can //
NK038(nyi)005:1540: dur khrod mkha' 'gro'i tshogs kyi bdag /
NK038(nyi)005:1541: rdo rje chos kyi las mkhan po //
NK038(nyi)005:1542: gri thogs chos bzang lha yi 'dun sa ru /
NK038(nyi)005:1543: lha yi dmag dpon chen po ste //
NK038(nyi)005:1544: ljang nag lus la rdzu 'phrul can //
NK038(nyi)005:1545: rdo rje las rab drag po rtsal //
NK038(nyi)005:1546: gri thogs nam gyi phar phyed tshur phyed na /
NK038(nyi)005:1547: skyes pa dar ma'i srog gcod cing //
NK038(nyi)005:1548: bud med mngal bu srid kha sdoms //
NK038(nyi)005:1549: spyug glu len cing 'khor los gcod //
NK038(nyi)005:1550: rdo rje zla bzang mthu bo che //
NK038(nyi)005:1551: gri thogs sku mdog dmar nag khrag gi mdog /
NK038(nyi)005:1552: lce spyang dmar po sprul par 'gyed //
NK038(nyi)005:1553: mi zad lag ring chen mo sde //
NK038(nyi)005:1554: rdo rje nyi ma mdangs chen po //
NK038(nyi)005:1555: gri thogs rngams pa'i nga ros gsang sngags ni //
NK038(nyi)005:1556: nam mkha'i khams nas 'brug sgra grogs //
