NK038(nyi)005:1557: mche ba rngams pas dgra snying 'byin //
NK038(nyi)005:1558: rdo rje seng chen mthu bo che //
NK038(nyi)005:1559: gri thogs nag po mi bzad spyan gsum pa //
NK038(nyi)005:1560: shwa na khyi gdong 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NK038(nyi)005:1561: lcags kyi spyang mo mgo dgu pa //
NK038(nyi)005:1562: rdo rje 'chang gi mthu bo che /
NK038(nyi)005:1563: gri thogs mi rtog rtog la gnas pa'i sku //
NK038(nyi)005:1564: thogs pa med pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyis //
NK038(nyi)005:1565: mtshon cha sna tshogs char du 'bebs //
NK038(nyi)005:1566: rdo rje nam mkha' mthu bo che //
NK038(nyi)005:1567: gri thogs mi zad khro bo chen po ni //
NK038(nyi)005:1568: dus bzhi kun tu nyul byed cing //
NK038(nyi)005:1569: nyams pa'i dgra la dus 'bebs pa'i //
NK038(nyi)005:1570: rdo rje dus mtshan mthu bo che //
NK038(nyi)005:1571: gri thogs mthing nag khros pa'i cha byad can //
NK038(nyi)005:1572: mi mgo stong gi phreng bas brgyan //
NK038(nyi)005:1573: ljang nag drag po gsal shing can //
NK038(nyi)005:1574: phyogs bzhi dag tu rgyu mdzad cing //
NK038(nyi)005:1575: phyogs mtshams dag tu rgyug mdzad pa //
NK038(nyi)005:1576: rdo rje phyogs 'dul mthu bo che //
NK038(nyi)005:1577: gri thogs mthing nag khros pa'i cha byad can //
NK038(nyi)005:1578: mi mgo stong gi phreng bas brgyan //
NK038(nyi)005:1579: mi ro bam gyi gdan la bzhugs //
NK038(nyi)005:1580: rdo rje dur khrod bdag po bya //
NK038(nyi)005:1581: gri thogs gri thogs gying chen bcu gsum po //
NK038(nyi)005:1582: la la rak+ta'i thig le can //
NK038(nyi)005:1583: la la zhag gi zo ris can /
NK038(nyi)005:1584: la la thal chen tshom bus brgyan //
NK038(nyi)005:1585: la la drig gi ag shams can //
NK038(nyi)005:1586: la la lcags gri rnon po bsnams //
NK038(nyi)005:1587: glo snying 'byin cing nang khrol za //
NK038(nyi)005:1588: nyams pa'i dgra la khra tshogs chos //
NK038(nyi)005:1589: gang la bya ba'i lus srog 'phrol //
NK038(nyi)005:1590: 'bar ba khro bo'i zhal du btab //
NK038(nyi)005:1591: bcol pa'i phrin las grub par mdzod /
NK038(nyi)005:1593: 'dzam gling nyi ma lho phyogs pha gi na //
NK038(nyi)005:1594: seng gdong khra bo brjid pa'i nang shed na //
NK038(nyi)005:1595: lcags mkhar sngon po gnam du ldems se ldem //
NK038(nyi)005:1596: g.yas na pho seng brgya yis kha yang 'thab //
NK038(nyi)005:1597: g.yon na mo seng brgya yis mche ba bdar //
NK038(nyi)005:1598: 'og na zhe sdang dug mtsho me re re //
NK038(nyi)005:1599: steng na bse yi bya glag brgyad khri bzhi stong lding //
NK038(nyi)005:1600: sked la nyi ma zla ba'i 'od zer 'char //
NK038(nyi)005:1601: ngos la nga rgyal glog dmar brengs se breng //
NK038(nyi)005:1602: bse 'brug ldir ba gnam la rgyug cing sgrog /
NK038(nyi)005:1603: bse yi ser ba lug tsam rtag tu 'bab //
NK038(nyi)005:1604: de 'dra'i sku mkhar 'jigs pa'i nang shed nas //
NK038(nyi)005:1605: ma rungs gdug pa kun gyi gtso bo bzhugs //
NK038(nyi)005:1606: yab gcig gnod sbyin zangs mdog rgyal po bzhugs //
NK038(nyi)005:1607: sku mdog dmar nag brjid pa la //
NK038(nyi)005:1608: dbu la rgya mdud 'khor lo rtsegs //
NK038(nyi)005:1609: ral pa dmar po sprin ltar gtibs //
NK038(nyi)005:1610: spyan dmar dam nyams dgra la bzlog /
NK038(nyi)005:1611: 'jigs pa'i zhal ni bgrad pa las //
NK038(nyi)005:1612: mche ba gnam lcags dgu khri stobs //
NK038(nyi)005:1613: sku la shun gyi g.yang gzhi gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:1614: g.yas na gser gyi ral gri phyar //
NK038(nyi)005:1615: g.yon na bse mdung dmar po bsnams //
NK038(nyi)005:1616: ba dan dmar po glog ltar 'khyug /
NK038(nyi)005:1618: sngon dus zhe sdang las la grub //
NK038(nyi)005:1619: do nub drag po'i las la gshegs //
NK038(nyi)005:1620: de yi yum chen srin mo ni //
NK038(nyi)005:1621: bse gdong zangs mgrin rdzu 'phrul can //
NK038(nyi)005:1622: sngo dmar lus la gzha' ris brgyan //
NK038(nyi)005:1623: ral pa sngo dmar bu yug 'tshubs //
NK038(nyi)005:1624: g.yas pa byad thag dgra la 'phen //
NK038(nyi)005:1625: g.yon pa sngo dmar skyal pa 'phen //
NK038(nyi)005:1626: kha rlangs sngo dmar nad du 'khyil //
NK038(nyi)005:1627: 'jigs pa'i spyugs glu rtse re re //
NK038(nyi)005:1628: srin mo 'bum tshogs las la bskul //
NK038(nyi)005:1629: sngon dus do nub drag khyod kyi bka' nyan las byed pa //
NK038(nyi)005:1630: bse yi sde dpon gyad chen bzhi //
NK038(nyi)005:1631: lha srin sde brgyad las la bskul //
NK038(nyi)005:1632: dam nyams srog gi gshed ma gyis //
NK038(nyi)005:1633: sa bdag bse yi lha mo bzhi //
NK038(nyi)005:1634: bud med sde bzhi'i dmag sna drongs //
NK038(nyi)005:1635: 'du ba rnam bzhi'i nad tshogs rgyob //
NK038(nyi)005:1636: snying zan srog len srog phrog tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1637: 'khor gyi gying chen bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK038(nyi)005:1639: stag ral g.yas la gzig shubs g.yon /
NK038(nyi)005:1640: phyag na zangs gri rno dbal bsnams //
NK038(nyi)005:1641: srog rtsa bcad nas snying khrag 'thung //
NK038(nyi)005:1642: bse phub dmar po'i me 'od kyis //
NK038(nyi)005:1645: gtum chen dregs pa ging gi tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1646: sha khrag srog dbugs mchod par bzhes //
NK038(nyi)005:1647: bcol pa'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:1649: nyi ma nub phyogs ya ki na //
NK038(nyi)005:1650: drag po'i lcags mkhar 'bar ba'i nang shed na //
NK038(nyi)005:1651: srin po yak+sha dz+wa la glog phreng dang //
NK038(nyi)005:1652: klu mo hab sha gdug pa klu yi bu //
NK038(nyi)005:1653: khyab 'jug chen po kun tu rgyu //
NK038(nyi)005:1654: 'jigs byed chen po ra hu la //
NK038(nyi)005:1655: lus po gcig la mgo bo dgu /
NK038(nyi)005:1656: mgo lus med par mig gis khengs //
NK038(nyi)005:1657: ro stod srin po ro smad sbrul //
NK038(nyi)005:1658: sku mdog brjid pa'i dud kha la //
NK038(nyi)005:1659: g.yas pa rdo rje gri gug gis //
NK038(nyi)005:1660: nyams pa'i khog shog tsit+ta phyung //
NK038(nyi)005:1661: g.yon pa chu srin zhags pa yis //
NK038(nyi)005:1663: nyi ma zla ba lto bar za //
NK038(nyi)005:1664: nyi ma'i rjes gcod shar du rgyug /
NK038(nyi)005:1665: zla ba'i rjes gcod nub tu rgyug /
NK038(nyi)005:1666: nyin mo rgyu bzhin bla srog sdud //
NK038(nyi)005:1667: mtshan mo rgyu zhing srog dbugs gcod //
NK038(nyi)005:1668: dmag dpon chen po'i dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)005:1669: gza' bdud chen po'i dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)005:1670: dbang phyug chen po'i dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)005:1671: nam mkha'i khams nas 'brug sgrogs shing //
NK038(nyi)005:1672: bar snang khams nas glog chen 'khyug /
NK038(nyi)005:1673: sa yi dkyil du thog chen 'bebs //
NK038(nyi)005:1674: rgya mtsho'i dkyil nas ser chen 'gril //
NK038(nyi)005:1675: dam nyams dgra bo'i gshed ma gyis //
NK038(nyi)005:1676: lo la khrag gi ser ba phob //
NK038(nyi)005:1677: srog la glo bur ye 'grog thong //
NK038(nyi)005:1678: phyogs bzhi nam mkha'i dkyil yangs nas //
NK038(nyi)005:1679: ngan sngags bdag mo gdong mo bzhi //
NK038(nyi)005:1680: cho 'phrul sprul pa dgra la thong //
NK038(nyi)005:1681: pho lhogs la sogs nad mtshon rgyob //
NK038(nyi)005:1682: phyogs bzhi mtshams bzhi steng 'og nas //
NK038(nyi)005:1683: srin po'i rgyal po chen po bcu //
NK038(nyi)005:1684: mdog ni ma nges khros pa'i zhal //
NK038(nyi)005:1685: mtshon cha sna tshogs 'khor lo sgyur /
NK038(nyi)005:1686: sprul pa lha srin sde brgyad 'gyed //
NK038(nyi)005:1687: bstan pa bsrung bar dam bcas pa'i //
NK038(nyi)005:1688: dam tshig chen po'i dus la babs //
NK038(nyi)005:1689: dam nyams srog rtsa dmar po chod //
NK038(nyi)005:1691: rgya mtsho zho 'phrog chi li li //
NK038(nyi)005:1692: gnam sa bsgyur ba'i dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)005:1693: srog rtsa gtubs la snying gong chod //
NK038(nyi)005:1695: dgra bo'i rtsa ba rlung la bskur //
NK038(nyi)005:1696: bcol pa'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:1698: ma h+aa k+aa la srin po'i tshogs las la bskul ba'i le'u ste bcu gcig pa'o //
NK038(nyi)005:1700: nyi ma byang shar pha gi na //
NK038(nyi)005:1701: khrag mtsho khol ma me re re //
NK038(nyi)005:1702: dug rlangs na bun phyu ru ru //
NK038(nyi)005:1703: mtshon sprin sngo dmar rba rlabs chi li li //
NK038(nyi)005:1704: bse mkhar smug po gnam du zengs se zeng //
NK038(nyi)005:1705: dur bya kam ka'i tshogs ni lding zhing 'dzum //
NK038(nyi)005:1706: lce spyang ling dus tshogs ni di ri ri //
NK038(nyi)005:1707: nad kyi mtshon sprin sngo dmar thibs se thib //
NK038(nyi)005:1708: ma gcig dpal ldan gnyen gyi re ma ti //
NK038(nyi)005:1709: ya mtshan bud med nag mo rngams pa'i gdong //
NK038(nyi)005:1710: sku mdog mthing nag 'jigs pa la //
NK038(nyi)005:1711: khrag gi ral pa mun ltar gtibs //
NK038(nyi)005:1712: spyi bo'i gtsug na zla ba 'char //
NK038(nyi)005:1713: lte ba'i dbus na nyi ma 'char //
NK038(nyi)005:1714: srid pa gsum la bla tshe brku //
NK038(nyi)005:1715: snyan cha seng sbrul dril bus brgyan //
NK038(nyi)005:1716: thams cad zil gnon gdug pa 'dul //
NK038(nyi)005:1717: sku stod zhing gi g.yang gzhi la //
NK038(nyi)005:1718: rgyu phreng khrag dang zhag gis brgyan //
NK038(nyi)005:1719: sku smad re lde'i sham thabs la //
NK038(nyi)005:1720: sbrul dang thod rlon dril bu brgyan //
NK038(nyi)005:1721: chibs su drel rta rkang gsum chibs //
NK038(nyi)005:1722: drag po mtshon cha'i lte lan can //
NK038(nyi)005:1723: g.yas na gshin rje'i khram bam bsnams //
NK038(nyi)005:1724: g.yon na nad kyi rkyal pa bsnams //
NK038(nyi)005:1725: btsan gyi shwa rdel phyogs bcur 'thor //
NK038(nyi)005:1726: nad kyi rkyal pa phyogs bcur sdebs //
NK038(nyi)005:1727: 'tshub nag stong gi nang na bzhugs //
NK038(nyi)005:1728: khyod kyi thugs dam dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)005:1729: za byed tshogs kyi sprul pa khyod //
NK038(nyi)005:1730: bar snang khams kyi za byed ma //
NK038(nyi)005:1731: nag mo ra la can bye ba 'bum //
NK038(nyi)005:1732: rdo rje rigs kyi rnal 'byor ma //
NK038(nyi)005:1733: khyod kyi thugs dam dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)005:1734: shar phyogs khams gyi za byed ma //
NK038(nyi)005:1735: dkar mo ral can bye ba 'bum //
NK038(nyi)005:1736: sangs rgyas rigs khyod kyi shar gyi dgra bgegs thul //
NK038(nyi)005:1737: lho phyogs khams ser mo ral can khros pa'i tshe //
NK038(nyi)005:1738: rin chen khyod kyi nub phyogs khams /
NK038(nyi)005:1739: dmar mo ral can pho nyar bcas //
NK038(nyi)005:1740: pad+ma khyod kyi byang phyogs khams kyi za byed ma //
NK038(nyi)005:1741: ljang nag ral can rngams pa'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1742: las kyi khyod kyi byang ces gsungs so //
NK038(nyi)005:1743: dpal ma h+aa k+aa la'i ma mo'i tshogs bskul ba'i le'u ste bcu gnyis pa'o ////
NK038(nyi)005:1744: rgyud mtshon cha sngon rol las /
NK038(nyi)005:1745: bal po b+ha su rda ras /
NK038(nyi)005:1746: gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes la gdams //
NK038(nyi)005:1747: bla ma zur gyi bka' bsrung /
NK038(nyi)005:1749: de nas smon lam 'di ltar gdab ste /
NK038(nyi)005:1750: ho mgon po khyed mchod byin brlabs kyi //
NK038(nyi)005:1751: sems can legs don 'byor pa la //
NK038(nyi)005:1752: bgegs ni rnam kun med par shog /
NK038(nyi)005:1753: rta dang ba glang nor dang 'bru //
NK038(nyi)005:1755: dge zhing tshe ring nad med par //
NK038(nyi)005:1756: thams cad 'byor pa ldan par shog /
NK038(nyi)005:1757: 'gro la phan bdes khyab gyur nas //
NK038(nyi)005:1758: nad dang mu ge kun bral zhing //
NK038(nyi)005:1759: rgyal po dge zhing des pa rnams //
NK038(nyi)005:1760: chos kyi rgyal srid skyong bar shog /
NK038(nyi)005:1761: bde bar gshegs pa'i bstan pa 'di //
NK038(nyi)005:1762: phyogs dus kun tu dar rgyas nas //
NK038(nyi)005:1763: mtha' yas sems can thams cad kyang //
NK038(nyi)005:1764: chos kyi snod du 'gyur bar shog /
NK038(nyi)005:1765: dge ba thams cad legs bsngo zhing //
NK038(nyi)005:1766: mgon po mchod rten mthu dpal gyis //
NK038(nyi)005:1767: bdag dang bdag 'khor sbyin bdag rnams //
NK038(nyi)005:1768: khyad par rdo rje theg mchog gi /
NK038(nyi)005:1769: rim gnyis zab mo mthar phyin nas //
NK038(nyi)005:1770: 'bras bu sku gnyis mchog thob nas //
NK038(nyi)005:1771: don gnyis phun sum tshogs par shog /
NK038(nyi)005:1772: de ltar gnas skabs mthar thug gi /
NK038(nyi)005:1773: dus dang rnam pa thams cad du //
NK038(nyi)005:1774: chos skyong rgyal po dpal mgon che //
NK038(nyi)005:1776: bla ma mchog dang yi dam lha //
NK038(nyi)005:1777: dkon mchog gsum gyi thugs rje dang //
NK038(nyi)005:1778: bden pa'i byin rlabs la brten nas //
NK038(nyi)005:1780: da lta snyigs ma lnga bdo'i dus 'di na //
NK038(nyi)005:1781: bka' gsang rmad byung don la bdag spyod kyi //
NK038(nyi)005:1782: dam tshig dbang gi lus dang grib ma ltar //
NK038(nyi)005:1783: 'grogs te bdag 'khor longs spyod bsrung zhing skyabs //
NK038(nyi)005:1784: zhe sdang gdug pa'i dgra bgegs gang byung dus //
NK038(nyi)005:1785: dpal mgon khyed kyi mthu rtsal der phyung zhing //
NK038(nyi)005:1786: rtags dang cho 'phrul dngos su bstan pa dang //
NK038(nyi)005:1787: mngon spyod drag po'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:1788: ma h+aa k+aa la'i mchod sprin bal po b+ha su d+ha ras mdzad pa rdzogs so ////
NK038(nyi)005:1789: rgyud mtshon cha sngon rol la brten nas /
NK038(nyi)005:1790: bal po b+ha su d+ha ras mdzad pa /
NK038(nyi)005:1791: gnubs chen po sangs rgyas rin po che la gdams nas rim pas brgyud de /
NK038(nyi)005:1793: bdag blan gyi ban d+he dpal ldan mgon po la //
NK038(nyi)005:1794: thugs dgos bzhin pa'i sgo nas //
NK038(nyi)005:1795: rta nag gi dben gnas bde chen sgrol pa sbub tu //
NK038(nyi)005:1796: dag lung rdzogs par gnang ba lags so //
NK038(nyi)005:1797: bdag slan ban gyi bka' bsrung //
NK038(nyi)005:1798: bstan pa bsrung ba'i ba tsas su che'o //
NK038(nyi)005:1799: 'brub khung las kyi legs ldan dkyil 'khor bzhugs so //
NK038(nyi)005:1800: dpal badz+ra he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)005:1801: chos sku nam mkha' nyid dang mtshungs pa la //
NK038(nyi)005:1802: gzugs sku rnam gnyis 'gro ba'i don sprul mdzad //
NK038(nyi)005:1803: lnga bcu rtsa brgyad sprul pa yang sprul la //
NK038(nyi)005:1804: bdag nyid dang bas kun nas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)005:1805: mar khu lta bu'i bstan pa dam pa la //
NK038(nyi)005:1806: gnod byed dgra bgegs bsgral ba'i las 'di brtsam //
NK038(nyi)005:1807: dkyil 'khor bdun pa'i las rim la //
NK038(nyi)005:1808: las la sbyar ba'i rim pa ni //
NK038(nyi)005:1809: ko ka thang dmar mtsho yin no //
NK038(nyi)005:1810: 'brub khung drag shul can gyi gnas //
NK038(nyi)005:1811: rdo rje thabs kyi lta ba'i yul //
NK038(nyi)005:1812: dur khrod bdag po 'khor dang bcas //
NK038(nyi)005:1813: bdag ni bka' yi las mkhan te //
NK038(nyi)005:1814: sangs rgyas kun gyi gdul dka' ba //
NK038(nyi)005:1815: de dag ma lus bdag gi 'dul //
NK038(nyi)005:1816: gsungs pa'i don ni 'di yin te //
NK038(nyi)005:1817: las la sbyar ba gnyis su bstan //
NK038(nyi)005:1818: rdzas bshams pa dang ting 'dzin no //
NK038(nyi)005:1821: 'brub khung rim pa gzhug na gsal //
NK038(nyi)005:1822: lid+ga grog shing sa dang ni //
NK038(nyi)005:1823: khung hrul sa dang phung pa dang //
NK038(nyi)005:1825: rjes sa la sogs sa sna lnga //
NK038(nyi)005:1826: bshang gci dgra yi kha chu mig chu dang //
NK038(nyi)005:1827: lus kyi dri ma gos dum dang //
NK038(nyi)005:1828: sa spyin dag dang sbyar byas la //
NK038(nyi)005:1829: lid+ga phyag rgya bzhi yis brgya //
NK038(nyi)005:1830: snying khar ming rus sne nas dkar nag gi btags la //
NK038(nyi)005:1832: mda' dang gsal zhing rnams la 'dud //
NK038(nyi)005:1835: sarba sha trum ma ra ya phata /
NK038(nyi)005:1836: ces bya ba snying khar gzhug /
NK038(nyi)005:1838: mkhar gyi phyogs bzhi dbus dang lnga gru gsum lcags khang rnams su //
NK038(nyi)005:1839: shog bu'i lid+ga gong bzhin gzhug /
NK038(nyi)005:1840: rang rang rten rdzas steng nas mnan //
NK038(nyi)005:1841: dus bzhir tshogs kyi lhag ma la //
NK038(nyi)005:1842: gong gi rdzas bcas lid+ga ni //
NK038(nyi)005:1843: dus bzhir bsgral zhing bskyed pa bstan //
NK038(nyi)005:1844: mgo ngos lid+ga mnan pa bya //
NK038(nyi)005:1845: rkang ngos lid+ga sbyin bsreg bya //
NK038(nyi)005:1847: ting nge 'dzin gyi rim pa ni //
NK038(nyi)005:1848: da ni las la sbyar ba yis //
NK038(nyi)005:1849: gtor ma la sogs mchod pa rnams //
NK038(nyi)005:1850: bsgrub pa chen po'i dus bzhin du //
NK038(nyi)005:1851: dus bzhir tshogs kyi mchod pa bya //
NK038(nyi)005:1852: mnyes shing mgu ba tshul bzhin bya //
NK038(nyi)005:1853: gong bzhin lhag ma'i lid+ga bsgral //
NK038(nyi)005:1854: ji srid mtshan ma rnyed kyi bar //
NK038(nyi)005:1856: bzhi snying cig tu dril ba'i sngags //
NK038(nyi)005:1857: rngams pa'i nga ros 'don pa ni //
NK038(nyi)005:1858: bdag nyid dpal chen he ru ka'i //
NK038(nyi)005:1859: thugs kyi gsang mchod dag la ni //
NK038(nyi)005:1860: phyi nang gsang ba'i ru tra yis //
NK038(nyi)005:1862: phyi yi ru tra'i thugs kar thim //
NK038(nyi)005:1863: de yi ru tra lnga sprul te /
NK038(nyi)005:1864: de ni zhabs kyi long bu las //
NK038(nyi)005:1865: gnod sbyin 'jigs tshogs mang sprul te //
NK038(nyi)005:1866: stag smad la sogs gcan zan rnams //
NK038(nyi)005:1867: bse khrab gyon pa'i gnod sbyin dpag med tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1868: phyag g.yas lcags kyu dgra bo'i snying nas bzungs //
NK038(nyi)005:1869: g.yon ru mtshon nag po spyi bo nas //
NK038(nyi)005:1870: bzungs ste rang dbang med par dmigs bya kun //
NK038(nyi)005:1871: tshor ba'i phung po bcom nas nga rgyal gtsad nas gcod //
NK038(nyi)005:1872: gang la dmigs pa'i sha chen gtso la stob //
NK038(nyi)005:1873: sha rus khrag dang nang khrol la sogs pa //
NK038(nyi)005:1874: gcan zan rnams kyis rab tu za bar bsam //
NK038(nyi)005:1875: nyid kyi rtsibs logs g.yas g.yon ma mo'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1876: 'phar ba rkang ldag dred mo lag sdeb dang //
NK038(nyi)005:1877: dpal ldan lha mo nag mos dmag sna drongs //
NK038(nyi)005:1878: nag mo smug mo dkar ser dmar mo'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1879: ljang mo'i tshogs ni sprin phung tsam sprul nas //
NK038(nyi)005:1880: g.yas na khrag dang dug dang nad kyi thun //
NK038(nyi)005:1881: thogs nas dmigs bya bsgral bar byed par bsam //
NK038(nyi)005:1882: g.yon pa nyams pa dmigs bya rgyu zhags kyis //
NK038(nyi)005:1883: ske nas khrid nas rang dbang med par bkug /
NK038(nyi)005:1884: 'du byed phung chom phrag dog rtsad nas bcad //
NK038(nyi)005:1885: thugs rjes dmigs bya'i dri chu gtso la btab //
NK038(nyi)005:1886: sha rus khrag dang nang khrol dbang po dang //
NK038(nyi)005:1887: snying la dred 'phar za byed tshogs kyi rol //
NK038(nyi)005:1888: nyid kyi sta zur g.yas g.yon khro bo'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1889: rnams kyi sprul pa seng ge pho mo rnams //
NK038(nyi)005:1890: g.yu ral bsig cing gcan zan spos mo'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1891: sprul pa sprin gyis phung po bzhin byung nas //
NK038(nyi)005:1892: g.yas kyi lcags kyus dam nyam dmigs bya'o //
NK038(nyi)005:1893: snying nas bzung nas rang dbang med par de //
NK038(nyi)005:1894: bkug nas g.yon pa'i yungs zor dmigs bya yis //
NK038(nyi)005:1895: snying mkhar brdeg cing de yi phung po bcom //
NK038(nyi)005:1896: zhe sdang rtsad nas bcad cing byang chub sems //
NK038(nyi)005:1897: bdud rtsi khro rgyal gtso la 'bul bar bsam //
NK038(nyi)005:1898: sha rus khrag dang nang khrol seng ge la //
NK038(nyi)005:1899: sogs pa mche ba can gyi rol bar bsam //
NK038(nyi)005:1900: de nyid smin btsub g.yas g.yon srin po dang //
NK038(nyi)005:1901: srin mo'i tshogs ni sprin phung bzhin sprul nas //
NK038(nyi)005:1902: bya khyung la sogs 'dab chags yang sprul dang //
NK038(nyi)005:1903: gza' mchog la sogs srin po srin mo'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:1904: phyag g.yon sbrul zhags dmigs bya'i ske nas bzungs //
NK038(nyi)005:1905: g.yas kyi mtshon chas spyi bo gzir cing mnan //
NK038(nyi)005:1906: rang dbang med par bkug nas 'du shes bcoms //
NK038(nyi)005:1907: gang la dmigs nas 'dod chags rtsad nas gcod //
NK038(nyi)005:1908: rak+ta gtso la stobs cing sha rus rnams //
NK038(nyi)005:1909: nang khrol spyang tshogs gtum tshogs za bar bsam zer
NK038(nyi)005:1910: ba 'dug nang khrol bcas sogs gtum sogs za bar
NK038(nyi)005:1911: bsam // thugs kyi gsang ba'i mgon po ljang sngon ni //
NK038(nyi)005:1912: drag po gsal shing can ni mang sprul nas /
NK038(nyi)005:1913: dmigs bya bkug nas rnam shes phung po bcom //
NK038(nyi)005:1914: gti mug rtsad gcod dri chen gtso la stobs //
NK038(nyi)005:1915: sha rus khrag dang nang khrol 'khor sprul pa //
NK038(nyi)005:1916: kun gyi za zhing dug lnga rtsad nas gcod //
NK038(nyi)005:1917: dug lnga phung po lnga ni gnas 'gyur ba //
NK038(nyi)005:1918: bdud rtsi ye shes lnga ni rigs lngar bsam //
NK038(nyi)005:1919: spyod la ma chags stong nyid rdo rjer sbyangs //
NK038(nyi)005:1920: byas na nyon mongs rdul gyis gos mi 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)005:1921: gtso 'khor rnams kyi sngags bzlos ting nge 'dzin //
NK038(nyi)005:1922: 'khor lo gsal ces phal cher 'di nyid do //
NK038(nyi)005:1923: skabs skabs dag tu 'khor lo byin rlabs ting 'dzin ni //
NK038(nyi)005:1924: 'khor lo che ge'i ma ni bla ma bdag las blangs //
NK038(nyi)005:1925: de ltar dus bzhir tshogs mchod dbul zhing bsgral //
NK038(nyi)005:1926: dus bzhir lhag ma'i stabs pa bya ba'i rim pa ni /
NK038(nyi)005:1927: dang po phyogs bzhi dbus lnga'i ling chen bsgral /
NK038(nyi)005:1928: ting 'dzin rim pa da la bdun pa las /
NK038(nyi)005:1929: mthu 'jug khrid pa'i sbyor thabs kyis //
NK038(nyi)005:1930: bdud rtsi lnga yis dngas sbyor bas //
NK038(nyi)005:1931: gshung pa lnga ni bdud rtsir bsgyur //
NK038(nyi)005:1932: byas la mi sogs phrin las kyis //
NK038(nyi)005:1933: spyod pa ye shes ma chags pas //
NK038(nyi)005:1934: thams cad stong nyid rdo rjer sbyangs //
NK038(nyi)005:1935: zhes pa'i don rnams 'di yin te //
NK038(nyi)005:1936: dang po snang srid lha 'dre'i tshogs rnams la //
NK038(nyi)005:1937: gser skyems btang zhing ma nyes gzu dpang gsol /
NK038(nyi)005:1938: gnyis pa badz+ra bdag nyid he ru ka'i nga rgyal kyis //
NK038(nyi)005:1939: thugs las e 'phros 'brub khung gzi byin skyed //
NK038(nyi)005:1940: phyag rgya rdo rje sdams pas sor mo nang du rkyang ba ni //
NK038(nyi)005:1941: mee 'bar lta bur byas la e ram zhes //
NK038(nyi)005:1942: brjod pas 'brub khung lcags khang nang nas me 'bar bsam /
NK038(nyi)005:1943: gsum pa gang la dmigs bya ste /
NK038(nyi)005:1944: dgug cing rten la stim pa'i phyag rgya ni /
NK038(nyi)005:1945: rdo rje khu tshur rgyab sprad mathe'u chung //
NK038(nyi)005:1946: lu gu rgyud sbrel 'dzub gnyis lcags kyu'i tshul /
NK038(nyi)005:1947: bur kur i tsi ke phyi u tsu sma kro
NK038(nyi)005:1948: d+ha che ge mo badz+ra ang+ku a kar+sha ya h'u
NK038(nyi)005:1949: dza dzah ni yang dza dzah zhes pa'i sngags kyis
NK038(nyi)005:1951: ting 'dzin bdag gi thugs las gying chen 'khor dang bcas /
NK038(nyi)005:1952: dpag tu med pa sprin phung bzhin spros nas /
NK038(nyi)005:1953: phyag g.yas lcags kyus dmigs bya'i snying bzung nas /
NK038(nyi)005:1954: g.yon gyi rgyu zhags ske nas 'khrid par bsam /
NK038(nyi)005:1955: bzhi pa ling ga'i ni las dmigs bya yis /
NK038(nyi)005:1956: shes pa gsal bskyed dgug la stim pa ni /
NK038(nyi)005:1957: rtsa ba'i sngags la che ge mo ak+sha ya ces pas bstim par thim par bsam /
NK038(nyi)005:1958: lnga pa lha dang bral ba lha ni lnga /
NK038(nyi)005:1959: pho lha dgra lha yul lha srog lha dang //
NK038(nyi)005:1960: mo lha lnga ste rdzas kyi dbral ba ni //
NK038(nyi)005:1961: g.yag dang bon por rdzu na pho lha yin //
NK038(nyi)005:1962: lham 'bog sha chen gu gul nag pos bdug /
NK038(nyi)005:1963: stag gam rta pa gegs byed dgra lha yin //
NK038(nyi)005:1964: khyi lud tshil chen gu gul nag pos bdug /
NK038(nyi)005:1965: bgegs byed med par 'gugs dka' srog lha yin //
NK038(nyi)005:1966: lham 'bog yungs nag ske tshe tshil chen dang //
NK038(nyi)005:1967: gu gul nag po bsreg cing bdug par byed //
NK038(nyi)005:1968: sha ba'am bud med bzang pos bsrung na mo lha yin //
NK038(nyi)005:1969: khyi lud tshil chen yugs sa'i dor rtas bdug /
NK038(nyi)005:1970: zhang blon bon po rdzu na yul lha yin //
NK038(nyi)005:1971: khyi lud dor rta gu gul nag pos bdug /
NK038(nyi)005:1972: gzhan yang ban d+he dag dang 'gres gyur na //
NK038(nyi)005:1973: kho yi yi dam gang byed 'khor lo bri //
NK038(nyi)005:1974: bdag gi 'og bcug gu gul dam rdzas bdug /
NK038(nyi)005:1975: rgyal po sna tshogs bsreg cing dang 'dres khyi lud tsha ba lnga //
NK038(nyi)005:1976: za 'og gu gul nag po bsreg cing bdug /
NK038(nyi)005:1977: bon po dang 'gras lham 'brog khyi lud dang //
NK038(nyi)005:1978: sha chen gu gul nag pos bsreg cing bdug /
NK038(nyi)005:1979: mi nag dang 'gras dor rta tshil chen dang //
NK038(nyi)005:1980: khyi lud gu gul nag gsum po bsreg cing bsres cing bdug /
NK038(nyi)005:1981: spyir ni gong gi rdzas te glang ru'i zhogs ma dang //
NK038(nyi)005:1982: rta dug rma kha rgyal tshil rta sbangs rnams bsreg nas //
NK038(nyi)005:1983: cha snyam zhib rtags gu gul nag po'i chus sbrus ste sran ma 'bring po'i tshad tsam bsreg /
NK038(nyi)005:1984: lha dang bral zhing drag po'i stang stabs bya //
NK038(nyi)005:1985: ru zor 'phang zhing drag po'i phrin las bcol //
NK038(nyi)005:1986: sngags dang dmigs bya'i ming spel drag sngags bzlas //
NK038(nyi)005:1987: pho nya dus bzhir bskul zhing zor 'phang ste //
NK038(nyi)005:1988: rtsa ba'i sngags la che ge de ba pra be sha ya phata /
NK038(nyi)005:1989: rtags pa la rdzas dud bdug cing dmigs bya de //
NK038(nyi)005:1990: mthu rtsal mgon med skyabs dang bral bar bsam //
NK038(nyi)005:1991: sngags dug thun gzhi snying dril la bzlas //
NK038(nyi)005:1992: lid+ga la brab shes pa myos shing brgyal //
NK038(nyi)005:1993: lus rengs gcer bu skra gzings skyabs bral bsam //
NK038(nyi)005:1994: drug pa bsgral ba'i ting 'dzin rim pa ni //
NK038(nyi)005:1995: bdag nyid badz+ra he ru ka'i thugs kha nas //
NK038(nyi)005:1996: gsal ba'i mgon po ljang sngon gsal shing can //
NK038(nyi)005:1997: sngon du bsnyen phul mnga' gsol thugs rjes bskul //
NK038(nyi)005:1998: ye shes lnga ldan byang sems gsal shing bsam sngon
NK038(nyi)005:1999: du bsnyen pa phul ba'i bu ga'i mtshon cha nag
NK038(nyi)005:2000: po thogs te sku lnga ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin
NK038(nyi)005:2001: byang sems dkar la 'tsher ba rnam rtog gi skyon
NK038(nyi)005:2002: gang gis kyang ma gos par bsam /
NK038(nyi)005:2003: sngon du bsnyen phur mnga' gsol ba'i phur pa nag po blangs /
NK038(nyi)005:2004: bskul ba ye shes lnga ldan byang chub sems kyi gsal shing bsam zer ba 'dug /
NK038(nyi)005:2005: gsal shing sha dang lpags pa bral //
NK038(nyi)005:2006: kha sbyor che la bsgral ba'i las bya'o //
NK038(nyi)005:2007: 'tshor ba'i phung po snying gi sgo lnga bcad zhe sdang rtsad na bcad /
NK038(nyi)005:2008: me long ye shes rtogs nas rdor sems sku rgyu bsam /
NK038(nyi)005:2009: snying nas 'od ni tshon gang thal byung nas //
NK038(nyi)005:2010: 'du shes rtsad bcad 'byung ldan sku ru bsam //
NK038(nyi)005:2011: nga rgyal nyon mongs rtsad bcad mnyam nyid ye shes rtogs //
NK038(nyi)005:2012: khrag gi sbal pa bye'u'i klad pa tsam //
NK038(nyi)005:2013: de nyid thal byung 'du shes phung po bcom //
NK038(nyi)005:2014: 'dod chags rtsad bcad mtha' yas sku ru bsam //
NK038(nyi)005:2015: sor rtogs ye shes lta ba ngang gi gsal //
NK038(nyi)005:2016: nga rgyal lha'i bu'i rnam shes phung po bcom //
NK038(nyi)005:2017: de nyid don yod grub pa'i sku ru gsal //
NK038(nyi)005:2018: phrag dog rtsad bcad nyon mongs bya grub ngang du gsal //
NK038(nyi)005:2019: mtshon cha nag po byang sem dkar la 'tsher //
NK038(nyi)005:2020: dmigs bya'i tshe ni ba mo brgya btags 'dra //
NK038(nyi)005:2021: rdo tshan mchil ma bzhin du gsal shing la //
NK038(nyi)005:2022: 'dus shing gti mug phung po bcom par bsam //
NK038(nyi)005:2023: chos dbyings ye shes gsal bas gzugs phung bcom //
NK038(nyi)005:2024: rnam snang skur gyur stong nyid rdo rjer sbyangs //
NK038(nyi)005:2025: bag chags rdul ma gos pas byang sems dang //
NK038(nyi)005:2026: sdig pas ma gos mig sogs phrin las yin //
NK038(nyi)005:2027: 'byung ba lnga ni dug lnga phung po lnga //
NK038(nyi)005:2028: bdud rtsi lnga sbyor ye shes rig lngar gsal //
NK038(nyi)005:2029: 'di rnams sbyor sgrol lam zab thabs mchog 'di //
NK038(nyi)005:2030: shes rab mchog gyur lta ba rtogs pa yi //
NK038(nyi)005:2031: spyod yul tsam yin kun gyi spyod yul min //
NK038(nyi)005:2032: de ltar ma yin lta ba dman zhing shes rab zhan /
NK038(nyi)005:2033: zhe sdang rgyun gyi dmigs bya rlag 'dod don 'di gsungs /
NK038(nyi)005:2034: dang po zhe sdang me yis dmigs bya bkug /
NK038(nyi)005:2035: gnyis pa nga rgyal bdag gi shes pa rten la stim /
NK038(nyi)005:2036: gsum pa 'dod chags lha lngas gong bzhin lha dang bral /
NK038(nyi)005:2037: bzhi pa phrag dog nyon mongs yid can bsgral ba ni /
NK038(nyi)005:2038: bdag nyid dpal chen he ru'i thugs las 'phros pas /
NK038(nyi)005:2039: gsang ba'i mgon po bskul zhing srog bcad par gzhug /
NK038(nyi)005:2040: pho nya dus gzhir bskul zhing mtshon cha nag po brlag /
NK038(nyi)005:2041: khro tshogs mang po sprul cing gnas 'dun gdam //
NK038(nyi)005:2042: gnod sbyin 'jigs byed tshogs ni sprin phung rtsal //
NK038(nyi)005:2043: spro zhing dmigs bya'i lha rten bcom pa ru //
NK038(nyi)005:2044: bsam zhing rgyug zer snying gi dkyil du brdeg /
NK038(nyi)005:2045: za byed ma mo'i tshogs kyi khrag dang dug thun thogs //
NK038(nyi)005:2046: dmigs bya myos shing brgyal bar byas la gnad gtong bsam brabs par /
NK038(nyi)005:2047: khro bo gying gi tshogs kyi khro tshogs mang //
NK038(nyi)005:2048: sprul nas yungs dkar skye zor snying gi dkyil du 'phang zhing rdeg /
NK038(nyi)005:2049: gsum pa zor dkar nag mtshams su 'phang zhing brdeg zer ba 'dug /
NK038(nyi)005:2050: srin po'i dmag tshogs stag dang dom dang mche ba can rnams dang /
NK038(nyi)005:2051: bdud bya khra thabs mang sprul sha khrag za bar bsam /
NK038(nyi)005:2052: tshogs bdag mar bskul grug gi dmigs bya bkug /
NK038(nyi)005:2053: gong du gsung bzhin bsreg dang stabs dang mnan pa bya /
NK038(nyi)005:2054: bzhi snying dril ba 'bum du bzlas la dbul zhing lid+ga bsgral /
NK038(nyi)005:2055: 'khor la khri tsho re yi phyogs bzhi'i lid+ga bsgral /
NK038(nyi)005:2056: nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi nyin mo lho yi ling chen bsgral /
NK038(nyi)005:2057: khro bo gnod sbyin chen po bstab pa'i bro brdungs la /
NK038(nyi)005:2058: nyi shu dgu yi nub mo sbyin bsreg las sbyor rtsam /
NK038(nyi)005:2059: gtad khram mnan pa'i las kyang de yi nub mo rtsam /
NK038(nyi)005:2060: gnam stong bdag la tshogs mchod bshams shing mchod pa dbul /
NK038(nyi)005:2061: bskang gso byas la bkra shis gsol shing lhag gtor btang /
NK038(nyi)005:2062: ye shes gshegs gsol dam tshig bdag la bsdu //
NK038(nyi)005:2063: 'di dag ni las sbyor ting 'dzin rim pa yin /
NK038(nyi)005:2065: mi pham he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)005:2066: tshogs bdag mgon po 'khor bcas kyi //
NK038(nyi)005:2067: bsnyen dang nye ba'i bsnyen pa dang //
NK038(nyi)005:2068: bsgrub dang bsgrub pa chen po yis //
NK038(nyi)005:2069: las sbyor rim pa mdo tsam bri //
NK038(nyi)005:2070: dang po bsnyen pa'i rim pa ni //
NK038(nyi)005:2071: dkyil 'khor bdun pa'i rim pa las //
NK038(nyi)005:2072: bka' sdod pho nya'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK038(nyi)005:2073: dang po rten rdzas tshogs par bsham //
NK038(nyi)005:2074: lha yi bsnyen pa rdzogs pa dang //
NK038(nyi)005:2075: tshogs bdag 'khor bcas bskyed pa ni //
NK038(nyi)005:2076: ri bo byan slag 'chongs kyi rtser //
NK038(nyi)005:2077: ma la ya yi rtse mo ru //
NK038(nyi)005:2078: ko ka thang dmar rgya mtsho'i ngo //
NK038(nyi)005:2079: bam ri thod pa'i mkhar rtse la //
NK038(nyi)005:2080: steng na bdud bya nag po gnas //
NK038(nyi)005:2081: bdud kyi ru mtshon pu ru ru //
NK038(nyi)005:2082: de nang gru gsum lcags mkhar 'bar //
NK038(nyi)005:2083: tshogs bdag yab yum bzhugs pa'i gnas //
NK038(nyi)005:2084: phyogs bzhi gru gsum lcags mkhar bzhi //
NK038(nyi)005:2085: gnod sbyin la sogs 'khor bzhi gnas //
NK038(nyi)005:2086: de dag gsal bar bsgom par bya //
NK038(nyi)005:2087: de ru 'khor bcas bdag he ru ka gsal ba'i
NK038(nyi)005:2088: thugs ka nas rgyu zhes brjod pas dbus su bsam
NK038(nyi)005:2089: / gcer bu bya yi gshog pa can /
NK038(nyi)005:2090: bskyed pa ni 'di rim pa bstan /
NK038(nyi)005:2091: dbus su rgyu las tshogs bdag bskyed //
NK038(nyi)005:2092: bur kur ma h+aa ka la sa ma ya h'u phatah sngags de brjod pa tsam gyi ni /
NK038(nyi)005:2093: legs ldan nag po bdud kyi rje //
NK038(nyi)005:2094: wa mdog nag po zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum bgrad //
NK038(nyi)005:2095: phyag na gri gug rdo rjes mtshan //
NK038(nyi)005:2096: g.yon pa b+han+d+ha lcang lo can khrag gis bkang ba bsnams //
NK038(nyi)005:2097: mche gtsigs zhal gdang ljags 'dril zhing //
NK038(nyi)005:2098: dur khrod chas brgyad rgyan gyis brgyan //
NK038(nyi)005:2099: ha la ha la'i sgra sgrogs shing //
NK038(nyi)005:2100: ro yi gdan la brkyangs bskum du bzhugs pa /
NK038(nyi)005:2101: dmigs bya khros pa'i sems kyis mnan /
NK038(nyi)005:2102: g.yon du nye gnas kro ti shwa ri sku mdog sngo skya g.yas yab la khyud pa /
NK038(nyi)005:2103: g.yon b+han+d+ha dmar gyis gang ba bsnams pa /
NK038(nyi)005:2104: mkhar nag lcags khang nang du bskyed //
NK038(nyi)005:2105: lho yi lcags khang ra ba ru //
NK038(nyi)005:2106: ya sam 'od du zhu ba las //
NK038(nyi)005:2107: yak+sha dz+wa la sa ma ya //
NK038(nyi)005:2108: ces pas gnod sbyin zangs thogs yab /
NK038(nyi)005:2109: bse gdong zangs mgrin rdzu 'phrul yum //
NK038(nyi)005:2110: yab yum gnyis la 'khor gyi sras //
NK038(nyi)005:2111: zor gyi rgyal po mched bzhi dang //
NK038(nyi)005:2112: bse yi skyes bu drug la sogs //
NK038(nyi)005:2113: bse yi mi reng bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK038(nyi)005:2114: gnod sbyin tshogs kyi phyag na ni //
NK038(nyi)005:2115: rgyu zor mda' zor spungs zor dang //
NK038(nyi)005:2116: thod zor thog pa dpag med bsam //
NK038(nyi)005:2117: byang gi mkhar du yi ge rtsa //
NK038(nyi)005:2118: de nyid 'od du zhu ba las //
NK038(nyi)005:2119: tsit+ta dz+wa la sa ma ya //
NK038(nyi)005:2120: ces pas za byed ma mo'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:2121: dpal ldan lha mo nag mo che //
NK038(nyi)005:2122: tshibs su dril rta rkang gsum chibs //
NK038(nyi)005:2123: g.yas na gshin rje'i khram shing bsnams //
NK038(nyi)005:2124: g.yon na nad kyi rkyal pa thogs //
NK038(nyi)005:2125: de yi 'khor du ma mo'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:2126: dkar ser dmar smug phyag na ni //
NK038(nyi)005:2127: khrag dang nad rkyal thogs pa'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:2128: sprin gyi phung po tsam du gyur //
NK038(nyi)005:2129: shar gyi mkhar du yi ge ba //
NK038(nyi)005:2130: de nyid 'od du zhu ba las //
NK038(nyi)005:2131: badz+ra kro ta dz+wa la sa ma ya /
NK038(nyi)005:2132: ces pas khro bo gying gi tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:2133: phyag na yungs dkar mtshon bsnams pa //
NK038(nyi)005:2134: sna tshogs sprin phung tsam du gyur //
NK038(nyi)005:2135: nub kyi mkhar du yi ge ra //
NK038(nyi)005:2136: de nyid 'od du zhu ba las //
NK038(nyi)005:2137: rak+sha dz+wa la sa ma ya //
NK038(nyi)005:2138: ces pas srin po mgo dgu pa //
NK038(nyi)005:2139: ro stod mi la ro smad sbrul //
NK038(nyi)005:2140: mgo lus med par mig gi gang //
NK038(nyi)005:2141: lag na sbrul zhags gri gug thogs //
NK038(nyi)005:2142: de ni sring mo gdong mo bzhi //
NK038(nyi)005:2143: srin po'i rgyal po chen po bcu //
NK038(nyi)005:2144: la sogs srin po srin mo'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:2145: sprin gyi phung po tsam du gyur //
NK038(nyi)005:2146: de ltar drag po 'khor bcas bskyed //
NK038(nyi)005:2147: ri bo byan brlag 'chong gyi rtse //
NK038(nyi)005:2148: ko ka thang dmar rgya mtsho'i dkyil //
NK038(nyi)005:2149: 'brub khung drag shul can gyi gnas //
NK038(nyi)005:2150: bam ri thod pa mkhar gnas nas //
NK038(nyi)005:2151: drag po 'khor dang bcas pa bkug /
NK038(nyi)005:2152: bdag nyid dpal he ru'i thugs kha nas khro bo
NK038(nyi)005:2153: lcags kyu thogs pa dpag tu med pa las 'od
NK038(nyi)005:2154: zer lcags kyu'i dbyibs lta bu dpag tu med pa
NK038(nyi)005:2155: 'phros pas / lcags kyu'i phyag rgya rdo rje khu tshur rgyab sprad de /
NK038(nyi)005:2156: mathe'u chung lu gu rgyud du sbrel la mdzub mo lcags kyu'i tshul du bkug pa dang /
NK038(nyi)005:2158: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK038(nyi)005:2159: bur kur ma h+aa ka la sa ma ya hrim hrim /
NK038(nyi)005:2161: zhes brjod pas drag po 'khor dang bcas pa khro
NK038(nyi)005:2162: bo dang 'od zer lcags kyu lta bus snying nas
NK038(nyi)005:2163: bzung ste dgug pa ni drag po 'khor dang bcas
NK038(nyi)005:2164: pa'o // de nyid dgug nas mdun na gnas pa ngag tu /
NK038(nyi)005:2165: ru lu ru lu h'u phata b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)005:2168: rak+sha sh+ri he ru ka ru tra ma tra ha ha ham /
NK038(nyi)005:2171: bdag nyid dpal he ru ka'i nga rgyal du gsal
NK038(nyi)005:2172: bas zhal du rngubs te mi gtsang ba'i snam nas
NK038(nyi)005:2173: / mdun du bskyed pa la bstim /
NK038(nyi)005:2174: de'i sdig pa dag pa dang /
NK038(nyi)005:2176: bdag la de ring phan chad las ci bgyi bka'
NK038(nyi)005:2177: stsol cig zer bar bsam pa ni zhal du rngub
NK038(nyi)005:2178: cing snam nas bton pas ming gi rnam grangs dang
NK038(nyi)005:2179: bcas pa'o // dpa' bo chen po dgongs su gsol zhes pa la sogs pa /
NK038(nyi)005:2181: zhes gsol ba 'debs par bsam mo //
NK038(nyi)005:2182: h'u h'u h'u bi shwa badz+ra kro ta dz+wa la man+da la phata /
NK038(nyi)005:2188: skal ldan 'dus pa'i tshogs chen khyed //
NK038(nyi)005:2189: ces pas spro ba bskyed par bsam /
NK038(nyi)005:2190: drag po 'khor dang bcas pas byang chub tu sems bskyed par gsol ba 'debs par bsam mo //
NK038(nyi)005:2191: de nas bdag dpal chen po'i nga rgyal dang ldan
NK038(nyi)005:2192: pas chos srung 'khor dang bcas pa'i lce la bdud
NK038(nyi)005:2194: badz+ra a mri ta a hi hi sarba man+da la h'u /
NK038(nyi)005:2196: ces pas bdud rtsis dbang bskur du bcug la chos srung dam can du mnga' gsol bsam mo //
NK038(nyi)005:2197: nar bu tshar bu zhes mna' sgag par bsam mo //
NK038(nyi)005:2198: de la nye ba'i 'byor pa'i mchod pa lnga dbul ba ni /
NK038(nyi)005:2199: bur kur ma h+aa ka la e ho shwa mo kro d+ha /
NK038(nyi)005:2207: de nas dam rdzas bsngo ba ni /
