NK038(nyi)005:2523: bsnyen bsgrub bzhi yi man ngag 'jug tshugs su mdzad pa rdzogs so //
NK038(nyi)005:2524: dpal chen po 'khor dang bcas pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)005:2525: dgongs pa 'dus pa'i rgyud dag las //
NK038(nyi)005:2526: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung ba'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)005:2527: dkyil 'khor bdun pa'i rim pa tsam //
NK038(nyi)005:2528: de la rnam pa gnyis yin te //
NK038(nyi)005:2531: 'jig rten pa la da la gsum /
NK038(nyi)005:2532: de yi gdam dag dam pa 'di //
NK038(nyi)005:2534: bla ma'i gsung 'phros mang thos pas //
NK038(nyi)005:2535: bsgrub pa'i lag len mang thos phyir //
NK038(nyi)005:2536: yig sna 'dir ni bri bar bya //
NK038(nyi)005:2537: de la sbyir bzlas pa la gnyis te /
NK038(nyi)005:2540: ngag gi bzlas pa la yang gnyis te /
NK038(nyi)005:2541: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i bzlas pa dang /
NK038(nyi)005:2543: rdo rje'i bzlas pa la gnyis te /
NK038(nyi)005:2545: de kho na nyid kyi bzlas pa'o //
NK038(nyi)005:2546: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i bzlas pa la gsum ste //
NK038(nyi)005:2547: bsnyen pa dang bsgrub pa dang las la sbyar ba'o //
NK038(nyi)005:2548: bsnyen pa la ni bskyed pa'i rim pa rdzogs nas /
NK038(nyi)005:2549: mchod bstod tshul bzhin byas pa'i rjes la bzlas pa'i
NK038(nyi)005:2550: dus su zhi rgyas dbang gsum gyi bzlas pa'i bsnyen
NK038(nyi)005:2551: pa'o // bsgrub pa ni dkyil 'khor du me tog dor te /
NK038(nyi)005:2552: gang la babs pa'i lhas bdag la dbang bskur te /
NK038(nyi)005:2553: gzi byin dang ldan par bya ba ni bsgrub pa'o //
NK038(nyi)005:2554: las la sbyar ba'i dus su dang po bdag gi gser skyems la sogs pas mchod /
NK038(nyi)005:2556: de nas bdag nyid steng gi nam mkha' la sangs rgyas mi bskyod pa dmigs te /
NK038(nyi)005:2557: sngags kyi 'od zer gyi 'od du zhu nas /
NK038(nyi)005:2558: bdag la bstim ste gzi byin dang ldan par byas la //
NK038(nyi)005:2559: de nas ngag gi bzlas pa byas pas /
NK038(nyi)005:2560: bdag gis zhal nas phar drag po sngags kyi 'od
NK038(nyi)005:2561: zer kha dog po sna lnga la lcags kyus mtshan
NK038(nyi)005:2562: pa spros te drag po'i tshad ni gyad kyi mda'
NK038(nyi)005:2564: lha sbyin gyi rgyud la phog pa ni lcags kyi thog rgyab pa lta bu'o //
NK038(nyi)005:2565: snying po byang chub kyi bcud bsdus te tshur 'ongs pa thag pa dkar nag sgril ba lta bu'o //
NK038(nyi)005:2566: de nas bdag la thim ste bdag dpal chen po'i gzi mdangs dang ldan par bskyed pa ni /
NK038(nyi)005:2567: dgra bo'i rnam par shes pa bdag rnal 'byor pa'i go cha'o //
NK038(nyi)005:2568: nyon mongs pa dang bcas pa'i phung po lhag ma
NK038(nyi)005:2569: la mkha' 'gro la tshogs su bstab par bya ste
NK038(nyi)005:2570: / de ltar de'i sbyor bas nyin lan gsum mtshan lan gsum du tshogs kyi mchod pa dang /
NK038(nyi)005:2572: bzlas pa bya ba ni las la sbyar ba'o //
NK038(nyi)005:2573: 'jig rten pa'i bzlas pa la gsum ste /
NK038(nyi)005:2577: de la dang po rtag rten bsham te /
NK038(nyi)005:2578: sa sna bdun gyi 'dag pa la mkhar bya ste /
NK038(nyi)005:2579: tshad ni zhing du khru gang chur rkyang khru gang /
NK038(nyi)005:2580: logs bzhi la glo skar bzhi thod pas mtshan pa'o //
NK038(nyi)005:2581: ru mtshon chen po bzhi dang /
NK038(nyi)005:2583: steng du bya khyung gi phyag rgya gnyis dang //
NK038(nyi)005:2584: de'i nang du gru gsum mthing nag gi nang du /
NK038(nyi)005:2585: dmigs bya'i lid+ga gzhag khro bo'i steng du mda' sgro
NK038(nyi)005:2586: yud lnga pa cig la dug med nag po btsugs
NK038(nyi)005:2587: pa la mgul du dar mthing nag gi le'u gcig
NK038(nyi)005:2588: gdags / de la dang po ril bu'i phur ma rten pa'i rdzas /
NK038(nyi)005:2589: bar ma khrol bu brab pa'i rdzas /
NK038(nyi)005:2591: phur pa ling ga'i snying khar btsugs la /
NK038(nyi)005:2592: khro mo'i brten du nam mkha' sngon mo gser mig la gcig /
NK038(nyi)005:2593: bya rgod kyi mathe'u gcig la dar lce bzhi dang bcas te mad'i steng btsugs la bzhag go //
NK038(nyi)005:2594: khro bo'i rdzas ni za ma tog sman sna tshogs kyis bkang ba dang /
NK038(nyi)005:2597: bse byang dmar po dang ri rab spyi skor thod bram kyang bzhag /
NK038(nyi)005:2598: khro mo'i rdzas su thod pa tshal bu'i nang du rkang sna tshogs /
NK038(nyi)005:2601: khrag sna tshogs kyis bkang la bzhag shar du khro bo'i mkhar byas la /
NK038(nyi)005:2602: dmigs bya'i ling ga'i steng du mchog phur zhig la
NK038(nyi)005:2603: rgyu zhags sam mkhar nag gi gdags steng snying mkhar
NK038(nyi)005:2604: btsug ste bzhag / rgyu zhags kyi sna ri rab spyi bskor gyi dmigs sdang la btags la bzhag /
NK038(nyi)005:2605: k+ai la ya nyer gcig sgrom shing du byin gyis brlabs la bzhag /
NK038(nyi)005:2606: lho phyogs gnod sbyin gyi mkhar du ling+ka'i steng du
NK038(nyi)005:2607: bse mdung dmar po ba dan dang bcas te bzhag
NK038(nyi)005:2610: nub phyogs srin po'i mkhar du lid+ga'i steng du sbrul mgo gdeng ka gsum du bzhag /
NK038(nyi)005:2611: g.yas su sha sna deb rtse gang //
NK038(nyi)005:2612: g.yon du klu sman deb rtse gang //
NK038(nyi)005:2614: byang phyog za byed kyi mkhar du ling ga'i steng du dar mthing nag gi gur dbub /
NK038(nyi)005:2615: byang phyogs ling ga'i steng du yungs dkar gyi thun brab /
NK038(nyi)005:2617: dgra bo lha dang bral ba'i phyir rgya tshil la sogs pa'ang bzhag /
NK038(nyi)005:2618: de nas khro bo'i zhal byas la mkhar gyi nang du mda' la skyon te /
NK038(nyi)005:2619: de rnal 'byor pa bdag nyid la kha bstan la bzhag /
NK038(nyi)005:2620: de nas bsnyen bsgrub tshul bzhin du bya /
NK038(nyi)005:2621: de nas las la sbyor ba'i dus su 'brub khung las kyi dkyil 'khor bya ste /
NK038(nyi)005:2622: dang po gser skyems btang la bden pa brdar /
NK038(nyi)005:2624: de nas drag po'i sngags bzlas pa'i dus su bdag
NK038(nyi)005:2625: dpal chen thugs kha nas las kyi mgon po zhal
NK038(nyi)005:2626: gcig phyag gnyis pa sku mdog sngo nag gcer bu
NK038(nyi)005:2627: ral pa gyen du bardzesa pa /
NK038(nyi)005:2628: phyag g.yas na gsal shing nag po /
NK038(nyi)005:2629: g.yon na zangs gri nag po tsar gyis bton la /
NK038(nyi)005:2630: bzhi bo'i mgon po dang gnyis su med par byas ste /
NK038(nyi)005:2631: bdag dpal chen po la las ci bgyi zhes bka' na par bsam mo //
NK038(nyi)005:2632: rnal 'byor pa bdag nyid kyi brda bstan pas /
NK038(nyi)005:2634: lce spyang dmar por sprul te /
NK038(nyi)005:2635: lha sbyin gyi g.yas na yar zhugs /
NK038(nyi)005:2637: don snying lnga rtsar gyis btab nas slar la phyung ste /
NK038(nyi)005:2638: bdag dpal chen po la bstab par bsam /
NK038(nyi)005:2639: de ltar de'i sbyor ba dang ldan pa'i nyin mtshan
NK038(nyi)005:2640: dus drug tu bstab pa'i las bya zhing drag po'i
NK038(nyi)005:2642: de nas mtshan ma gnad pa la phebs pa dang /
NK038(nyi)005:2643: rnal 'byor gcig gis mtho mtshams su phyin la /
NK038(nyi)005:2644: rgya tshil gyi dud pa btang la lha dang dbral ba'i cho ga bya'o //
NK038(nyi)005:2645: slar log ste phur pa btab pa dang /
NK038(nyi)005:2649: de nas bstab pa'i las bya /
NK038(nyi)005:2651: de nas mnan pa'i las byas nas sbyin sreg byas
NK038(nyi)005:2652: pa'i thal ba la byas te ming byang ling ga'i
NK038(nyi)005:2654: de 'khor lo kha sbyar gyi bar du bcug te
NK038(nyi)005:2655: ma khar nag gam rgyu zhags kyis bsdams la gtad
NK038(nyi)005:2656: pa'i sar khyer la phur pa bzhis sa bdag 'bros
NK038(nyi)005:2657: rgyun bcad / de nas gser skyems btang /
NK038(nyi)005:2658: yul gyi lha 'dre la ma nyes pa'i dpang gzugs /
NK038(nyi)005:2659: sa bdag de la yang klu sman sna tshogs kyi mchod pa sbyin /
NK038(nyi)005:2660: de nas mnan pa'i sa gru gsum khru gang pa brus te /
NK038(nyi)005:2661: de nas rgya mtsho'i gting na gnas pa'i klu bdud che ge mo kha phye zhig /
NK038(nyi)005:2662: rgyas pa'i dgra bo sho ra re byas te kha sbyar la gzhug /
NK038(nyi)005:2663: de'i steng du mgon po mi'u thung gi gzugs bskyon /
NK038(nyi)005:2664: de'i steng du khro bo'i mkhar bya khyung gi phyag rgya dang bcas pa bzhug /
NK038(nyi)005:2665: de'i steng du g.yam pa nag po la rdo rje rgya gram gyis rgyas btab la kha bcad do //
NK038(nyi)005:2666: de nas dpa' bo'i bro brdungs ste //
NK038(nyi)005:2667: gom pa nyi shu rtsa gcig phyir bskyod la zor brdeg go //
NK038(nyi)005:2668: logs na spogs pa'i cho ga bya'o //
NK038(nyi)005:2669: g.yas su log na rkang pa g.yas la lan gsum bskor la 'phangs /
NK038(nyi)005:2671: g.yon du log na'ang de bzhin bya'o //
NK038(nyi)005:2672: thad dkar 'dug par tho gcig btsugs la phar tshur rdeg go //
NK038(nyi)005:2673: de ru yang log na g.yas su phyin la sngags mjug go bzlog byas la stong tsho gcig 'don /
NK038(nyi)005:2674: de nas yang zor las bya /
NK038(nyi)005:2675: de nas gtang rag gi gtor ma btang /
NK038(nyi)005:2676: ye shes kyi lha gshegs su gsol /
NK038(nyi)005:2677: dam tshig pa lus la bsdu /
NK038(nyi)005:2679: de ltar byas pa ni las la sbyar ba'o //
NK038(nyi)005:2680: de ltar byas pas kyang lo ru thogs nas phyi rtags med na mnan pa bya /
NK038(nyi)005:2681: 'phar nas 'dug na mnan pa'i las bya /
NK038(nyi)005:2682: ma phar na lha gnad la dbab pa'i las bya ste /
NK038(nyi)005:2683: mgon po'i gzugs mtho gang pa byas la /
NK038(nyi)005:2684: ru lu'i sngags spyi bor bri /
NK038(nyi)005:2685: bsnyen pa dang nye ba'i bsnyen pa rkang pa g.yas
NK038(nyi)005:2686: nas lag pa g.yas pa'i bar du gzhogs g.yas la
NK038(nyi)005:2687: bri / bsgrub pa bsgrub pa chen po gnyis rkang pa g.yon pa nas gzhogs g.yon la bri /
NK038(nyi)005:2688: bzhi snying gcig tu dril ba ni 'doms su bri /
NK038(nyi)005:2689: yi ge'i mgo ni nang du bstan no //
NK038(nyi)005:2690: de nas dag dpa' bo'i 'og tu zhag gsum gzir mnan bya'o //
NK038(nyi)005:2691: tha ma 'byung po'i nyin zhag la zangs gri nag pos gtub la /
NK038(nyi)005:2692: drag po'i me sbar te sbyin bsreg bya'o //
NK038(nyi)005:2693: de nas thal ba la mgon po'i gzugs /
NK038(nyi)005:2694: khong par dmigs bya'i ling ga gzhug /
NK038(nyi)005:2695: gso ba'i cho ga gzhung bzhin bya //
NK038(nyi)005:2696: mnyes pa'i chod pa lnga yang sbyin //
NK038(nyi)005:2697: khyad par gyi ni mchod pa'ang //
NK038(nyi)005:2698: mthu pa'i rdzas kyi bsngo bar bya //
NK038(nyi)005:2699: mchod rten nag po mtho gang la //
NK038(nyi)005:2700: gu gul dud pas bdugs byas la //
NK038(nyi)005:2701: dur khrod chen po'i sar khyer te //
NK038(nyi)005:2702: dong brus mgon po'i gzugs bcug la //
NK038(nyi)005:2703: de yis steng du mchod rten bzhag /
NK038(nyi)005:2704: g.yang gzhi nag po btab cing bskor ba phyir log bya /
NK038(nyi)005:2705: ma nyes dpang gzugs rgyangs brdungs bar bya /
NK038(nyi)005:2706: de ltar byas na las la gdon mi za /
NK038(nyi)005:2707: lha gnad la bor ba'i cho ga bya /
NK038(nyi)005:2708: b+h+yo phata ru lu ru lu phata h'u d+ha kro
NK038(nyi)005:2709: sh+ma tsu u phyi ki tsi ka li bur kur
NK038(nyi)005:2713: h'u ru lu ru lu b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)005:2714: ces pas kun bas che ba'i rgyal po'o //
NK038(nyi)005:2716: 'khor rnams bsdud pa'i nga rgyal lo //
NK038(nyi)005:2718: kun gyi mi thub cing gzhan pas pra ba'i rgyal po'o //
NK038(nyi)005:2719: ru tra ma tra ma ra tra /
NK038(nyi)005:2720: dgra 'du kun 'du rab tu 'dum dam la 'du zhes pa'i skad do //
NK038(nyi)005:2723: dkyil 'khor bdun pa'i bka' sdod pho nya'i dkyil 'khor la bcu bzhi /
NK038(nyi)005:2724: drag po 'khor bcas bskyed pa dang gcig /
NK038(nyi)005:2726: zhal du rngubs te snam nas bton pa dang gsum /
NK038(nyi)005:2727: drag po dpal chen po la dkyil 'khor du chug cig par gsol ba gdab pa bzhi /
NK038(nyi)005:2728: dpal chen pos dkyil 'khor du snang nas bcug pa dang lnga /
NK038(nyi)005:2729: drag po dpal chen po la bskyed chug par gsol ba gdab pa dang drug /
NK038(nyi)005:2730: dpal chen pos sems bskyed pa ni dam tshig dbab pa dang bdun /
NK038(nyi)005:2731: dpal chen po bdag la dbang bskur bar gsol ba btab pa dang brgyad /
NK038(nyi)005:2732: dpal chen pos bdag la dbang bskur ba dang dgu /
NK038(nyi)005:2733: drag pos dbang nod cing dbang yon dbul ba dang bcu /
NK038(nyi)005:2734: dpal chen pos mnga' gsol zhing mchod pa dbul ba dang bcu gcig /
NK038(nyi)005:2735: dpal chen po la lus la sogs pa 'bangs su dbul ba dang bcu gnyis /
NK038(nyi)005:2736: dpal chen pos 'bangs su gnang ba byin pa dang bcu gsum /
NK038(nyi)005:2737: rdo rje ljags kyi bzlas pas nye bar bsdus te bzlas pa bya'o //
NK038(nyi)005:2740: he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)005:2741: tshogs bdag mgon po 'khor bcas kyi //
NK038(nyi)005:2742: bsnyen pa dang ni nye bsnyen dang //
NK038(nyi)005:2743: bsgrub pa dang ni bsgrub chen po //
NK038(nyi)005:2744: las sbyong rim pa bri bar bya //
NK038(nyi)005:2745: dang po bsnyen pa'i rim pa ni //
NK038(nyi)005:2746: dkyil 'khor bdun pa'i rim pa las //
NK038(nyi)005:2747: bka' sdod pho nya'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK038(nyi)005:2748: dang po rten rdzas tshogs par bya //
NK038(nyi)005:2749: lha yi bsnyen pa rdzogs pa dang //
NK038(nyi)005:2750: tshogs bdag bskyed rim bstan pa ni //
NK038(nyi)005:2751: ri bo byan rlag phyongs kyi rtse //
NK038(nyi)005:2752: ma la ya yi rtse mo ru /
NK038(nyi)005:2753: ko ka thang dmar rgya mtsho'i dkyil //
NK038(nyi)005:2754: bam ri thod pa'i mkhar chen la //
NK038(nyi)005:2755: steng du bdud bya nag po gnas //
NK038(nyi)005:2756: bdud kyi ru mtshon pu ru ru //
NK038(nyi)005:2757: de na gru gsum lcags mkhar 'bar //
NK038(nyi)005:2758: tshogs bdag yab yum bzhugs pa'i gnas //
NK038(nyi)005:2759: phyogs bzhir gru gsum lcags mkhang bzhi //
NK038(nyi)005:2760: gnod sbyin la sogs 'khor bzhi gnas //
NK038(nyi)005:2761: de ru 'khor bcas bskyed pa ni //
NK038(nyi)005:2762: bdag dpal he ru gsal ba'i thugs ka nas ru zhes brjod pas dbus su ru bsam /
NK038(nyi)005:2764: bu kur ma h+aa ka la sa ma ya zhes brjod /
NK038(nyi)005:2765: tshogs bdag bdud kyi rje mgon po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK038(nyi)005:2766: sku mdog nag po gcer bu bya'i gshog pa can
NK038(nyi)005:2767: dbu skra kham nag 'bar zhing rnyigs pa spyan gsum
NK038(nyi)005:2768: bgrad pa / phyag g.yas na gri gug yu ba rdo rjes byas pa /
NK038(nyi)005:2769: g.yon b+han+d+ha lcang lo can khrag gi bkang ba bsnams /
NK038(nyi)005:2770: zhal gdangs zhing mche ba gtsigs pa ljags 'dril ba /
NK038(nyi)005:2771: dur khrod kyi chas brgyad kyis brgyan pa /
NK038(nyi)005:2772: ha la ha la'i sgra sgrogs pa //
NK038(nyi)005:2773: ro'i gdan la rkyang bskum du bzhugs pa /
NK038(nyi)005:2774: dmigs bya khros pa'i sems kyis gnon pa'o //
NK038(nyi)005:2775: g.yon du nye gnas kro ti shwa ri ma sku mdog lngo skya g.yas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK038(nyi)005:2776: g.yon b+han+d+ha dmar gyis bkang ba bsnams pa gtso 'khor
NK038(nyi)005:2777: bskyed pa la bzhi las dang po kro ta khro
NK038(nyi)005:2779: zhes brjod pas shar phyogs lcags mkhar 'bar ba ru bsam /
NK038(nyi)005:2780: de 'od du zhu ba las badz+ra kro ta dz+wa
NK038(nyi)005:2781: la sa ma ya zhes brjod pas grol gying chen
NK038(nyi)005:2782: po bco brgyad gying tsam bcu gnyis 'dzin gying bzhi
NK038(nyi)005:2783: cu rtsa gnyis la sogs pa khro bo gying gi
NK038(nyi)005:2784: tshogs phyag na mtshon cha bsnams pa lcags mkhar nang
NK038(nyi)005:2785: du bskyed do // ya gnyis pa gnod sbyin gyi tshogs bskyed pa ni /
NK038(nyi)005:2786: zhes brjod pas lho phyogs lcags mkhar nang du ya bsam /
NK038(nyi)005:2788: yak+sha dz+wa la sa ma ya zhes brjod pas /
NK038(nyi)005:2789: gnod sbyin zangs thog gi rgyal po dang /
NK038(nyi)005:2790: yum bse gdong zangs mgrin ma sras zor gyi rgyal po bzhi phyag na yungs zor /
NK038(nyi)005:2792: thod zor thogs pa sprin phung tsam bse'i skyes bu bzhi lag na sbrul zhags bse'i dgug /
NK038(nyi)005:2793: ming sring bzhi bcu pa thams cad bskyed do //
NK038(nyi)005:2794: ra gsum pa zhes brjod pas nub phyogs lcags khang du ra bsam de 'od du zhu ba las /
NK038(nyi)005:2795: rak+sha dz+wa la sa ma ya zhes brjod pas khyab
NK038(nyi)005:2796: 'jug chen po ra hu la ro stod mi la
NK038(nyi)005:2797: ro smad sbrul mjug lus thams cad mig gi khengs
NK038(nyi)005:2798: pa / sring mo gdong mo bzhi /
NK038(nyi)005:2799: phyogs bcur srin mo bcu la sogs pa srin po dang sring mo'i rgyal mo bcu rnams bskyed do //
NK038(nyi)005:2801: byang phyogs su lcags mkhar nang du ma bsam /
NK038(nyi)005:2803: tsit+ta dz+wa la sa ma ya zhes brjod pas /
NK038(nyi)005:2804: dpal ldan nag mo re ma ti drel rta rkang gsum la chibs pa /
NK038(nyi)005:2811: byang du ljang mo 'bum sde bskyed do //
NK038(nyi)005:2812: thams cad sku mdog phyag mtshan bsnams //
NK038(nyi)005:2813: pho nya ring mo nas 'byung ba bzhin bsgom mo //
NK038(nyi)005:2815: de nas bdag dpal du gsal ba las /
NK038(nyi)005:2816: ngag tuh ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK038(nyi)005:2817: bur kur ma h+aa ka la sa ma ya hrim hrim /
NK038(nyi)005:2819: a gu sha dza dzah zhes brjod pas dpal chen
NK038(nyi)005:2820: po'i thugs ka nas 'od zer lcag kyu'i dbyibs lta
NK038(nyi)005:2821: bu 'phros pas nag po 'khor dang bcas pa'i snying
NK038(nyi)005:2822: kha nas bzung nas mdun du dgug la /
NK038(nyi)005:2823: mdun du gnas pa la ru lu ru lu b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)005:2826: rak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka ru tra ma tra /
NK038(nyi)005:2827: ri bo byan slag chongs kyi rtse nas kub nas /
NK038(nyi)005:2830: bdag dpal mgon po 'khor bcas chen por gsal ba'i
NK038(nyi)005:2831: zhal du gsol nas gnam nas bton nas mdun du
NK038(nyi)005:2832: bskyed pa dang gnyis su med par stim la bzhag
NK038(nyi)005:2833: go // de nas nag po chen pos /
NK038(nyi)005:2834: dpa' bo kho rang gsal gdab po chen po dgongs su gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:2835: bdag cag skal ldan 'dus pa'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:2837: rgyal ba'i sras su bzung du gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:2838: zhes dpa' bo la gsol ba gdab bo //
NK038(nyi)005:2840: bi shwa gnas sbyong zhig byin gyis brlabs pa badz+ra kro ta dz+wa la man+da la phata phata /
NK038(nyi)005:2841: ta kem kho'i sgrib pa dag par bsam ta kem phata /
NK038(nyi)005:2845: skal spro ba skyed pa dang dga' bar bsam /
NK038(nyi)005:2848: grub pa lung gi gsang sgo 'dir //
NK038(nyi)005:2849: su dag 'ong par slar mi bzlog /
NK038(nyi)005:2850: dpa' bo chen pos sbyod pa dang //
NK038(nyi)005:2851: byin gyis brlabs dang spro ba bskyed pa'o //
NK038(nyi)005:2852: bdag dang mtha' yas sems mgon pos mdzad pa can rnams /
NK038(nyi)005:2853: mun pas sgrib pas de ma shes //
NK038(nyi)005:2854: byang chub mchog gi lam 'di nas /
NK038(nyi)005:2855: sangs rgyas sa la 'jug par bya'o //
NK038(nyi)005:2856: mgon pos sems bskyed pa dang /
NK038(nyi)005:2857: dkyil 'khor du 'jug par khas blangs pa'o //
NK038(nyi)005:2858: rdo rje can gyi rnal 'byor khyod //
NK038(nyi)005:2859: rdo rje can du ci nges na //
NK038(nyi)005:2860: gsang ba gsum du nges pa nyid //
NK038(nyi)005:2861: mi phyed rdo rje'i dam tshig ni //
NK038(nyi)005:2862: gsang ba gsum gyi dbyings nas byung //
NK038(nyi)005:2863: da la gsum gyi dam tshig yin //
NK038(nyi)005:2864: grub na 'jigs pa'i dus med do //
NK038(nyi)005:2866: zhes lan gsum brjod pas mgon po'i spyi bor /
NK038(nyi)005:2867: mgrin par +aah snying khar h'u thim pas sku gsung
NK038(nyi)005:2868: thugs kyi dam tshig las mi 'da' bar bsam mo
NK038(nyi)005:2869: // sa ma ya zhes lan gsum tu bdud rtsi gtor /
NK038(nyi)005:2870: brjod pas dam tshig blangs na dam bcas par bsam mo //
NK038(nyi)005:2871: de nas dam chu blud pa ni ting nge 'dzin gsal bar /
NK038(nyi)005:2872: gsang ba gsum gyi dam pa rnams //
NK038(nyi)005:2873: khyod kyi rab tu bslus gyur na //
NK038(nyi)005:2874: de kun khros nas khrag chen po //
NK038(nyi)005:2875: nyams pa'i snying nas drangs te thung //
NK038(nyi)005:2876: i dan ste na ra kan /
NK038(nyi)005:2879: sa ma ya rak+sha si si ti /
NK038(nyi)005:2880: bi sa na badz+ra a mri ta he ta lan
NK038(nyi)005:2881: gsum kan ces bdud rtsi gtor ba mgon pos 'thungs
NK038(nyi)005:2882: pas snying la thim pas h'u mthing nag du gyur
NK038(nyi)005:2883: te khos dam ma nyams par bdag gi stong grogs
NK038(nyi)005:2884: byas nas rdo rje sems dpa' tshon gang par gyur
NK038(nyi)005:2885: par bsam // de ltar ma byas na badz+ra yak+sha
NK038(nyi)005:2886: lcags kyi sdig pa mgo dgu pa zhig du gyur
NK038(nyi)005:2887: te kho'i snying po byed par bsam mo //
NK038(nyi)005:2888: dpa' bo chen pos dam tshig dbog cing dam tshig dran pa'o //
NK038(nyi)005:2889: ye shes rin kho bos phyag 'tshal ba chen dbu rgyan mchog /
NK038(nyi)005:2890: gzi brjid phung po bla na med //
NK038(nyi)005:2891: sangs rgyas rin chen kun 'dus pa //
NK038(nyi)005:2892: rnam par rgyal la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)005:2893: dbyig gi ye shes gtso mchog nyid //
NK038(nyi)005:2894: rdo rje sems dpa' mchog 'dzin pa //
NK038(nyi)005:2895: khyed kyi dam tshig gtso lags kyi //
NK038(nyi)005:2896: dbang mchog rgyal pos bdag dbang bskur //
NK038(nyi)005:2897: nag po chen pos phyag 'tshal ba dang //
NK038(nyi)005:2898: phyag 'atsala bar gsol bar gdab pa'o //
NK038(nyi)005:2899: +aahmh'u a mri ta a hi hi sarba man+da la h'u /
NK038(nyi)005:2901: dpa' bos ye shes kyi bdud rtsis thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes su dbang bskur ba'o //
NK038(nyi)005:2902: bdag gi skyes bu khyed kyis sngon du dbang bskur bas /
NK038(nyi)005:2903: sangs rgyas kun gyi bdag nyid kyi bdag la dbang bskur bas /
NK038(nyi)005:2904: bcom ldan thams cad mchog gi ni bdag lags te /
NK038(nyi)005:2905: mchog nyid bsgrub phyir dbang rnams blangs bar bya'o //
NK038(nyi)005:2906: de'i rjes su 'khor rnams kyi mos pa dang dang bas gtang rag gi mchod pa dbul ba'o //
NK038(nyi)005:2907: de nas dpal chen pos rang la nye bar mchod
NK038(nyi)005:2908: pa lngas mchod par bstan pa ni kho la dbul
NK038(nyi)005:2909: / bur kur ma h+aa k+aa la e ho shwa
NK038(nyi)005:2910: mo kro ta kro ta ru pa p+au 'di rnams
NK038(nyi)005:2911: dngos las lha mo bslab pa mi bslab gsung tsa
NK038(nyi)005:2917: de nas dam tshig gi dam rdzas bsngo ba ni //
NK038(nyi)005:2918: dka' thub chen po tshur gson cig /
NK038(nyi)005:2919: legs ldan nag po ma rungs pa //
NK038(nyi)005:2920: sha khrag dmar gyi gtor ma bzhes //
NK038(nyi)005:2921: rang gi rgyal srid la gnas te //
NK038(nyi)005:2922: gzhan gyi sde rnams 'joms mdzad pa //
NK038(nyi)005:2923: khram la btab pa'i dgra bgegs rnams //
NK038(nyi)005:2924: rol cig dgongs shig kh+aa ram kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)005:2925: khyed kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)005:2926: bse byang khram la btab pa yis //
NK038(nyi)005:2927: ma dang srong mo bu rnams la //
NK038(nyi)005:2928: dpa' bo khyod kyi rol mdzad cing //
NK038(nyi)005:2929: dam tshig chen po ma btang cig /
NK038(nyi)005:2930: zhe sdang gtso bo la bsngo ba khro bo rnams la bsngo ba can gyi bdag po'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:2931: sems can kun gyi srog phrog ma //
NK038(nyi)005:2932: bse byang khram la btab pa yis //
NK038(nyi)005:2933: sha dang khrag la longs spyod kyis //
NK038(nyi)005:2934: gnod sbyin rnams la bsngo ba chen po ma rungs pa //
NK038(nyi)005:2935: bse byang khram la btab pa yis //
NK038(nyi)005:2936: gser sogs yul mkhar blangs nas ni //
NK038(nyi)005:2937: rang gi 'dod par longs spyod kyis //
NK038(nyi)005:2938: rtog pa'i rgyal po rnams gson cig /
NK038(nyi)005:2939: mgo thod bcad nas rtags rten dang //
NK038(nyi)005:2941: yid bzhin lta bu'i dngos grub stsol //
NK038(nyi)005:2942: rigs ngan rme sha can gyi tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:2943: mi sha glang chen sha sogs bzhes //
NK038(nyi)005:2944: srin mo khrag 'thung ma lus la //
NK038(nyi)005:2945: bsad pa'i khrag ni dron mo 'thung //
NK038(nyi)005:2946: bzhes shig dgra bo'i khrag la 'thung //
NK038(nyi)005:2947: sprul pa'i phra men chen po rnams //
NK038(nyi)005:2948: thod rus rkang dang 'bru mar khrag /
NK038(nyi)005:2949: chang dang a mri ta sbyar ba //
NK038(nyi)005:2950: rdzu 'phrul grub pa'i rdzas mchog bzhes //
NK038(nyi)005:2951: rin chen mi mo ma rung pa //
NK038(nyi)005:2952: sha chen bshang gci khu ba khrag /
NK038(nyi)005:2954: bdag gi rims nad bzlog tu gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:2955: dmigs bya 'di la rim nad thong //
NK038(nyi)005:2956: srid pa'i bud med ma rung khyed //
NK038(nyi)005:2957: bro gar glu tshig mchod pa bzhes //
NK038(nyi)005:2958: dmigs bya 'jo sgeg stobs kyis phrogs //
NK038(nyi)005:2959: shor ba gzhon nu bdud mo'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:2960: rnal 'byor chen po'i bka' byung gi /
NK038(nyi)005:2961: sngags sgra rang gi mchod pa bzhes //
NK038(nyi)005:2962: dmigs bya'i phung po rdul du rlog /
NK038(nyi)005:2963: log bsred can gyi tshogs rnams nyon //
NK038(nyi)005:2964: yang dag ngang du kun rig na //
NK038(nyi)005:2965: che chung las gnyis gang byas kyang //
NK038(nyi)005:2966: gnyis kyi dbang du mi 'gyur gyis //
NK038(nyi)005:2968: gsang tshig rten pa'i tshogs rnams nyon //
NK038(nyi)005:2969: bshang gci khrag dang gsol khu'i gso //
NK038(nyi)005:2970: bargya'am stong du gnas so ni //
NK038(nyi)005:2972: dam rdzas mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK038(nyi)005:2973: bcol pa'i las rnams grub par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)005:2974: mnga' bdag chen po ma rungs pa //
NK038(nyi)005:2975: rdo rje sems dpa' sprul pa ste //
NK038(nyi)005:2976: khro bo'i rgyal po gying chen po //
NK038(nyi)005:2977: mnga' bdag bdud kyi rgyal po zhes //
NK038(nyi)005:2978: rnal 'byor chen po ngas bstod cing //
NK038(nyi)005:2979: khyed la mthun pa'i rdzas phul bas //
NK038(nyi)005:2980: sngon gyi bskal pa bzang po la //
NK038(nyi)005:2981: mkhas blangs dam bcas mna' bor ba'i //
NK038(nyi)005:2982: sngon du rig 'dzin gong mas sgrubs //
NK038(nyi)005:2983: da lta rnal 'byor bdag sgrub pas //
NK038(nyi)005:2984: bam ri thod pa'i mkhar gyi rtser //
NK038(nyi)005:2985: ru mtshon nag po pu ru ru //
NK038(nyi)005:2986: mtshon cha nag po char du 'bab //
NK038(nyi)005:2987: bdud bya nag po lding zhing 'jum //
NK038(nyi)005:2988: dur khrod mang po'i rgyan rnams rdzogs //
NK038(nyi)005:2989: mche ba tsegs rngam pa'i zhal gdengs nas /
NK038(nyi)005:2990: khro bo khro mo'i sprul pa 'khrigs //
NK038(nyi)005:2991: srin po pho mo rkan sgra sdebs //
NK038(nyi)005:2992: gnod sbyin pho mo 'brug sgra sgrogs //
NK038(nyi)005:2993: za byed ma mo glog ltar 'khyug /
NK038(nyi)005:2994: so so mos pa tha dad pa'i //
NK038(nyi)005:2995: yid bzhin nor bu'i dam tshig 'di //
NK038(nyi)005:2996: yongs su rdzogs par blang bar bya'o //
NK038(nyi)005:2997: bur kur ma h+aa k+aa la //
NK038(nyi)005:2998: e ho shwo mo kro ta ma h+aa mam sa kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)005:3001: ma h+aa ba su ta kh+aa h+ai /
NK038(nyi)005:3003: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)005:3004: sarba sha t+r+aum m+aa ra ya kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)005:3005: zhes chos srung nyid la phul bas mnyes par bsam mo //
NK038(nyi)005:3006: 'khor bzhi bo la yang bskyed sngags la mchod sngags dbul lo //
NK038(nyi)005:3008: 'bangs la nan tan ma chung zhig /
NK038(nyi)005:3009: de nas slan chad bka' bzhin du //
NK038(nyi)005:3010: bka' lung bzhin du rjes su bsgrub //
NK038(nyi)005:3011: gal te bka' bzhin ma bgyis na //
NK038(nyi)005:3013: bdag cag rnams kyi mgo lus snying //
NK038(nyi)005:3015: ma dang sring mo bud med rnams //
NK038(nyi)005:3017: dbus su mchis skal mi ldan gyis //
NK038(nyi)005:3019: phud la 'tshal skal mi ldan gyis //
NK038(nyi)005:3020: lhag ma'i kha chus bran la gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:3021: nye gnas gdung ba'i ma sring rnams //
NK038(nyi)005:3022: deng nas rgyal ba'i 'bangs yin gyis //
NK038(nyi)005:3023: khyed kyi ci bgyis bka' yi las mkhan te //
NK038(nyi)005:3024: bka' yi las byung rtag par myur du sgrubs //
NK038(nyi)005:3025: zhes pas rang gi dam bcas pa bzhin du /
NK038(nyi)005:3026: dam tshig la gnas par khas blangs so //
NK038(nyi)005:3027: ru lu ru lu b+h+yo zhes srog la tshad bzung nas mna' skyal lo //
NK038(nyi)005:3028: de nas dam bsre ba ni /
NK038(nyi)005:3029: rdo rje dri yi bdud rtsi mchog /
NK038(nyi)005:3030: pany+tsa a mri ta dang sbyar /
NK038(nyi)005:3031: bsre ba'i mchog de srog gi snying /
NK038(nyi)005:3032: snying dang snying gi spun du bya'o //
NK038(nyi)005:3033: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta sa ma ya th+aa /
NK038(nyi)005:3034: zhes bdud rtsi gtor bas kyang bdag gi lan gsum zos /
NK038(nyi)005:3035: mgon pos kyang lan gsum zos nas dam las mi
NK038(nyi)005:3036: 'da' bar bdag gi dper na grogs 'dra bas sdong
NK038(nyi)005:3037: grogs byas ste ga cig gi gcig ngo bor gyur
NK038(nyi)005:3038: bar bsam mo // dam brdar ba ni /
NK038(nyi)005:3039: ma h+aa gling gi bsgrub gnas su //
NK038(nyi)005:3040: rdo rje srin po'i spyan snga ru //
NK038(nyi)005:3041: ji ltar khas blangs dam bcas pa'i //
NK038(nyi)005:3042: dam tshig gnyen po ma 'da' cig /
NK038(nyi)005:3043: ma h+aa k+aa la ma h+aa pany+tsa sa ma s+t+wam /
NK038(nyi)005:3045: brtse bar byed na ma ru bya'o //
NK038(nyi)005:3046: gdung bar byed na sring mo ste /
NK038(nyi)005:3047: brtson par byed na bran du bya'o //
NK038(nyi)005:3048: byang chub dag na bur bya'o //
NK038(nyi)005:3050: bskul bar mgyog na pho nyar bya'o //
NK038(nyi)005:3051: bka' bzhin byed na bka' la btags //
NK038(nyi)005:3052: zhes dpa' bos zhal gyis bzhes pa'o //
NK038(nyi)005:3053: h'u kun las za ba'i bdud po che /
NK038(nyi)005:3055: de yi de 'dul mngag gzhug go //
NK038(nyi)005:3056: gzhan la srid ni za bar byed //
NK038(nyi)005:3057: nga ni stobs chen dpal chen po //
NK038(nyi)005:3058: gzhan gyi log rtog 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)005:3059: zil gyis mnan cing dbang du bsdu //
NK038(nyi)005:3064: ru tra ma tra ha ha ham /
NK038(nyi)005:3065: dpa' bo chen pos zil gyis mnan nas dbang du bsdus pa'o //
NK038(nyi)005:3066: dpa' bo'i mdun na 'dar khri li li 'dug nas bka' nyan gsung sdod byed par bsam mo //
NK038(nyi)005:3067: bsnyen pa la 'jug pa'i phyir 'dzab bstod bya ba ni /
NK038(nyi)005:3068: h'u nyon mongs lnga 'joms drag po sku lnga po /
NK038(nyi)005:3069: rang la khro bo'i dgongs pa kun 'dus dpa' bo ste /
NK038(nyi)005:3070: dpa' bo las ni chags med chen po mchog /
NK038(nyi)005:3071: dpa' bos rol zhig dmigs bya'i snying la rol //
NK038(nyi)005:3072: dmigs bya rlag byed chu bo gang ga ltar //
NK038(nyi)005:3073: rgyun mi chad par dmigs bya dga' bar rol //
NK038(nyi)005:3074: ma rungs khros pas nyon mongs dug gsum 'joms //
NK038(nyi)005:3075: de nyid kyis ni de nyid gsum bsregs shing //
NK038(nyi)005:3076: gnas 'dir shog la dam tshig srungs //
NK038(nyi)005:3077: bsgrub pa po la dngos grub stsol //
NK038(nyi)005:3078: sdang ba'i dgra la rtags chen phyung //
NK038(nyi)005:3079: gnod pa'i bgegs chen rdul du bzlog /
NK038(nyi)005:3081: bur kur ma h+aa pad+ma rde 'bur tsi 'bur byi
NK038(nyi)005:3082: ge ma na se e ho sho mo kro ta
NK038(nyi)005:3083: h'u h'u h'u phata phata phata s+w+aa h+aa /
NK038(nyi)005:3085: bdag dpal chen por gsal ba'i thugs kha nas 'od zer lcags kyu'i dbyibs lta bu 'phros te /
NK038(nyi)005:3086: nag po chen po 'khor dang bcas pa bam ri
NK038(nyi)005:3087: thod pa mkhar na gnas pa'i snying ka nas bzung
NK038(nyi)005:3088: nas mdun du bkug la bskyed pa dang gnyis su
NK038(nyi)005:3090: de na gnas pa'i de rnams bka' nyan gsung sdod
NK038(nyi)005:3091: de ring phan chad las ci bgyi zer bar bsam
NK038(nyi)005:3092: zhing mgon po zhi ba'i zhal dang ldan par bsams
NK038(nyi)005:3093: shing 'bum mtsho gcig la bsnyen pa'i tshad du bzlas
NK038(nyi)005:3094: par bya'o // stong stong thon pa dang thon mchod bya ste //
NK038(nyi)005:3095: tshogs rje tshogs bdag dpal chen he ru ka /
NK038(nyi)005:3096: 'bar ba'i rgyal po khrag 'thung lnga bcu rtsa brgyad la /
NK038(nyi)005:3097: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK038(nyi)005:3098: thugs rje brtse dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK038(nyi)005:3099: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta sh+r+ai ban kha hi //
NK038(nyi)005:3100: rnal 'byor yongs kyi bstan pa bsrung bar zhal 'ches pa'i //
NK038(nyi)005:3101: dpal ldan mgon po 'khor bcas la //
NK038(nyi)005:3102: rnam dag bdud rtsi'i mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK038(nyi)005:3103: thugs rje che dgongs gtso 'khor lnga'i rang sngags la /
NK038(nyi)005:3104: ma h+aa pa ny+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi btags la sman mchod bya /
NK038(nyi)005:3105: gtor ma dang rak+ta'i mchod pa yang 'bul zhir sman rag sbreng ngo //
NK038(nyi)005:3106: sngon tshe dpal gyi tshogs gdung dbyangs kyi bskul /
NK038(nyi)005:3107: de nas ldang bar 'dod na gsur chen btang /
NK038(nyi)005:3109: rak+ta dang phud kyi mchod pa phul bdag badz+ra he ru ka cha gnyis gsal bar bsgom la /
NK038(nyi)005:3110: gcig phyung la spyod lam rnams bzhi ci bder bya'o //
NK038(nyi)005:3111: de nas bzlas pa la 'jug na yang /
NK038(nyi)005:3112: dkyil 'khor lha tshogs dang chos srung 'khor dang bcas pa la gong ma ltar mchod pa phul la /
NK038(nyi)005:3113: bdag nyid dpal chen po la phar thim par bsam la bzlas pa bya'o //
NK038(nyi)005:3114: de ni thun mtshams gyi cho ga'o //
NK038(nyi)005:3115: da ni nye ba'i snyen pa bya ste /
NK038(nyi)005:3116: phrin las gzhung bsrang ba la sogs pa'i bsnyen pa mthun /
NK038(nyi)005:3117: bsnyen pa'i sngags lan gsum brjod la /
NK038(nyi)005:3118: de nas nye bsnyen gyi sngags la 'jug par bya ste /
NK038(nyi)005:3119: bdag nyid dpal chen po sems dpa' sum brtseg dang
NK038(nyi)005:3120: ldan pa'i nga rgyal gyis 'dzab bstod bya ba ni
NK038(nyi)005:3121: / snying rje lnga yi drag po lnga 'joms pa //
NK038(nyi)005:3122: sangs rgyas kun gyi bka' yi phrin las yin //
NK038(nyi)005:3123: drag po'i las 'di bka' yi man ngag gzhug go //
NK038(nyi)005:3124: myur bar myur bar rno bas yid kyi dbang po phyung //
NK038(nyi)005:3125: khyod kyi drag po'i phrin las rgyun mi chad //
NK038(nyi)005:3126: lus tshig sems khros dmigs bya ma btang zhig /
NK038(nyi)005:3127: khyod kyi ljang sngon drag po gsal shing can //
NK038(nyi)005:3128: khyod kyi dmigs bya dam nyams 'di //
NK038(nyi)005:3129: rten dang brten pa gnyis ka zo //
NK038(nyi)005:3130: kha 'dzin skyabs byed gnyis ka chom //
NK038(nyi)005:3131: rnam shes sprod la sha khrag bsregs //
NK038(nyi)005:3133: bsgrub pa sdang ba'i gnod pa'i de nas gzungs thag
NK038(nyi)005:3134: rten la btags pa de lag tu thogs la sngags
NK038(nyi)005:3135: bzlas te / bdag dpal chen po gsal ba'i thugs ka nas ye shes sems dpa' /
NK038(nyi)005:3136: de'i thugs ka nas ting nge 'dzin sems dpa'i rang
NK038(nyi)005:3137: bzhin gyi yi ge h'u la sngags kyi bskor ba
NK038(nyi)005:3138: las 'od zer byung ste srog rtsa nas yar byung
NK038(nyi)005:3139: / sna'i ye shes kyi rlung las sna'i rtse mor byung tsa na /
NK038(nyi)005:3140: ye shes kyi rlung ring po las mgon po ljang
NK038(nyi)005:3141: sngon gsal shing lag na thogs pa rgyud mar spros
NK038(nyi)005:3142: la mkhar gyi nang na me'i mgon po la bstim
NK038(nyi)005:3143: la / nang na mo nus pa bskyed pa ni bsgom pa'o //
NK038(nyi)005:3145: b+hu ru ku rma a kra na bu tsi ki byi ma na se /
NK038(nyi)005:3146: kha shog mgo kro d+ha h'u phata s+w+aa h+aa /
NK038(nyi)005:3147: mkhar nag gi skud pa la dar nag gi khud du dum bu gsum byas te /
NK038(nyi)005:3150: tha ma tsan dan dang sman sna tshogs dang bdud rtsi'o //
NK038(nyi)005:3151: gzungs thag la btags pa 'jog pa'i dus su /
NK038(nyi)005:3152: thum po tha ma sman gyi thum po kha phye
NK038(nyi)005:3153: ste bag tsam zhig blugs te 'jug gtor mkhar gyi
NK038(nyi)005:3154: nang na mo la byas pas sku'i tsha ba gzhil
NK038(nyi)005:3155: bar bsam mo // stong stong bzlas shing mchod pa
NK038(nyi)005:3156: re byas pa'i sngags 'bum tsho ga cig bzlas pa
NK038(nyi)005:3157: ni bsnyen pa'i man ngag go //
NK038(nyi)005:3158: thun mtshams gyi cho ga dang mthun no //
NK038(nyi)005:3160: 'phrin las gzhung bsrang ba la sogs gong dang mthun
NK038(nyi)005:3161: bdag dpal chen po'i nga rgyal dang ldan pas 'dzab
NK038(nyi)005:3162: stod bya ste / bzhi pa lnga ni bskul ba lnga //
NK038(nyi)005:3163: bzhi po lnga ni bka' sdod lnga //
NK038(nyi)005:3164: bskul ba lnga ni rgyal ba lnga //
NK038(nyi)005:3165: de ni sangs rgyas phrin las yin //
NK038(nyi)005:3166: de nyid seng ge lta bu ste //
NK038(nyi)005:3167: 'brug ltar sgrog pa'i nga ro can //
NK038(nyi)005:3168: glog ltar 'khyug pa'i khro bo yin //
NK038(nyi)005:3169: de yi de snying brlag par bya //
NK038(nyi)005:3171: sgrub pa po la dngos grub stsol //
NK038(nyi)005:3172: sdang ba'i gnod pa'i zhes brjod la bsgom pa'i rim
NK038(nyi)005:3173: pa ni thum po bar pa yungs dkar thum po
NK038(nyi)005:3174: kha phye ste / mkhar gyi nang na me la bskul te /
NK038(nyi)005:3175: mkhar gyi mgon po la brabs pas de gdug pa'i
NK038(nyi)005:3176: sems skyes dgra bgegs bkug nas lid+ga bstim pa ni
NK038(nyi)005:3178: stong stong thon pa dang stong mchod bya /
NK038(nyi)005:3179: ma 'phang ma g.yel gyis snang srid lha 'dre la dpang gzugs /
NK038(nyi)005:3180: snang srid lha 'dre dmag du bran zhing bskang ba bya'o //
NK038(nyi)005:3181: thun mtshams kyi cho ga gong dang mthun no //
NK038(nyi)005:3182: bur kur i tsi ki byi u tsu sh+ma kro ta h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)005:3184: dpal dang bka' sdod pho nya btang /
NK038(nyi)005:3185: bsgrub pa chen po'i phrin las gzhung bsrang ba la
NK038(nyi)005:3186: sogs pa bsnyen pa dang mthun dpal gyi nga rgyal
NK038(nyi)005:3187: dang ldan pas 'dzab bstod bya ste /
NK038(nyi)005:3188: de nyid lhun gyis grub pas na dpa' bos de nyid gdeng du 'gyur /
NK038(nyi)005:3189: de nyid bdag gi dbang du bsdus //
NK038(nyi)005:3190: las la the tshom med par 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)005:3191: bsgrub pa la bstod dngos grub stsol //
NK038(nyi)005:3192: sdang ba'i dgra la gnod pa'i bgegs chen /
NK038(nyi)005:3193: bdag nyid dpal chen po'i nga rgyal dang ldan pas
NK038(nyi)005:3194: thum po dang po rak+ta'i thum po kha phye ste
NK038(nyi)005:3195: / rak+ta'i nang du bag tsam zhig blugs la bzlas pa la 'jug pa'i dus su /
NK038(nyi)005:3196: mkhar gyi mgon po la brabs pas /
NK038(nyi)005:3197: de gdug pa'i sems skyes te /
NK038(nyi)005:3198: rgyas pa'i dgra bo rnams khram la btab nas /
NK038(nyi)005:3199: de'i phan byed kyi lha dang bral nas sdug bsngal
NK038(nyi)005:3200: zhing skyabs med par skra shig nas rengs par 'dug
NK038(nyi)005:3201: pa ni bsgrub pa chen po'i bsam rgyud do //
NK038(nyi)005:3203: zhes bsgrub pa chen po la 'bum tsho cig bskyal lo //
NK038(nyi)005:3204: dus bzhir tshogs kyi mchod pa dang /
NK038(nyi)005:3206: dus bzhir bskul ba bya zhing dus bzhir zor 'phang /
NK038(nyi)005:3207: gzu dpang gsol zhing dgra bo lha dang bral /
NK038(nyi)005:3208: bsgrub pa chen po'i man ngag go bsnyen bsgrub bzhi'i las byang /
NK038(nyi)005:3210: bzhi snying gcig tu dril ba 'di la gtsor byed de /
NK038(nyi)005:3211: b+hu kur i tsi ki phyi /
NK038(nyi)005:3212: u tsu sh+ma kro ta che ge mo sarba sha trum m+aa ra ya h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)005:3213: yak+sha dz+wa la sa ma ya che ge mo sarba sha trum ma ra ya h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)005:3214: tsit+ta dz+wa la kro ta dz+wa la yak+sha dz+wa la sarba sha trum m+aa ra ya h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)005:3215: 'gre las la sbyor ba'i dus su dpal dang bka'
NK038(nyi)005:3216: sdod kyi bskyed rim la sogs pa bskyed rim bsgrub
NK038(nyi)005:3217: pa dang mthun / tshogs dang bskang ba /
NK038(nyi)005:3220: gzu dpang gsol ba lha dang dbral ba la sogs pa bsgrub pa chen po dang mthun /
NK038(nyi)005:3221: bdag dpal chen por gsal bas /
NK038(nyi)005:3222: zil gyis mnon pa'i tshig dang sngags kyis gong dang mthun par zil gyis mnan /
NK038(nyi)005:3223: bsnyen bsgrub bzhi'i sngags shas tsam bzlas la /
NK038(nyi)005:3224: de nas las sbyor gyi dus su bzhi snying cig dril ba'i sngags /
NK038(nyi)005:3225: b+hur kur i tsi ki phyi u tsu sh+ma kro
NK038(nyi)005:3226: ta che ge mo sarba sha trum m+aa ra ya
NK038(nyi)005:3227: h'u phata / ces sngags re bzlas pa'i dus su
NK038(nyi)005:3228: bdag dpal du gsal ba'i thugs kar 'od zer kha
NK038(nyi)005:3230: mdun gyi mgon po la thim /
NK038(nyi)005:3231: de'i thugs ka nas mgon po sku mdog ljang sngon
NK038(nyi)005:3232: phyag na gsal shing thogs pa bsam gyis mi khyab
NK038(nyi)005:3236: gcan zan mche ba can dang 'phar ba dang /
NK038(nyi)005:3237: dred mong la sogs pa bsam gyis mi khyab par sprul nas /
NK038(nyi)005:3238: gtso dang 'khor bcas pa'i sprul pas 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad khengs pas /
NK038(nyi)005:3239: de'i dmigs bya'i dgra bgegs gang na gnas kyang bkug nas lid+ga la stim ste /
NK038(nyi)005:3240: de nas bsgral bar bsam mo //
NK038(nyi)005:3241: yang na so sor yul lugs dang /
NK038(nyi)005:3242: bsad lugs las sbyor chen mo na gsal lo //
NK038(nyi)005:3243: badz+ra kro ta dz+wa la sa ma ya che ge
NK038(nyi)005:3244: mo sarba sha trum ma ra ya h'u h'u phata
NK038(nyi)005:3245: / 'khor gyi sngags gang bzlos kyang rang rang gi
NK038(nyi)005:3246: sprul pa bsam gyis mi khyab pas bsgrub bya'i dgra
NK038(nyi)005:3247: bgegs thams cad bsgral bar bsam mo //
NK038(nyi)005:3248: bka' sdod kyi bsgyu thabs zhal gdams su bkod pa /
NK038(nyi)005:3250: dang po bsnyen pa'i dus su thugs dam gyi rten
NK038(nyi)005:3251: phyogs bzhi dbus dang lngar dar mthing nag gi gur
NK038(nyi)005:3252: dbub pa'am / yang na man+dala gru bzhi pa'i steng
NK038(nyi)005:3253: du dur khrod kyi tshon rtsi dmar pos bkab pa
NK038(nyi)005:3254: ni mtsho ko ka thang dmar po de'i steng du
NK038(nyi)005:3255: sdom sdig rmigs pa sbrul 'gram mo //
NK038(nyi)005:3256: de nas dpangs su sor bzhi zur gsum rtse mo nub tu bstan pa'i nang du ling+ga bzhag /
NK038(nyi)005:3257: tshad dang ldan pa'i mkhar brtsigs la /
NK038(nyi)005:3260: bya khyung gnyis kyis brgyan pa'o //
NK038(nyi)005:3262: nam mkha' sngon po g.yu mig can //
NK038(nyi)005:3263: mkhar gyi thon khu pa su bzhug go //
NK038(nyi)005:3264: mtho khung gi thod tshal sor bzhi pa'i nang du
NK038(nyi)005:3265: 'bru mar chang dang a mri sbyar ba bzhag go
NK038(nyi)005:3266: // de nas phyogs bzhir zur gsum lid+ga dang bcas pa /
NK038(nyi)005:3267: lhor gnod sbyin gyi mkhar du ru skyogs bzhag /
NK038(nyi)005:3268: byang du za byed pa'i steng du dar mthing gi sbra dang /
NK038(nyi)005:3269: khrag sna tshogs pa'i gtor ma bzhag /
NK038(nyi)005:3270: byang du khro bo rnams kyi rten du phur pa
NK038(nyi)005:3271: dmar nag dar gyi cod pan can bco brgyad bzhag
NK038(nyi)005:3272: / nub tu srin po'i rten rabs chad nag po'i thod pa gling bzhi pa bzhag /
NK038(nyi)005:3273: de ni rtsa ba'i man+dala lho nub tu bzhag go //
NK038(nyi)005:3274: lho phyogs 'brub khung gi dal bya //
NK038(nyi)005:3276: gtad khram kyi dkyil 'khor tshad ldan pa'i khar gru gsum pa steng bya khyung gi brgyan pa /
NK038(nyi)005:3277: khro bo chen po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa gsal shing thogs pa /
NK038(nyi)005:3280: mtshan ma sbreng ba nub tu bzhag go //
NK038(nyi)005:3281: bka' sdod kyi man+dala ni 'jig rten pa'i bsnyen pa'i dus su ru las tshogs bdag 'khor bcas bskyed /
NK038(nyi)005:3282: dbus kyi gtso bo zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa g.yas gri gug /
NK038(nyi)005:3284: de nas drag po'i gnas gdug pa bkug nas stim la /
NK038(nyi)005:3286: g.yas dang po na lcag kyu /
NK038(nyi)005:3287: g.yon dang po na gsal shing /
NK038(nyi)005:3288: g.yon tha ma na thod pa /
NK038(nyi)005:3289: g.yas tha ma na gri gug /
NK038(nyi)005:3290: de nas tshogs zhes pa nas bzung du gsol zhes
NK038(nyi)005:3291: pa'i bar gyis gsol ba gdab pa dang gsum pa'o
NK038(nyi)005:3292: // de nas sngags kyi sgrib pa sbyang ste bzhi pa'o //
NK038(nyi)005:3293: mi ldog par spro ba bskyed pa dang lnga //
NK038(nyi)005:3294: 'jug par khas blangs pa dang drug /
NK038(nyi)005:3295: dus med par de'i yon tan bstan pa dang bdun /
NK038(nyi)005:3296: de nas yi ge gcig phyag btsal ba'o //
NK038(nyi)005:3297: yi ge gcig gi dbang bskur cig par gsol ba gdab pa'o //
NK038(nyi)005:3298: de nas sngags des dbang bskur ba'o //
NK038(nyi)005:3299: dbang blangs ba dang bcu pa'o //
NK038(nyi)005:3300: dbang yon dbul ba dang bcu gcig /
NK038(nyi)005:3301: mnga' gsol pa tsa btab pa dang bcu gnyis rang
NK038(nyi)005:3302: gi mthun pa'i dam rdzas dbul ba dang bcu gsum
NK038(nyi)005:3303: / dam mnos pa dang bcu bzhi /
NK038(nyi)005:3304: mna' skyal ba dang bco lnga /
NK038(nyi)005:3305: srog la tshad gzugs pa dang bcu drug /
NK038(nyi)005:3306: dam tshig bsre ba dang bcu bdun //
NK038(nyi)005:3307: zil gyis mnan pa dang bco brgyad do //
NK038(nyi)005:3308: de dag gi bsnyen pa'i don chen tshol ba zhes bya'o //
NK038(nyi)005:3309: de nas tshon skud lag tu blangs la /
NK038(nyi)005:3310: sngags kyi tshad rdzogs pa dang /
NK038(nyi)005:3311: sna'i bu ga'i h'u ring las ljang sngon drag po gsal shing can spros te /
NK038(nyi)005:3312: lha chen po dang gnyis med bstim pa ni /
NK038(nyi)005:3314: de nas thum po bar ma kha phye ste mkhar
NK038(nyi)005:3315: gyi glo dkar gyi nang du khro bo chen po
NK038(nyi)005:3316: la las bgyid par bskul ba ni sgrub pa ni
NK038(nyi)005:3318: de nas smad du byung ba ste bsgrub pa chen po bya ba dang /
NK038(nyi)005:3319: zil gyis mnan pa'i sngags khri 'bum mam stong rtsa brgyad bzlas shing /
NK038(nyi)005:3322: rab tu khros pa'i sems kyis byas nas /
NK038(nyi)005:3323: thal chen tshom bu zhag gi zo ris byas nas /
NK038(nyi)005:3325: ha hi hi zhes rta skad byas pas de dag gi 'jig rten pa bsgrub pa rdzogs so //////
NK038(nyi)005:3326: dpal mgon legs ldan bsgrub pa bzhugs so //
NK038(nyi)005:3327: bcom ldan rdo rje srin po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)005:3328: dpal mgon po legs ldan nag po bsgrub par 'dod pas /
NK038(nyi)005:3329: ru lu'i bsnyen rdzogs par byas te /
NK038(nyi)005:3331: ru lu rtsa ba'i sngags dag la /
NK038(nyi)005:3332: 'bum mam bye ba'i bar du bzlas /
NK038(nyi)005:3334: de ltar ye shes kyi bsnyen pa bye ba rdzogs nas /
NK038(nyi)005:3335: dpal mgon po bsgrub pa'i rim pa la 'jug ste /
NK038(nyi)005:3337: dang po bsod nams kyi dpung bskyed pa ni /
NK038(nyi)005:3339: de bzhin nyid kyi 'byor pa'i yo byad la /
NK038(nyi)005:3340: rnam gsum tshal du nan tan bya'o //
NK038(nyi)005:3345: gnyis pa bsgrub pa'i cha rkyen ni /
NK038(nyi)005:3347: rtags dang rten ni gzhung ltar bshams /
NK038(nyi)005:3349: rtags ni mgon po'i bris sku dang /
NK038(nyi)005:3350: bsnyen phur pa 'jigs shing rngams pa'i cha byad do //
NK038(nyi)005:3354: snying chen la sogs pa bshams /
NK038(nyi)005:3355: gsum pa bsnyen bsgrub kyi rim /
NK038(nyi)005:3356: phyag rgya dngos grub dkyil 'khor gong du khrig gzhan
NK038(nyi)005:3357: ma byas na thun mong khyad par can gyi mchod
NK038(nyi)005:3361: mchod pa byin gyis brlab so /
NK038(nyi)005:3363: dang po ting 'dzin ni chos thams cad skye med stong pa nyid dmigs med du bsgom /
NK038(nyi)005:3364: kun ting ni ye shes sgyu ma lta bu ma 'gags par bsgom /
NK038(nyi)005:3365: rgyu ting ni rang rig pa mdun gyi nam mkha' la h'u mthing nag /
NK038(nyi)005:3366: h'u de las e ham ram kem ram /
NK038(nyi)005:3367: ces pas dbang chen 'byung ba rim brtseg bskyed /
NK038(nyi)005:3368: yang h'u yig de las b+h+aum cig chad /
NK038(nyi)005:3370: b+h+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he ban+d+ha dz+ny+aa na tsakra man+dala /
NK038(nyi)005:3373: ti ra bam zhes pas khro bo'i gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa bskyed /
NK038(nyi)005:3374: h'u zhes pas h'u de dbus kyi gdan thog tu h'u sgril ma lngar gyur /
NK038(nyi)005:3378: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da
NK038(nyi)005:3379: sarba dush+tam ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa
NK038(nyi)005:3381: badz+ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri sa ma ya stam /
NK038(nyi)005:3382: de rnams sku mdog phyag mtshan sngags rnams dam pa brgyan ltar bskyed /
NK038(nyi)005:3383: zhes rigs kyi gtso bo yab yum lnga'i sku gsal bar bskyed do //
NK038(nyi)005:3384: thugs ka'i ye shes sems dpa' gtso bo ltar du mnyam du bskyed /
NK038(nyi)005:3385: 'khor rnams ni rang rang gi yig 'bru las bskyed /
NK038(nyi)005:3386: ye shes lngas dbang bskur sku gsung thugs su byin gyis rlabs /
NK038(nyi)005:3387: de nas snyan gsan dbab ste /
NK038(nyi)005:3388: ye shes spyan gyi spyod yul na //
NK038(nyi)005:3389: dpal chen khrag thung 'khor dang bcas //
NK038(nyi)005:3390: sems can don phyir dam tshig dgos //
NK038(nyi)005:3391: gnas 'dir ma lus gshegs su gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:3392: badz+ra sa ma ya h'u dzah spyan drangs pa ni /
NK038(nyi)005:3393: snyigs ma lnga yi dus kyi tha ma la /
NK038(nyi)005:3394: las kyi mnar ba'i sdang ba'i dgra dang bgegs //
NK038(nyi)005:3395: thugs rjes bsgral ba'i skal dang mi ldan yang //
NK038(nyi)005:3396: shugs kyi bsgral ba'i phrin las mdzad 'tshal gyis //
NK038(nyi)005:3397: gtum rngams bsgral ba'i tshogs chen ma lus rnams //
NK038(nyi)005:3398: bdag cag brtse bas mchod pa dbul ba'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)005:3399: dus gsum rgyal ba ma lus gshegs su gsol //
NK038(nyi)005:3400: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK038(nyi)005:3401: e h+yi a na ya hoh dzahmh'u bam ho ram
NK038(nyi)005:3402: zhes me ri 'dab 'byor du byon par bsam mo
NK038(nyi)005:3403: spyan drangs so // badz+ra kro ta sa ma ya h'u /
NK038(nyi)005:3404: zhes rig pa'i me tog dor ro //
NK038(nyi)005:3407: rdo rje srin pos bdud rnams 'dul mdzad pa /
NK038(nyi)005:3408: bdud dang dregs pa'i tshogs rnams 'dul mdzad phyir //
NK038(nyi)005:3409: thugs rje 'bar ba'i byin rlabs bsam yas pa'i //
NK038(nyi)005:3410: dbang dang dngos grub rab tu stsol //
NK038(nyi)005:3411: badz+ra dri ldan du mchod pa rak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK038(nyi)005:3412: badz+ra kro ta shwa ri a ha ra /
NK038(nyi)005:3417: p+au ny+tsa h'u h'u he he phata b+h+yo ram zhes stim /
NK038(nyi)005:3418: badz+ra rak+sha ma h+aa rak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK038(nyi)005:3419: ma h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)005:3420: sarba dush+tam sa ma ya mu tra pra ban tsakra h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)005:3421: k+aa ya wak+ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra /
NK038(nyi)005:3422: bdag de ltar he ru ka'i rang bzhin gsal ba'i
NK038(nyi)005:3423: mdun du khar dang lcags khang la sogs pa stong
NK038(nyi)005:3424: pa'i ngang las bam cig zhu ba las bam rak+ta
NK038(nyi)005:3426: zhes brjod pas rak+ta'i rgya mtsho chen por bsam /
NK038(nyi)005:3427: de'i steng du ri bo ma la ya de'i tshul
NK038(nyi)005:3428: du bsam pa'i steng du thod khar chen po bsam
NK038(nyi)005:3431: dur khrod chen po rab 'jigs pa'i //
NK038(nyi)005:3432: mtsho ni ko ka thang dmar na //
NK038(nyi)005:3433: ri bo byan rlag 'chongs kyi ri //
NK038(nyi)005:3434: gnam lcags yod pa'i rtse mo na //
NK038(nyi)005:3435: keng rus thod pa mkhar du brtsigs //
NK038(nyi)005:3436: 'jigs pa'i thod khar ldems se ldem //
NK038(nyi)005:3437: shar phyogs bam ri stag thod mkhar //
NK038(nyi)005:3438: stag thod 'dzum mdangs mu lu lu //
NK038(nyi)005:3439: lho phyogs bam ri mi thod mkhar //
NK038(nyi)005:3440: mi thod spyugs pa kyu ru ru //
NK038(nyi)005:3441: nub phyogs bam ri rta thod mkhar //
NK038(nyi)005:3442: rta thod mtsher gdangs lhangs se lhang //
NK038(nyi)005:3443: byang phyogs bam ril bya thod mkhar //
NK038(nyi)005:3444: bya thod tsig sgra di ri ri //
NK038(nyi)005:3445: srin po'i thod pas kha bad can //
NK038(nyi)005:3447: ngos la nga rgyal glog chen 'khyugs //
NK038(nyi)005:3448: rtse la bdud bya nag po lding //
NK038(nyi)005:3449: ru mtshon nag po pu ru ru //
NK038(nyi)005:3450: gnam lcags 'bar ba'i sgo mo gsal //
NK038(nyi)005:3451: 'jigs pa'i sku mkhar nang shed na //
NK038(nyi)005:3452: mi ro mang po khri ru brtsigs //
NK038(nyi)005:3453: rta ro mang po bcal du dgram //
NK038(nyi)005:3454: mi ro rta ro'i khri steng na //
NK038(nyi)005:3456: de nas mkhar gyi lcags ma khang 'bar ba'i nang du ru /
NK038(nyi)005:3457: shar gyi lcags khang du ba /
NK038(nyi)005:3458: byang gi lcags khang du ma /
NK038(nyi)005:3460: nub kyi lcags khang du ra bsam /
NK038(nyi)005:3465: zhes brjod pas ru zhu ba las gri gug tu bsam /
NK038(nyi)005:3467: bur kur ma h+aa k+aa la sa ma ya h'u /
NK038(nyi)005:3468: ces pas mgon po gri gug thod khrag can bya'i gshog pa can bskyed /
NK038(nyi)005:3469: rang rang gi yi ge rnams las 'khor rnams gur chen mo ltar bskyed /
NK038(nyi)005:3470: de nas mgon po dgug pa ni /
NK038(nyi)005:3471: rang lhar gsal ba'i thugs ka nas 'od zer lcags
NK038(nyi)005:3472: kyu rnams lta bu 'phros te lcags kyu'i phyag rgya
NK038(nyi)005:3473: bcas te / ru lu ru lu h'u phata b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)005:3474: bur kur ma h+aa k+aa la sa ma ya hrim hrim /
NK038(nyi)005:3475: am gu sha dza dzahzhesa brjod pas /
NK038(nyi)005:3476: mtsho ko ka thang dmar ri ma la ya'i rtse nas /
NK038(nyi)005:3477: rang rgyud pa'i mgon po'i snying kha nas lcags kyu'i bzung nas mdun du bkug par bsam mo //
NK038(nyi)005:3478: tshig gi spyan drangs pa ni /
NK038(nyi)005:3479: lad+ga yul gyi grong brdal gyi /
NK038(nyi)005:3481: gnas 'dir ma lus gshegs su gsol /
NK038(nyi)005:3482: ces pa yan gyi drang ngo //
NK038(nyi)005:3483: zhal du rngubs te sna nas gdon pa ni /
NK038(nyi)005:3484: badz+ra rak+sha ma ha sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sarba du sh+tam /
NK038(nyi)005:3485: sa ma ya mu tra a sa s+t+wam pa ya ka h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)005:3488: rak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka ru tra ma tra /
NK038(nyi)005:3490: ces pas sna nas bton nas /
NK038(nyi)005:3491: bur kur ma h+aa ka la sa ma ya pra be sha phata /
NK038(nyi)005:3492: a se a zhes pas gong du bskyed pa'i mgon po bstim /
NK038(nyi)005:3493: h'u h'u h'u bi shwa badz+ra la man+da la phata /
NK038(nyi)005:3495: ha la ha la ha ram /
NK038(nyi)005:3499: zhes pas sdig pa dag par gyur nas /
NK038(nyi)005:3500: dkyil 'khor gsum du bzhugs par bsam mo //
NK038(nyi)005:3502: drag po dug lnga gzhom pa'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)005:3503: bcom ldan dpal chen he ru ka'i //
NK038(nyi)005:3504: zhal du rngums te sna nas bton //
NK038(nyi)005:3505: de tshe sme ba brtsegs par bstan //
NK038(nyi)005:3506: rnal 'byor yongs kyi grogs bya zhes //
NK038(nyi)005:3507: dam bca' de las mi 'gyur bas //
NK038(nyi)005:3508: de phyir mgon po nag por btags //
NK038(nyi)005:3509: khyod ni yak+sha gnod sbyin gtso //
NK038(nyi)005:3510: de phyir tshogs kyi bdag por btags //
NK038(nyi)005:3511: khyod kyi khro bo gying gi tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:3512: de phyir sgrol gying chen por btags //
NK038(nyi)005:3513: khyod ni ma mo yongs kyi gtso //
NK038(nyi)005:3514: de phyir dur khrod bdag por btags //
NK038(nyi)005:3515: khyod ni lha srin yongs kyi bdag /
NK038(nyi)005:3516: de phyir nam mkha'i bdag mor btags //
NK038(nyi)005:3517: rnal 'byor dam can dgos pa sgrub //
NK038(nyi)005:3518: de phyir legs ldan nag por btags //
NK038(nyi)005:3519: phyi yi mtshan nas bos pa'i tshe //
NK038(nyi)005:3520: mgon po legs ldan nag por byas //
NK038(nyi)005:3521: nang gi mtshan nas bos pa'i tshe //
NK038(nyi)005:3522: bdud 'dul dur khrod sgrol ba'i gying //
NK038(nyi)005:3523: gsang ba'i mtshan nas bos pa'i tshe //
NK038(nyi)005:3524: rdo rje sgrol byed drag po rtsal //
NK038(nyi)005:3525: gang nas bos kyang khyod kyi ming //
NK038(nyi)005:3526: ji ltar btags kyang khyod kyi mtshan //
NK038(nyi)005:3527: ma g.yel dur khrod chen po yis //
NK038(nyi)005:3529: yum chen dbang mo skam ma dang //
NK038(nyi)005:3530: ro yi gdan la gnyis med bzhugs //
NK038(nyi)005:3531: b+hur kur ma h+aa k+aa la kro ti shwa ri sa ma ya tish+tha lhan /
NK038(nyi)005:3533: pad+ma ta kri ta badz+ra kro ta h+ya ya gri
NK038(nyi)005:3534: ba h'u hu lu hu lu h'u phata zhes khro
NK038(nyi)005:3535: bo rta gdong gi phyag gi sbrul zhags kyis nag
NK038(nyi)005:3537: bsdams nas dam las 'da' bar mi ster bar bsam mo //
NK038(nyi)005:3539: ye shes rin chen dbu rgyan mchog /
NK038(nyi)005:3540: gzi brjid phung po bla na med //
NK038(nyi)005:3541: sangs rgyas rin chen kun 'dus pas //
NK038(nyi)005:3542: rnam par rgyal la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)005:3543: badz+ra rak+sha pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka na ma a ti pu'o //
NK038(nyi)005:3545: bdag gi rtsa ba yan lag gi dam tshig mi mnyam par bsam shing bsrung ngo //
NK038(nyi)005:3547: pho brang thod mkhar rab 'jigs pa'i //
NK038(nyi)005:3548: gnam lcags 'bar ba'i gzer chen gyis //
NK038(nyi)005:3549: brtan par btab pa'i dur khrod na //
NK038(nyi)005:3550: tshogs bdag yab yum phyag rgya ni //
NK038(nyi)005:3551: gdong bzhi mthing nag thod phreng can //
NK038(nyi)005:3552: spyan ldog mche gtsegs rdzu 'phrul mgo /
NK038(nyi)005:3553: phyag bzhi phyag drug rdzu 'phrul lag /
NK038(nyi)005:3554: zhabs bzhi zhabs gnyis rdzu 'phrul can //
NK038(nyi)005:3555: yang dag don gyi phyag rgya ni //
NK038(nyi)005:3556: zhal gcig phyag gnyis gcer bu yis //
NK038(nyi)005:3557: g.yas pa gri gug sngon po yis //
NK038(nyi)005:3558: g.yon pa b+han+d+ha lcang lo bsnams //
NK038(nyi)005:3559: drag po ral can 'khril zhing khro //
NK038(nyi)005:3560: g.yas pa rgyu zhags yab la 'khyud //
NK038(nyi)005:3561: g.yon pa b+han+d+ha thod nang du //
NK038(nyi)005:3562: 'bru mar rdzas lnga chang sbyar ba //
NK038(nyi)005:3563: rang gi longs spyod gtso la bstab //
NK038(nyi)005:3564: yab yum gnyis su med pa khyed //
NK038(nyi)005:3565: dur khrod gdan la bzhugs nas kyang //
NK038(nyi)005:3566: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa bzhes //
NK038(nyi)005:3567: sarba ta th+aa ga ta dang po phyi mchod 'bul
NK038(nyi)005:3568: ba ni badz+ra rak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra da
NK038(nyi)005:3569: ri ma h+aa dz+ny+aa na man+dala badz+ra a ha ru
NK038(nyi)005:3576: badz+ra ru nang gi mchod pa'i sngags gong gi sham bu ru pa p+au tsa h'u /
NK038(nyi)005:3578: r+aa sa spa r+she p+au tsa h'u /
NK038(nyi)005:3579: mgon po'i yang phyi mchod 'bul ba ni bur kur ma h+aa ka la ya /
NK038(nyi)005:3585: badz+ra a h+aa ra p+au tsa h'u /
NK038(nyi)005:3601: rang byung sman mchod ni gdod nas rnam par dag /
NK038(nyi)005:3602: rtsa brgyad stong la sbyar ba'i sman //
NK038(nyi)005:3603: rtsa ba 'bum phrag yongs pa'i bcud //
NK038(nyi)005:3604: sangs rgyas stong gi dngos grub len //
NK038(nyi)005:3605: dam tshig sbyin pa chen po 'di //
NK038(nyi)005:3606: sbyin no bstab po bskul lo mchod //
NK038(nyi)005:3607: dus gsum bde gshegs rgyal ba ma lus dang //
NK038(nyi)005:3608: yi dam dkyil 'khor lha tshogs ma lus pa //
NK038(nyi)005:3609: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mchod pa 'bul //
NK038(nyi)005:3610: thugs rje che dgongs dbang dang dngos grub rtsol //
NK038(nyi)005:3611: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa ram kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)005:3612: lung dang man ngag shes rgyud gab sbas pa'i //
NK038(nyi)005:3613: nges pa'i lung ston dus gsum bla ma la /
NK038(nyi)005:3614: rnam dag 'gre tshogs rje tshogs bdag dpal ldan he ru ka /
NK038(nyi)005:3615: 'bar ba'i rgyal po khrag thung yab lnga la //
NK038(nyi)005:3616: rnam dag rtsa sngags la kha ram gdags so //
NK038(nyi)005:3617: dpal chen sku la gnyis med dgyes sbyor ba'i //
NK038(nyi)005:3618: kro ti shwa ri yum chen lnga rnams la /
NK038(nyi)005:3619: rnam dag dpal chen yab yum sku la bskyed pa'i sras //
NK038(nyi)005:3620: gnas yul sgo ma khro mo nyi shu la //
NK038(nyi)005:3621: rnam dag slas dang byi mo ming sring ma mo'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:3622: dbang phyug la sogs bka' nyan tshogs rnams la //
NK038(nyi)005:3623: rnam dag rnal 'byor yongs kyi bsrung mar zhal bzhes pa'i //
NK038(nyi)005:3624: dpal ldan mgon po legs ldan nag po dang //
NK038(nyi)005:3625: nye gnas yum chen kro ti shwa ri la //
NK038(nyi)005:3626: rnam dag bsgrub sngags la kha ram gdags so //
NK038(nyi)005:3627: kro ta khro bo gying gi tshogs rnams la //
NK038(nyi)005:3628: rnam dag rak+sha gnod sbyin dregs pa'i tshogs rnams la /
NK038(nyi)005:3629: rnam dag rak+sha srin po rngam pa'i tshogs rnams la //
NK038(nyi)005:3630: rnam dag tsit+ta za byed ma mo'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)005:3631: rnam dag nye gnas gdung ba'i ming sring brgyan rnams la //
NK038(nyi)005:3632: rnam dag gus pa'i bu mo chen mo brgyad rnams la //
NK038(nyi)005:3633: rnam dag dur khrod sa yi sgo bsrung bzhi rnams dang //
NK038(nyi)005:3634: dur khrod bdag mo gru 'debs bzhi rnams la /
NK038(nyi)005:3635: rnam dag sring mo chen mo nyi shu rtsa brgyad dang //
NK038(nyi)005:3636: bka' nyan pho nyan dam can rgya mtsho la //
NK038(nyi)005:3637: rnam dag +aahmh'u zhes 'bru gsum gyi dngos grub blang ngo //
NK038(nyi)005:3639: lcang lor gnas pa'i ma h+aa b+han+d+ha ru //
NK038(nyi)005:3640: byang chub sems dang ma h+aa rak+ta dang //
NK038(nyi)005:3641: dri chen ku ku'i chu de rnam pa lnga //
NK038(nyi)005:3642: gnyis meng sbyar ba'i pany+tsa a mri ta //
NK038(nyi)005:3643: nag po chen po 'khor dang bcas la 'bul //
NK038(nyi)005:3644: mchod bzhes dam skongs dngos grub stsol //
NK038(nyi)005:3645: sarba ta th+aa ga ta badz+ra rak+sha sh+r+ai he ru
NK038(nyi)005:3646: ka badz+ra da ri dz+ny+aa na man+da la i dan
NK038(nyi)005:3654: sarba ta th+aa ga ta badz+ra rak+sha sh+r+ai he ru
NK038(nyi)005:3655: ka badz+ra d+ha ri dz+nya na man+da la ma h+aa
NK038(nyi)005:3656: pany+tsa a mri ta pi pa zhes gsang mnan dbul
NK038(nyi)005:3658: gong ltar la 'gre sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma
NK038(nyi)005:3659: h+aa rak+ta a r+g+ham pra tits+tsha bi pa ta kh+aa
NK038(nyi)005:3660: hi / bur kur ma h+aa k+aa la kro ta
NK038(nyi)005:3661: yak+sha rak+sha tsit+ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa
NK038(nyi)005:3662: hi / hi / ma h+aa ba lim ta kh+aa h+ai ma h+aa rak+ta pi pa ta kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)005:3663: ma h+aa ba su kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)005:3665: go ro tsa na kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)005:3666: e h+ye ma h+aa k+aa la i dan du sa /
NK038(nyi)005:3669: mam sa ma h+aa ba limd+ha pra t+ainy+tsa ho /
NK038(nyi)005:3671: tshogs bdag 'khor bcas kyis gtor ma //
NK038(nyi)005:3673: dam rdzas longs spyod chang phud /
NK038(nyi)005:3674: rak+ta'i rgyal mtsho zhal du gsol bar bsam mo //
NK038(nyi)005:3675: de nas mnyes par bsam la /
NK038(nyi)005:3676: dam dbag rdo rje can go /
NK038(nyi)005:3678: mna' yid la dan te bgag /
NK038(nyi)005:3680: dam ma h+aa gling gi ces lngar ltar dam rdzas dbul lo rdar rnams bya /
NK038(nyi)005:3683: dka' thub tshur bsdom tsan da thub chen po zhes pa nas 'jug tu /
NK038(nyi)005:3684: bskang ngo dgra srog chod la shog /
NK038(nyi)005:3686: b+hur kur ma h+aa k+aa la yo /
NK038(nyi)005:3687: h'u mes rdzas ma dag pa bshags ka ri byi ra ku li sha sa ro da ya /
NK038(nyi)005:3688: ni la dzo mu dang ba no gan d+ha kha tam ka ga he dz+wa la ba phud te /
NK038(nyi)005:3689: ba ta ge shwa bi sha la /
NK038(nyi)005:3690: a shi ra pad+ma tsan+d+ra ni /
NK038(nyi)005:3691: ka ma ku ta da ri /
NK038(nyi)005:3692: rak+ta bi drod dza la s+t+wam b+han+d+ha he ru ka badz+ra ma /
NK038(nyi)005:3693: pa ra san pa mu khang tig shan dang ta ka ra la /
NK038(nyi)005:3694: ces lan gsum bang pas sdu tsa ma gnas pa
NK038(nyi)005:3695: shag tha ma sam ti mig sar pa bshags so
NK038(nyi)005:3697: bcom smon lam gdab pa ni ldan rdo rje srin
NK038(nyi)005:3698: po tshogs kyi bdag po dpal sh+r+ai he ru ka
NK038(nyi)005:3699: / badz+ra ta ki ni la sogs te ku tsa
NK038(nyi)005:3700: can gyi tshogs bsam gyis mi khyab pa rnams rang
NK038(nyi)005:3701: rang dga' mgu dang dad pa'i stobs dang brtul shugs
NK038(nyi)005:3702: kyis bskal pa'i me dpung ltar 'dril zhing 'gro ba'i
NK038(nyi)005:3703: don la thugs rje rtse gacigatu gsan du gsol /
NK038(nyi)005:3704: gzhan yang dpal rdo rje srin po'i bka'i pho nya /
NK038(nyi)005:3709: phyi ltar rdo rje shangs gtso rtsal /
NK038(nyi)005:3710: nang ltar rdo rje drag po rtsal /
NK038(nyi)005:3711: gsang ba ltar ro langs tshogs kyi bdag po /
NK038(nyi)005:3715: dur khrod kyi ma mo bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang bcas pa rnams gsan du gsol lo //
NK038(nyi)005:3716: bdag cag rnams kyi dga' ba chen po'i sgor zhug
NK038(nyi)005:3717: nas rdo rje slob dpon gyi sku la smad cing
NK038(nyi)005:3718: gdung sems rgyun chad pa dang /
NK038(nyi)005:3719: rdo rje mched la spangs pa'i las byas pa dang /
NK038(nyi)005:3720: lha gdos par sgom zhing bzlas pa yengs shing mi tshig dang 'dres pa dang /
NK038(nyi)005:3721: lta ba logs par rtogs shing snod med pa la man ngag spel ba dang /
NK038(nyi)005:3722: gab pa'i gsang ba ma rtogs par sbas pa'i gsang ba la mngon par 'chol te /
NK038(nyi)005:3723: sbyor sgrol du ming btags nas bsad pa dang /
NK038(nyi)005:3724: sred pa'i 'dod chags la mngon par zhen cing nga
NK038(nyi)005:3725: rgyal dang dregs pa'i dbang gis dpa' bo'i ngang tshul
NK038(nyi)005:3726: 'chos su gyur te gsang sngags spyod nyes pa dang
NK038(nyi)005:3727: / sred pa'i 'dod chags la mngon par zhen cing
NK038(nyi)005:3728: nga rgyal dang dregs pa'i dbang gis tshe 'dir rnal
NK038(nyi)005:3729: 'byor pho mo rnams kyi thugs dang 'gal te /
NK038(nyi)005:3730: yang ngan song sdug bsngal gyi rgyur gyur pa rnams
NK038(nyi)005:3731: mthol bshags shing mchis na phral du dag cing yun
NK038(nyi)005:3732: du byang bar mdzad du gsol lo //
NK038(nyi)005:3733: de nas smon lam btab ste /
NK038(nyi)005:3735: mgon po khyed mchod byin rlabs kyis //
NK038(nyi)005:3736: phyogs dang dus rnams thams cad du //
NK038(nyi)005:3737: sems can legs don 'byor pa la //
NK038(nyi)005:3738: bgegs kyi gnod pa kun med shog /
NK038(nyi)005:3739: rta dang glang po nor dang 'bru //
NK038(nyi)005:3740: bu tsha pha ma gnyen bshes rnams //
NK038(nyi)005:3741: dge zhing tshe ring nad med par //
NK038(nyi)005:3742: thams cad 'byor pa ldan par shog /
NK038(nyi)005:3743: 'gro la nyes med bde gyur nas //
NK038(nyi)005:3744: nad dang mu ge kun bral shog /
NK038(nyi)005:3745: rgyal po dge zhing des pa rnams //
NK038(nyi)005:3746: chos kyi rgyal srid skyong bar shog /
NK038(nyi)005:3747: bde bar gshegs pa'i bstan pa 'di //
NK038(nyi)005:3748: phyogs bcu kun tu rgyas pa dang //
NK038(nyi)005:3749: myur du sems can thams cad kun //
NK038(nyi)005:3750: chos kyi snod du 'gyur bar shog /
NK038(nyi)005:3751: dge ba thams cad legs bsngo zhing //
NK038(nyi)005:3752: mgon po khyed rten mthu dpal gyis //
NK038(nyi)005:3753: bdag cag 'khor dang bcas pa rnams //
NK038(nyi)005:3754: longs spyod rnams gnyis thob nas kyang //
NK038(nyi)005:3755: khyad par rdo rje theg mchog gi /
NK038(nyi)005:3756: rim gnyis zab mo mthar phyin te //
NK038(nyi)005:3757: 'bras bu sku gnyis mchog thob nas //
NK038(nyi)005:3758: don gnyis phun sum tshogs par shog /
NK038(nyi)005:3759: bdag ni dus rnams thams cad du //
NK038(nyi)005:3760: dpal mgon dbang phyug legs ldan gyi //
NK038(nyi)005:3761: mthu byin thugs la dbang thob nas //
NK038(nyi)005:3763: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung bar shog /
NK038(nyi)005:3764: ces smon lam gdab pa ni /
NK038(nyi)005:3765: de ltar byas pa bkra shis shing mi rdzas 'phel bar 'gyur ro //
NK038(nyi)005:3766: de nas 'phrin las bcol la 'dzab bya ste /
NK038(nyi)005:3767: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK038(nyi)005:3768: bur kur i tsi ki phyi u tsash+ma kro ta h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)005:3769: bdag he ru kar gsal ba la phyogs bcu'i rgyal
NK038(nyi)005:3770: ba'i 'od zer mang po bdag la thim pas bdag
NK038(nyi)005:3771: dpal du gsal btab ste nus pa dang ldan par
NK038(nyi)005:3772: bsam / bdag gi thugs ka nas khro chung mang
NK038(nyi)005:3773: po 'phros te mgon po bskul nas las byed par
NK038(nyi)005:3774: bsam / bsam / 'khor rnams zhor langs la 'gro bar bsam mo //
NK038(nyi)005:3775: de nas thun mtshams su he ru ka dang mgon po la sman mchod dbul lo //
NK038(nyi)005:3780: gsur chen dud pa btang nas kyang /
NK038(nyi)005:3781: rdo rje rnge chung drag tu rdungs pas /
NK038(nyi)005:3782: ces pa la sogs pas bstod cing las gzhol /
NK038(nyi)005:3783: de nas tshogs khro bo ltar bya /
NK038(nyi)005:3785: dka' thub chen po tshur gson dang /
NK038(nyi)005:3787: yongs su rdzog par blang par bya'o //
NK038(nyi)005:3788: zhes pa'i bar gyis mgon po 'khor bcas la dbul lo //
NK038(nyi)005:3792: mnan pa zor byed na yang skabs 'dir bya /
NK038(nyi)005:3793: bstan ma skyong zhing dkyil 'khor bsdu //
NK038(nyi)005:3795: mgon po'i bsgrub thabs rdzogs so //
NK038(nyi)005:3797: rdo rje srin po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)005:3798: gang zhing bsnyen bsgrub bzhi la rtag tu gnas par 'dod pa des 'di ltar bya'o //
NK038(nyi)005:3802: zhes rang gi srog la tshad bzhag pa'i don yin no //
NK038(nyi)005:3804: ru lu pho nya tshogs su 'dren //
NK038(nyi)005:3805: pho nya'i pho brang lang+ka'i yul //
NK038(nyi)005:3806: u rgyan ri bo ma la ya //
NK038(nyi)005:3807: kong ka thang dmar drag po'i rtse //
NK038(nyi)005:3808: bam ri thod ma khar gzhal yas nas //
NK038(nyi)005:3809: khro bdag legs ldan nag po ni //
NK038(nyi)005:3811: ra li ra li zhes brjod las //
NK038(nyi)005:3812: dkar nag phye ba'i spyan 'bur bas //
NK038(nyi)005:3813: dmar la gdangs pas dbang du sdu //
NK038(nyi)005:3814: nyams pa gang yin dbang du bsdus //
NK038(nyi)005:3815: h+aa la ha la zhes brjod pas //
NK038(nyi)005:3816: ha ha rngam pa'i zhal gdangs shing //
NK038(nyi)005:3817: mche ba gnam lcags spu grir gtams //
NK038(nyi)005:3818: spu gri tham tham snying la tham //
NK038(nyi)005:3819: ru lu ru lu zhes brjod pas //
NK038(nyi)005:3820: g.yas na gri thogs sgril ba'i gying //
NK038(nyi)005:3821: gri gug spu gris sgrol bar byed //
